#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:177
msgid ""
"And so we come to another peaceful day... I know it is Lady Maat's order, "
"but the presence of all these Aragwaithi here is beginning to bother me."
msgstr ""
"Y así llegamos a otro día de paz… Sé que es orden de lady Maat, pero la "
"presencia de todos estos aragwaithi aquí empieza a molestarme."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:181
msgid "Why, Headmistress?"
msgstr "¿Por qué, directora?"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:185
msgid ""
"Isn't it obvious? They've been far from their homes and wives for three "
"weeks now, alone in this isolated valley with dozens of young women... They "
"may be Lord Abhai's trusted soldiers, but they're still men after all!"
msgstr ""
"¿No es obvio? Llevan tres semanas lejos de sus hogares y esposas, solos en "
"este valle aislado con docenas de mujeres jóvenes… Pueden ser los soldados "
"de confianza de lord Abhai, ¡pero siguen siendo hombres al fin y al cabo!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:189
msgid ""
"Well, in truth I think the students are kind of enjoying their presence..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, la verdad es que creo que las estudiantes están disfrutando bastante "
"de su presencia…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:193
msgid ""
"What do you... Wait, what is that column of smoke rising in the distance? "
"And why is that soldier running as if ogres were on his heels?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué quieres decir…? Espera, ¿qué es esa columna de humo que se eleva a lo "
"lejos? ¡Y por qué ese soldado corre como si tuviera ogros pisándole los "
"talones?"

#. [message], speaker=Allore
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:200
msgid ""
"(panting) Headmistress... Dragons... were sighted... in the mountains to... "
"the northwest..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Directora… Dragones… avistados… en las montañas… al noroeste…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:204
msgid ""
"(shocked) Dragons?! But... Is it possible that another dragon has gone rogue "
"and decided to attack us, like Krathon did years ago?"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendida) ¡¿Dragones?! Pero… ¿Es posible que otro dragón se haya "
"rebelado y decidido atacarnos, como hizo Krathon hace años?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:208
msgid ""
"If so, I'm really not worried; I can see them now, and they're quite puny "
"for dragons."
msgstr ""
"Si es así, realmente no estoy preocupada; los veo ahora y son bastante "
"insignificantes para ser dragones."

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:212
msgid ""
"It's because they're drakes, not dragons! Now things begin to make more "
"sense: not all drake tribes are under Lord Agniballi's control, and some "
"even dare harass us, or the Aragwaithi. (shouting) You, drake warrior! You "
"may have heard the Windsong were a peaceful order composed of women, and "
"thought us an easy prey, but know that armies larger than yours have already "
"attacked us, and that none of them has survived to tell the tale!"
msgstr ""
"¡Es porque son dracos, no dragones! Ahora las cosas empiezan a tener más "
"sentido: no todas las tribus draco están bajo el control de lord Agniballi y "
"algunas incluso se atreven a acosarnos a nosotros o a los aragwaithi. "
"(gritando) ¡Tú, guerrero draco! Puede que hayas oído que las Hijas del "
"Viento éramos una orden pacífica compuesta por mujeres y nos consideraras "
"presa fácil, ¡pero sabe que ejércitos más grandes que el tuyo ya nos han "
"atacado y que ninguno ha sobrevivido para contarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelka Kohn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:216
msgid ""
"(roaring) Onwards warriors, if we sweep this valley quickly enough we won't "
"have to share the witches' soft meat with the others!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Adelante guerreros, si barremos este valle lo bastante rápido no "
"tendremos que compartir la tierna carne de las brujas con los demás!"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:220
msgid ""
"He didn't even heed me, the impudent! But for what he says, his is not the "
"only band attacking the mountains; we must defeat it quickly so that we may "
"flee. However, I'm afraid that even if we put every student in this haven to "
"aid the Aragwaithi soldiers, we won't be able to withstand these drakes... I "
"need you to summon your pets to help us in this battle, Myra."
msgstr ""
"¡Ni siquiera me ha hecho caso, el insolente! Pero por lo que dice, la suya "
"no es la única banda atacando las montañas; debemos derrotarla rápido para "
"poder huir. Sin embargo, me temo que aunque pongamos a todas las estudiantes "
"de este refugio a ayudar a los soldados aragwaithi, no podremos resistir a "
"estos dracos… Necesito que invoques a tus mascotas para que nos ayuden en "
"esta batalla, Myra."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:224
msgid "You mean the elementals? But you told me to stop summoning them..."
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres a los elementales? Pero me dijiste que dejara de invocarlos…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:228
msgid ""
"I know I told you so, but now forget it! I need you to unleash them on the "
"drakes, or we'll all die before sunset!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo sé, pero ahora olvídalo! ¡Necesito que los sueltes sobre los dracos o "
"todos moriremos antes del atardecer!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:232
msgid "All right, I get it. I'm going to the forest to call them..."
msgstr "De acuerdo, lo entiendo. Voy al bosque a llamarlos…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:240
msgid "Erm, Miss Myra...?"
msgstr "Eh, señorita Myra…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:244
msgid "(sighing)*not her again...* What do you want now, blondie?"
msgstr "(suspirando) *no ella otra vez…* ¿Qué quieres ahora, rubia?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:248
msgid "I heard we're being attacked by dragons, is that true?"
msgstr "He oído que nos están atacando dragones, ¿es verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:252
msgid ""
"No, we're being attacked by drakes, and probably we'll all have to fight, so "
"go quickly to the sanctum, that Headmistress is rallying the soldiers and "
"the students to fight these invaders."
msgstr ""
"No, nos están atacando dracos y probablemente todos tendremos que luchar, "
"así que ve rápido al santuario, la directora está reuniendo a los soldados y "
"a las estudiantes para luchar contra estos invasores."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Erm, if you don't mind, I'd rather stay with you... I mean, not to hide "
"myself behind you, of course, but fight alongside you."
msgstr ""
"Eh, si no te importa, preferiría quedarme contigo… Quiero decir, no para "
"esconderme detrás de ti, claro, sino para luchar a tu lado."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:260
msgid ""
"(eyes rolling) Believe me, you'd be better off fighting under Headmistress' "
"leadership, I'll only lead you to your death. And besides, you'll just "
"burden me."
msgstr ""
"(poniendo los ojos en blanco) Créeme, estarías mejor luchando bajo el mando "
"de la directora, yo solo te llevaré a la muerte. Y además, solo me "
"estorbarás."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:264
msgid ""
"But I really can help you! I have learned to use the Cipher of Immobility, "
"with which I can slow down any enemy long enough for you to strike the death "
"blow!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero de verdad puedo ayudarte! He aprendido a usar el Cifrado de "
"Inmovilidad, con el que puedo ralentizar a cualquier enemigo el tiempo "
"suficiente para que tú des el golpe mortal."

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:268
msgid ""
"Just let her stay with you and summon your pets at once! Time is running!"
msgstr ""
"¡Déjala quedarse contigo e invoca a tus mascotas ahora mismo! ¡El tiempo se "
"acaba!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:272
msgid "(snorting) So be it, blondie, you may fight with me!"
msgstr "(resoplando) Está bien, rubia, ¡puedes luchar conmigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:284
msgid ""
"I had never seen one of them so close... They're just so cool! I doubt those "
"overgrown lizards will stand a chance against them!"
msgstr ""
"Nunca había visto uno tan de cerca… ¡Son impresionantes! Dudo que esos "
"lagartos crecidos tengan alguna posibilidad contra ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:298
msgid ""
"Wow! So this is the Soul Bullet I heard of so much! Please do tell me, how "
"do you..."
msgstr ""
"¡Guau! ¡Así que esta es la Bala del Alma de la que tanto he oído hablar! Por "
"favor dime, ¿cómo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Veela, if you don't shut up soon, I'll show you that I too know how to cast "
"a Cipher of Immobility!"
msgstr ""
"Veela, si no te callas pronto, te mostraré que yo también sé lanzar un "
"Cifrado de Inmovilidad."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:314
msgid "Here... it... goes...!"
msgstr "¡Aquí… va…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:329
msgid "(blinks) I... I did it!"
msgstr "(parpadea) ¡Yo… lo hice!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:333
msgid ""
"(chuckles) And most impressively, you survived to tell the tale. Maybe "
"you're not such a pushover after all, blondie."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Y lo más impresionante es que sobreviviste para contarlo. Quizá no "
"seas tan inútil después de todo, rubia."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:348
msgid "Welcome to the Windsong Haven at Hashira's Valley!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenidos al Refugio de las Hijas del Viento en el Valle de Hashira!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelka Kohn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:360
msgid ""
"We clearly underestimated you... But know that we're but a small fingernail "
"of Lord Shek'har's full army..."
msgstr ""
"Claramente os subestimamos… Pero sabed que solo somos una uña pequeña del "
"ejército completo de lord Shek’har…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:368
msgid "Shek'har, I've heard that name before..."
msgstr "Shek’har, he oído ese nombre antes…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:372
msgid ""
"Of course you have, he's the Dragons' Land's viceroy, second only to Lord "
"Agniballi himself. Can it be that he rebelled against Agniballi and decided "
"to attack us on his own...?"
msgstr ""
"Claro que sí, es el virrey de la Tierra de los Dragones, solo por debajo del "
"propio lord Agniballi. ¿Será que se rebeló contra Agniballi y decidió "
"atacarnos por su cuenta…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:376
msgid "Or maybe Agniballi himself decided to turn against us?"
msgstr "¿O quizá el propio Agniballi decidió volverse contra nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:380
msgid ""
"That can't be, he's been friendly with us humans for thousands of years! Why "
"would he change his mind so abruptly? Well, this is a question for the "
"Kalian; as for us, let's not tarry here any longer, and hurry to Valon, "
"which is better protected..."
msgstr ""
"Eso no puede ser, ¡ha sido amistoso con los humanos durante miles de años! "
"¿Por qué cambiaría de idea tan de repente? Bueno, esa es una pregunta para "
"el Kalian; en cuanto a nosotros, no nos demoremos más aquí y corramos a "
"Valon, que está mejor protegida…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:384
msgid "Why Valon? We should go to Hiera'Shirsha!"
msgstr "¿Por qué Valon? ¡Deberíamos ir a Hiera’Shirsha!"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:388
msgid ""
"Those drakes came from the west, and if what that leader said about his army "
"is true, Hiera'Shirsha is currently in great jeopardy. I want to go there "
"too, and you shall come with me should you wish, but I must first ensure the "
"safety of my students. Commander, will Valon grant us asylum?"
msgstr ""
"Estos dracos vinieron del oeste y, si lo que dijo ese líder sobre su "
"ejército es cierto, Hiera’Shirsha está ahora en grave peligro. Yo también "
"quiero ir allí y tú vendrás conmigo si lo deseas, pero primero debo asegurar "
"la seguridad de mis estudiantes. Comandante, ¿Valon nos concederá asilo?"

#. [message], speaker=Allore
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:392
msgid "Most certainly, Headmistress."
msgstr "Por supuesto, directora."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:396
msgid "If Hiera'Shirsha is in jeopardy, we should go to our sisters' aid!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si Hiera’Shirsha está en peligro, deberíamos ir en ayuda de nuestras "
"hermanas!"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:400
msgid ""
"Myra, you may be Lady Maat's daughter and our best student, but you must "
"still obey your elders. I say we're going east, to Valon, so east we shall "
"go!"
msgstr ""
"Myra, puedes ser la hija de lady Maat y nuestra mejor estudiante, pero aún "
"debes obedecer a tus mayores. ¡Digo que vamos al este, a Valon, así que al "
"este iremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:404
msgid ""
"And you may be my superior, but Hiera'Shirsha's still in danger, and needs "
"help now! So west <i>I</i> shall go!"
msgstr ""
"Y tú puedes ser mi superior, ¡pero Hiera’Shirsha sigue en peligro y necesita "
"ayuda ahora! ¡Así que al oeste <i>yo</i> iré yo!"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:430
msgid ""
"Damned girl! Honestly, I can't understand why Lady Maat insists so much on "
"keeping her, even if her potential power is so great! And that other "
"student, Veela, could have proved her mastery of the Immobility Cipher and "
"stopped Myra for her own sake!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita niña! ¡Sinceramente, no entiendo por qué lady Maat insiste tanto en "
"mantenerla, aunque su poder potencial sea tan grande! ¡Y esa otra "
"estudiante, Veela, podría haber demostrado su dominio del Cifrado de "
"Inmovilidad y haber detenido a Myra por su propio bien!"

#. [message], speaker=Allore
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:434
msgid ""
"Erm, Headmistress, I think she was too busy clinging herself to one of those "
"plant elementals to cast the cipher..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, directora, creo que estaba demasiado ocupada aferrándose a uno de esos "
"elementales de planta para lanzar el cifrado…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:438
msgid ""
"Wh... Oh no, don't tell me she followed Myra! And now what is that Veela has "
"seen in that darn girl that she idolizes her so much?! I give up; Maat shall "
"deal with her later, I've done all I could to put some sense in that head..."
msgstr ""
"Qu… ¡Oh no, no me digáis que siguió a Myra! ¡Y ahora qué ha visto esa Veela "
"en esa maldita niña para idolatrarla tanto?! Me rindo; Maat se ocupará de "
"ella después, he hecho todo lo que pude para meterle algo de sentido común "
"en la cabeza…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:454
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:307
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:385
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:605
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:254
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:471
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:422
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:838
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1047
msgid "I... can't die now... mother...!"
msgstr "Yo… no puedo morir ahora… ¡madre…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:458
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:311
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:389
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:609
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:258
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:475
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:426
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:842
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1051
msgid "No, Myra! Don't give up now, please!"
msgstr "¡No, Myra! ¡No te rindas ahora, por favor!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:472
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:325
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:403
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:623
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:272
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:489
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:440
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:856
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1065
msgid "It hurts! Myra, save me...!"
msgstr "¡Me duele! ¡Myra, sálvame…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:476
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:329
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:407
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:627
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:276
msgid ""
"No! How could I have let her die? If I can't even save a single person, I "
"don't think I'll be able to do anything for our cause..."
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¿Cómo he podido dejar que muriera? Si no soy capaz ni de salvar a una "
"sola persona, no creo que pueda hacer nada por nuestra causa…"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:491
msgid "I can't die now, my students need me!..."
msgstr "¡No puedo morir ahora, mis estudiantes me necesitan…!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelka Kohn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:502
msgid "Curse it! Now we won't have them only for ourselves!"
msgstr "¡Maldición! ¡Ahora no los tendremos solo para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Lashimi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/01_Rain_of_Fire.cfg:507
msgid "More drake forces come from the north! We're doomed!"
msgstr "¡Más fuerzas draco vienen del norte! ¡Estamos perdidos!"

