#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:107
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:133
msgid "Kegrid"
msgstr "Kegrid"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:143
msgid "(panting) Have we... arrived...?"
msgstr "(jadeando) ¿Ya… llegamos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:147
msgid ""
"Do you see any bright walls on the top of any mountain? Of course we haven't!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ves alguna muralla brillante en la cima de alguna montaña? ¡Claro que no "
"hemos llegado!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:151
msgid ""
"But we have been travelling for five days already, and you said "
"Hiera'Shirsha was three days away from Hashira's Valley..."
msgstr ""
"Pero ya llevamos cinco días viajando y dijiste que Hiera’Shirsha estaba a "
"tres días del Valle de Hashira…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:155
msgid "I... well, I think I took the wrong path."
msgstr "Yo… bueno, creo que tomé el camino equivocado."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:159
msgid "So we're lost?"
msgstr "¿Entonces estamos perdidas?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#. [message], speaker=Ronak
#. [unit_type], id=Veela Windsong Runeforger, race=windsong, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Veela Windsong Savant, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:163
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:470
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:381
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Veela_Runeforger.cfg:35
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Veela_Savant.cfg:29
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:167
msgid ""
"I feared it would happen, these forests and mountains are so similar to each "
"other, it's hard to find a reference point."
msgstr ""
"Temía que pasara, estos bosques y montañas se parecen tanto entre sí que es "
"difícil encontrar un punto de referencia."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:171
msgid ""
"Anyway, we may not have reached Hiera'Shirsha, but we haven't gone anywhere "
"either. Look, this valley is inhabited by trolls and dwarves, both allies of "
"us Windsong."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, puede que no hayamos llegado a Hiera’Shirsha, pero tampoco "
"nos hemos perdido del todo. Mirad, este valle está habitado por trolls y "
"enanos, ambos aliados de nosotras las Hijas del Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:175
msgid "I see, but they seem to be in trouble."
msgstr "Ya veo, pero parecen estar en problemas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:187
msgid "Yes, another bunch of drakes come from the north."
msgstr "Sí, otro grupo de dracos viene del norte."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:191
msgid "Quickly, we must aid our friends!"
msgstr "¡Rápido, debemos ayudar a nuestros amigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:199
msgid "Hey, aren't those Windsong coming from the south?"
msgstr "¡Eh, no son esas Hijas del Viento que vienen del sur?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Greetings, friends. I am Myra, daughter of High Ascendant Maat; I and my "
"companion have fled from our haven at Hashira's Valley, expelled by the same "
"monsters that are attacking you now. May we jump in the party as well?"
msgstr ""
"Saludos, amigos. Soy Myra, hija de la Gran Ascendente Maat; mi compañera y "
"yo hemos huido de nuestro refugio en el Valle de Hashira, expulsadas por los "
"mismos monstruos que os atacan ahora. ¿Podemos unirnos a la fiesta?"

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:207
msgid ""
"The daughter of the great Maat? Ye are more than welcome to help us, for "
"we're sorely beset!"
msgstr ""
"¿La hija de la gran Maat? ¡Sois más que bienvenidas a ayudarnos, estamos en "
"apuros!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:211
msgid ""
"I've noticed that, but then why don't you ally with the trolls, just for the "
"time being, given that you're both being attacked by the same foe?"
msgstr ""
"Me he dado cuenta, pero entonces ¿por qué no os aliáis con los trolls, "
"aunque solo sea temporalmente, ya que ambos estáis siendo atacados por el "
"mismo enemigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:215
msgid ""
"Hrumph! That is what I suggested, but those smelly, greedy dwarves would not "
"have it so! They say we will let them take the brunt of the offensive and, "
"when the battle is over, attack what is left of them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! ¡Eso es lo que yo propuse, pero esos enanos apestosos y avariciosos "
"no quisieron! ¡Dicen que les dejaríamos recibir todo el impacto de la "
"ofensiva y que, cuando termine la batalla, atacaríamos lo que quede de ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:219
msgid "And what else should we expect from brutish animals like ye?"
msgstr "¿Y qué más podríamos esperar de bestias brutales como vosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:223
msgid ""
"Hey, friends, calm down and listen, please. If we remain divided like this, "
"we'll be crushed one by one. If it's distrust that is preventing you from "
"uniting, then allow me to serve as a mediator; and, if any side leaves the "
"other helpless against the drakes, I shall turn against it myself."
msgstr ""
"Eh, amigos, calmaos y escuchad, por favor. Si seguimos divididos así, nos "
"aplastarán uno por uno. Si es la desconfianza lo que os impide uniros, "
"entonces permitidme actuar como mediadora; y si algún bando deja al otro "
"indefenso contra los dracos, yo misma me volveré contra él."

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:227
msgid ""
"Well, under these terms I think I can fight alongside those be... I mean, "
"the trolls."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, bajo estos términos creo que puedo luchar junto a esos ani… quiero "
"decir, los trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:231
msgid ""
"So says I... You are barely a girl, but you speak with intelligence and "
"authority, young Myra."
msgstr ""
"Yo también… Apenas eres una niña, pero hablas con inteligencia y autoridad, "
"joven Myra."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:235
msgid "(blushes slightly) Really...? Well, thanks very much!"
msgstr "(se sonroja ligeramente) ¿De verdad…? ¡Bueno, muchísimas gracias!"

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Onwards then, boys! Let it not be said that dwarves fought less than trolls "
"in this battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Adelante entonces, muchachos! ¡Que no se diga que los enanos lucharon menos "
"que los trolls en esta batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Crush those lizards' skulls, my warriors, so that their screams might be "
"heard in the deepest caves of the dwarves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aplastad los cráneos de esos lagartos, guerreros míos, para que sus gritos "
"se oigan en las cuevas más profundas de los enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:247
msgid ""
"(whispering) Good one! Now the trolls and the dwarves will compete for the "
"highest body count... I quake for the drakes!"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¡Bien hecho! Ahora trolls y enanos competirán por la mayor "
"cantidad de cuerpos… ¡Tiemblo por los dracos!"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:263
msgid ""
"It was a very good battle, young Myra. Without your intervention, those "
"invaders would have probably prevailed."
msgstr ""
"Fue una muy buena batalla, joven Myra. Sin tu intervención, esos invasores "
"probablemente habrían prevalecido."

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:267
msgid ""
"Aye, though I hate to admit it, the troll is right. Daughter of Maat, you "
"paid us dwarves a great service today; I'd like to invite ye to meet King "
"Auroghar, who I'm certain will be pleased to meet ye in person."
msgstr ""
"Sí, aunque me duela admitirlo, el troll tiene razón. Hija de Maat, hoy nos "
"has prestado un gran servicio a los enanos; me gustaría invitarte a conocer "
"al rey Auroghar, que estoy seguro estará encantado de conocerte en persona."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:271
msgid ""
"I deeply appreciate your offer, Commander Aiglur, but I and my companion are "
"in a hurry to reach our city of Hiera'Shirsha, which might be under attack "
"in this very moment."
msgstr ""
"Agradezco profundamente tu oferta, comandante Aiglur, pero mi compañera y yo "
"tenemos prisa por llegar a nuestra ciudad de Hiera’Shirsha, que podría estar "
"bajo ataque en este mismo momento."

#. [message], speaker=Aiglur
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:275
msgid ""
"So I know how we can repay you! The surface paths to that city are certainly "
"at the mercy of the fire lizards, but our caves are still intact; we can "
"take you there through our tunnels in a couple of days."
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces sé cómo podemos pagarte! Los caminos de superficie hacia esa "
"ciudad están seguramente a merced de los lagartos de fuego, pero nuestras "
"cuevas siguen intactas; podemos llevarte allí a través de nuestros túneles "
"en un par de días."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:279
msgid "If that is so, then I'm going with you to your capital."
msgstr "Si es así, entonces voy con vosotros a vuestra capital."

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:283
msgid ""
"I would take you there myself, but our tunnels lead eastwards, far from "
"Hiera'Shirsha."
msgstr ""
"Yo mismo te llevaría, pero nuestros túneles van hacia el este, lejos de "
"Hiera’Shirsha."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:287
msgid ""
"It's fine, Lord Groth; I hope we meet again another day, preferably at the "
"celebration of our victory over the drake invaders."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, lord Groth; espero que nos volvamos a ver otro día, "
"preferiblemente celebrando nuestra victoria sobre los invasores dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:291
msgid "So do us all..."
msgstr "Eso esperamos todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:343
msgid ""
"My people, go back to the caves... Protect the women and the children..."
msgstr "Pueblo mío, volved a las cuevas… Proteged a las mujeres y a los niños…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:347
msgid ""
"We can't defeat this drake troop without the trolls. What will we do now...?"
msgstr ""
"No podemos derrotar a esta tropa de dracos sin los trolls. ¿Qué haremos "
"ahora…?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:361
msgid "Aargh! How could I have fallen to these lizards?!"
msgstr "¡Aargh! ¡¿Cómo he podido caer ante estos lagartos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:365
msgid ""
"We can't defeat this drake troop without the dwarves. What will we do now...?"
msgstr ""
"No podemos derrotar a esta tropa de dracos sin los enanos. ¿Qué haremos "
"ahora…?"

#. [message], speaker=Kegrid
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/02_A_Common_Cause.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Reinforcements at last! Now we will crush these puny natives and take the "
"Windy Mountains from the inside!"
msgstr ""
"¡Refuerzos al fin! ¡Ahora aplastaremos a estos nativos insignificantes y "
"tomaremos las Montañas Ventosas desde dentro!"

#. [scenario], id=03_Monstrous_Help
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:4
msgid "Monstrous Help"
msgstr "Ayuda Monstruosa"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Proceed to the Great Northern Gate, and clear the caves from any possible "
"threat"
msgstr ""
"Avanzar hasta la Gran Puerta Norte y limpiar las cuevas de cualquier posible "
"amenaza"

#. [objective], condition=lose
