#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:460
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:580
msgid "Death of Dvalin"
msgstr "Muerte de Dvalin"

#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:65
msgid "Anitraz"
msgstr "Anitraz"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:117
msgid ""
"Well, we now have just a couple of kilometres to the Great Northern Gate. "
"Once we reach it, you'll see the mountain where Hiera'Shirsha stands, and "
"the path towards it is clear and easy."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ahora solo nos faltan un par de kilómetros hasta la Gran Puerta "
"Norte. Al llegar, veréis la montaña donde se alza Hiera'Shirsha, y el camino "
"hacia ella es claro y fácil."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:121
msgid ""
"It's fortunate that we're close to our home; this trip through the caves is "
"killing me. I was made for strolling around in the fields and woods, not for "
"dwelling in caves..."
msgstr ""
"Qué suerte que estamos cerca de casa; este viaje por las cuevas me está "
"matando. Yo nací para pasear por campos y bosques, no para vivir en cuevas..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:125
msgid ""
"Stop whining, blondie; you shouldn't have come with me if you wanted "
"comfort. Now, let's reach the Great Northern Gate."
msgstr ""
"Deja de quejarte, rubia; no deberías haber venido conmigo si querías "
"comodidad. Ahora, vamos a la Gran Puerta Norte."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:145
msgid ""
"By the way, Dvalin, thanks for offering to show us the way. It's actually "
"kind of nice to find someone who doesn't shun us 'Windsong witches'."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, Dvalin, gracias por ofrecerte a mostrarnos el camino. En "
"realidad es bastante agradable encontrar a alguien que no rechace a las "
"«brujas Hijas del Viento»."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Nah, that's nothing, lass. You know, you're not the first Windsong I meet. "
"When I was but a wee bairn I was saved by Windsong after I got lost in an "
"abandoned system of tunnels. Those were the early days of Krathon's War, "
"mind you, when we were still calling it 'Asuri Crisis'. In fact, your mother "
"was among those Windsong!"
msgstr ""
"Nah, no es nada, muchacha. Sabes, no eres la primera Hija del Viento que "
"conozco. Cuando era apenas un enano pequeño me salvaron unas Hijas del "
"Viento después de perderme en un sistema de túneles abandonado. Eran los "
"primeros días de la Guerra de Krathon, ojo, cuando todavía la llamábamos "
"«Crisis Asuri». ¡De hecho, tu madre estaba entre esas Hijas del Viento!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:153
msgid ""
"And I thought mother only became so famous among the dwarves because of that "
"showdown with Shek'har..."
msgstr ""
"Y yo que pensaba que mamá solo se hizo tan famosa entre los enanos por aquel "
"enfrentamiento con Shek’har…"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:157
msgid ""
"Nay, Lady Maat's done far more than that. I remember her: she was around the "
"same age as you are now. In fact, you look very like her, except your eyes "
"are like emerald and your hair is longer, like an obsidian cascade. But the "
"one I remember most is one of her peers, she with hair like a cascade of "
"ruby; I never saw her again, though, but when I learned of her passing, I "
"shaved my beard in sadness. Eh, that probably sounded very strange to you..."
msgstr ""
"No, la dama Maat hizo mucho más que eso. La recuerdo: tenía más o menos tu "
"edad de ahora. De hecho, te pareces mucho a ella, salvo que tus ojos son "
"como esmeraldas y tu cabello es más largo, como una cascada de obsidiana. "
"Pero la que más recuerdo es una de sus compañeras, la del cabello como "
"cascada de rubí; nunca la volví a ver, pero cuando me enteré de su muerte me "
"rapé la barba de tristeza. Eh, seguramente eso sonó muy raro para ti..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:161
msgid ""
"Not at all: I know that's how you dwarves mourn for those you hold dearest. "
"I know who you're talking about: Deianira the Scarlet Lightning... She was "
"one of mother's best friends, and one of our most popular sisters. We "
"mourned her death for weeks."
msgstr ""
"Para nada: sé que así es como los enanos lloran a quienes más quieren. Sé de "
"quién hablas: Deianira el Relámpago Escarlata… Era una de las mejores amigas "
"de mamá y una de nuestras hermanas más populares. Lloramos su muerte durante "
"semanas."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:165
msgid ""
"A pity indeed... Well, we can talk about the past another time - we have "
"some length of tunnels to cross yet!"
msgstr ""
"Una verdadera lástima... Bueno, podemos hablar del pasado en otro momento, "
"¡todavía nos quedan bastantes túneles por cruzar!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:180
msgid "Depleted mines"
msgstr "Minas agotadas"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:195
msgid "By the beard of Aigathol! What is that thing?"
msgstr "¡Por la barba de Aigathol! ¿Qué es esa cosa?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:199
msgid ""
"By the looks, I think it's a saurian. Oh no, that's not good: saurians are "
"allies of drakes, so if there are saurians here..."
msgstr ""
"Por su aspecto, creo que es un sauriano. Oh no, eso no es bueno: los "
"saurianos son aliados de los dracos, así que si hay saurianos aquí..."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:203
msgid ""
"But damn it, we have no minor, undefended gates in this area, how did they "
"enter our caves? Unless..."
msgstr ""
"¡Pero maldición, no tenemos puertas menores sin defensa en esta zona, cómo "
"entraron a nuestras cuevas! A menos que..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:207
msgid ""
"...they have entered through the Great Northern Gate. And if they did, it's "
"because Hiera'Shirsha... Folks, now we really must hurry. Let's defeat these "
"saurians and retake the northern gate!"
msgstr ""
"...hayan entrado por la Gran Puerta Norte. Y si lo hicieron, es porque "
"Hiera'Shirsha... ¡Gente, ahora sí tenemos que apurarnos! ¡Derrotemos a estos "
"saurianos y retomemos la puerta norte!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:211
msgid ""
"Spoke my very thoughts! Let's introduce these saurian things to our axes, "
"boys!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eso mismo pensaba! ¡Vamos a presentarles a estos bichos saurianos nuestras "
"hachas, muchachos!"

#. [unit], id=Kerx, type=Saurian Flanker
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:229
msgid "Kerx"
msgstr "Kerx"

#. [message], speaker=Kerx
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:245
msgid "Ssomething wrong here?"
msgstr "¿Algún problemass aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Anitraz
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:249
msgid "Reinforcementss at last! There iss a sstrong dwarf force attacking uss!"
msgstr "¡Refuerzoss al fin! ¡Una fuerte fuerzza enana noss está atacando!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:253
msgid "Blast it, there are more of them coming from the outside!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, vienen más desde afuera!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:257
msgid "There are too many of them! What will we do now, Myra?"
msgstr "¡Son demasiados! ¿Qué vamos a hacer ahora, Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:261
msgid "Um, I think... Yes, I must try that..."
msgstr "Eh, creo que... Sí, tengo que intentarlo..."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:265
msgid "Try what?"
msgstr "¿Intentar qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:269
msgid "Just give me a few minutes, and you'll see..."
msgstr "Solo denme unos minutos y lo verán..."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:312
msgid "Aaaahhh, spiders everywhere!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Aaaahhh, arañas por todos lados!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Don't attack them! I have lured and charmed them, they're under my control "
"now."
msgstr ""
"¡No las ataquen! Las he atraído y encantado, ahora están bajo mi control."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:320
msgid "And they're bringing friends, look at all those spiders!"
msgstr "¡Y están trayendo amigas, miren todas esas arañas!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:342
msgid "Och, how do you do that, girl?"
msgstr "¡Och, cómo haces eso, muchacha!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:346
msgid ""
"Just like I communicate with nature's spirits, I can communicate with other "
"animals and make them do my bidding. I'd never tried to lure so many "
"gigantic animals at once before, though."
msgstr ""
"Así como me comunico con los espíritus de la naturaleza, puedo comunicarme "
"con otros animales y hacer que obedezcan mis órdenes. Aunque nunca antes "
"había intentado atraer a tantos animales gigantes de una sola vez."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:350
msgid ""
"But you did a great job, as expected of you! Why was I even caring about "
"being tired when I was alongside you..."
msgstr ""
"¡Pero lo hiciste genial, como era de esperarse de ti! ¿Por qué me preocupaba "
"estar cansada si estaba a tu lado...?"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:354
msgid "(whispering to Myra) The fair-haired one really likes you, uh?"
msgstr "(susurrando a Myra) A la rubia le gustas mucho, ¿eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:358
msgid "Be silent, Dvalin..."
msgstr "Cállate, Dvalin..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:366
msgid "Now, let's go and see whatever is happening outside..."
msgstr "Ahora, vamos a ver qué está pasando afuera..."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:421
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:656
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:290
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:529
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:746
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1462
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:643
msgid "Aaargh! Curse these lizards..."
msgstr "¡Aaargh! ¡Malditos lagartos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/03_Monstrous_Help.cfg:432
msgid ""
"We have taken too much time in these caves! Now, I fear we will leave it "
"only to see our dear city crumbling..."
msgstr ""
"¡Hemos tardado demasiado en estas cuevas! Ahora me temo que saldremos solo "
"para ver nuestra querida ciudad derrumbándose..."

#. [scenario], id=04_Lightning_Strike
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:4
msgid "Lightning Strike"
msgstr "Golpe Relámpago"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:22
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:427
msgid "Hold off the dragon army till the end of turns"
msgstr "Contener al ejército dracónico hasta que acaben los turnos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:34
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:443
msgid "Death of M'lena"
msgstr "Muerte de M’lena"

#. [side], type=Librarian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:66
msgid "M'lena"
msgstr "M’lena"

#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:87
msgid "Mar'Ildian"
msgstr "Mar’Ildian"

#. [side], type=Inferno Drake
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:110
msgid "Kon Garashe"
msgstr "Kon Garashe"

#. [message], speaker=Mar'Ildian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:220
msgid ""
"Burn Hiera'Shirsha, my warriors, burn it to the ground and leave none alive!"
msgstr ""
"¡Quemad Hiera’Shirsha, guerreros míos, reducidla a cenizas y no dejéis a "
"nadie con vida!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Hold your ground, Windsong! Countless times has our Foundation been "
"attacked, and countless times have our foes clashed uselessly against our "
"walls! Our High Ascendant is on her way to help us, and her very sight shall "
"scare away these fire-breathing barbarians!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mantened la posición, Hijas del Viento! ¡Incontables veces han atacado "
"nuestra Fundación y otras tantas se han estrellado inútilmente contra "
"nuestras murallas! ¡Nuestra Gran Ascendente viene en camino a ayudarnos, y "
"su sola presencia ahuyentará a estos bárbaros escupefuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Shura
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Look! Look at the Dwarven Gate! Lady Maat has arrived, and is bringing "
"dwarvish reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad! ¡Mirad la Puerta Enana! ¡Ha llegado la señora Maat, y trae refuerzos "
"enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:234
msgid "No, wait, that's not her... By the elementals, I think it's Myra..."
msgstr "No, espera, no es ella… Por los elementales, creo que es Myra…"

#. [message], speaker=Naomi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:238
msgid "It's not the Ascendant...?"
msgstr "¿No es la Ascendente…?"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:243
msgid ""
"No, but for now let's content ourselves with her daughter; after all, Myra "
"and her elementals are better than another drake battalion."
msgstr ""
"No, pero por ahora contentémonos con su hija; al fin y al cabo, Myra y sus "
"elementales valen más que otro batallón de dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Dvalin, so this is the plan: hurry back to the caves and rally every dwarf "
"warrior you can find. If Hiera'Shirsha falls, the morale of every free "
"people in these realms will be severely weakened. Meanwhile, I shall help "
"our sisters in the Foundation's defence."
msgstr ""
"Dvalin, este es el plan: regresa rápido a las cuevas y reúne a todos los "
"guerreros enanos que encuentres. Si cae Hiera’Shirsha, la moral de todos los "
"pueblos libres de estos reinos quedará muy debilitada. Mientras, yo ayudaré "
"a nuestras hermanas en la defensa de la Fundación."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:251
msgid ""
"Aye, Myra, I'll be back in a blink... Sorry for not being able to help you "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo, Myra, vuelvo en un abrir y cerrar de ojos… Perdona por no poder "
"ayudarte ahora mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:272
msgid "(sobbing) But Myra, they're too many..."
msgstr "(llorando) Pero Myra, son demasiados…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Get a hold of yourself, Veela! It's a good thing there are many of them; "
"thus we'll be able to punish them more. Now, CHARGE!"
msgstr ""
"¡Contrólate, Veela! Que sean muchos es bueno; así podremos castigarlos más. "
"¡Ahora, A CARGAR!"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:301
msgid ""
"Master Assix, I have found the books you sought, including <i>that</i> one."
msgstr ""
"Maestro Assix, he encontrado los libros que buscaba, incluido <i>ese</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:305
msgid ""
"Wonderful! For this I shall reward you above all others! Ah, our foess shall "
"fall before uss one by one with the power this book will give uss!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maravilloso! ¡Por esto te recompensaré por encima de todos los demás! ¡Ah, "
"nuestros enemigos caerán ante nosotros uno a uno con el poder que este libro "
"nos dará!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:310
msgid ""
"Damned sneaky lizards, when did they enter the Library? Myra, kill him "
"before he escapes with those scrolls!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos lagartos sigilosos! ¿Cuándo entraron en la Biblioteca? ¡Myra, "
"mátalo antes de que escape con esos pergaminos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:314
msgid "Damn the scrolls, I will focus on protecting our sisters!"
msgstr "¡Malditos pergaminos! ¡Yo me centro en proteger a nuestras hermanas!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:319
msgid ""
"You don't understand the kind of knowledge contained within our Library! Who "
"knows what kind of secret, destructive lore that lizard has stolen - he "
"could even have stolen the forbidden lore of Ashura the Demon!"
msgstr ""
"¡No entiendes el tipo de conocimiento que guarda nuestra Biblioteca! ¡Quién "
"sabe qué secretos destructivos ha robado ese lagarto… hasta podría haberse "
"llevado el conocimiento prohibido de Ashura el Demonio!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:323
msgid "All right then, I'm going after him..."
msgstr "Está bien, voy tras él…"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:342
msgid ""
"You little witch... I shall not forget your face. You will pay for crossing "
"my path!"
msgstr ""
"Pequeña bruja… No olvidaré tu cara. ¡Pagarás por cruzarte en mi camino!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Then why don't you stay and fight instead of running away, you reptilian "
"COWARD?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces ¿por qué no te quedas a luchar en vez de huir, ¡COBARDE reptiliano?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:357
msgid "Forget about him, Myra, we must go to our sisters' aid!"
msgstr "¡Olvídate de él, Myra, tenemos que ir a ayudar a nuestras hermanas!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:361
msgid ""
"You're right. I just hope Dvalin returns soon, the situation does not bide "
"well for our side..."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón. Solo espero que Dvalin vuelva pronto, la situación no pinta "
"bien para nuestro bando…"

#. [message], speaker=Kon Garashe
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:377
msgid ""
"These humans are resisting for longer than we thought... Mar'Ildian, let's "
"call in the reserves and incinerate these witches once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Estos humanos resisten más de lo que creíamos… ¡Mar’Ildian, llamemos a las "
"reservas y acabemos con estas brujas de una vez por todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:381
msgid "Damn, Dvalin, where are you...?"
msgstr "Maldición, Dvalin, ¿dónde estás…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:406
msgid "About time!"
msgstr "¡Ya era hora!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:410
msgid "I went as fast as I could, but ye know, my legs are a bit short."
msgstr ""
"He venido tan rápido como he podido, pero ya sabes, mis piernas son un poco "
"cortas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:421
msgid "With Dvalin back, Myra may recruit dwarves again."
msgstr "Con Dvalin de vuelta, Myra puede reclutar enanos de nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:505
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:828
msgid "NO!"
msgstr "¡NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Kon Garashe
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:509
msgid "Yes! Behold the Pride of Dragons' Land, Khrakrahs son of Shek'har!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí! ¡Contemplad el Orgullo de la Tierra de los Dragones, Khrakrahs hijo de "
"Shek’har!"

#. [message], speaker=Khrakrahs
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:513
msgid ""
"I have been given the honour of finishing the famous Hiera'Shirsha, the "
"Jewel of the Continent! Advance, Children of Morogor, and consume our foes "
"in your flames!"
msgstr ""
"¡Se me ha concedido el honor de acabar con la famosa Hiera’Shirsha, la Joya "
"del Continente! ¡Adelante, Hijos de Morogor, y consumid a nuestros enemigos "
"en vuestras llamas!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:517
msgid ""
"M'lena, it's over now... We must save as many of our sisters as we can, and "
"one day we may be able to rebuild our order..."
msgstr ""
"M’lena, se acabó… Tenemos que salvar a todas nuestras hermanas que podamos, "
"y algún día quizá podamos reconstruir nuestra orden…"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:522
msgid ""
"(crying) I have dedicated my whole life to this Foundation... As did so many "
"generations of good women, collecting the wisdom of Irdya and keeping it "
"away from wrong hands... Only for all our work to be turned to ashes by "
"these merciless monsters..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) He dedicado toda mi vida a esta Fundación… Como tantas "
"generaciones de buenas mujeres, recogiendo la sabiduría de Irdya y "
"manteniéndola lejos de malas manos… ¡Solo para que todo nuestro trabajo se "
"vuelva cenizas por culpa de estos monstruos sin piedad…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Do you think I don't know how you feel? This place has been my only true "
"home, the place where I found happiness again after my blood mother's "
"death... It is lost now, but our sisters may yet live, so we must withdraw "
"into the tunnels, where the dwarves shall cover us!"
msgstr ""
"¿Crees que no sé cómo te sientes? Este lugar ha sido mi único hogar de "
"verdad, donde volví a encontrar la felicidad después de la muerte de mi "
"madre de sangre… Ahora está perdido, pero nuestras hermanas aún pueden "
"vivir, ¡así que debemos retirarnos a los túneles, donde los enanos nos "
"cubrirán!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:531
msgid ""
"You speak wisdom, like your mother... It is well, then: I charge you with "
"leading the younger Windsong out of our crumbling Foundation; I and the "
"eldest amongst us shall delay the enemy as much as we can."
msgstr ""
"Hablas con sabiduría, como tu madre… Está bien, entonces: te encargo que "
"guíes a las Hijas del Viento más jóvenes fuera de nuestra Fundación que se "
"derrumba; las mayores y yo retrasaremos al enemigo todo lo que podamos."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:535
msgid "M'lena...!"
msgstr "¡M’lena…!"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:540
msgid "Go before it's too late!"
msgstr "¡Vete antes de que sea demasiado tarde!"

#. [unit], id=Thalia, type=Oathkeeper
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:551
msgid "Thalia"
msgstr "Thalia"

#. [message], speaker=Thalia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Lady M'lena, are you sure Myra will be able to lead our sisters through this "
"mayhem all by herself? She's powerful, but is still young and brash."
msgstr ""
"Señora M’lena, ¿está segura de que Myra podrá guiar a nuestras hermanas por "
"este caos ella sola? Es poderosa, pero sigue siendo joven e impulsiva."

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:567
msgid ""
"You spoke my worries, Thalia... I too am uncertain about whether our young "
"friend will be able to take our students to safety. I must stay here and buy "
"them some time; but you, Thalia, you should go with them, and protect Myra "
"for me."
msgstr ""
"Has dicho mis preocupaciones, Thalia… Yo también dudo de que nuestra joven "
"amiga pueda llevar a las alumnas a salvo. Debo quedarme aquí y ganarles algo "
"de tiempo; pero tú, Thalia, deberías ir con ellas y proteger a Myra por mí."

#. [message], speaker=Thalia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:571
msgid ""
"I... I understand. I will make sure she and our sisters manage to reach the "
"Meadows in safety, even if it costs me my life."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Lo entiendo. Me aseguraré de que ella y nuestras hermanas lleguen a "
"salvo a los Prados, aunque me cueste la vida."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:587
msgid "Farewell, my home..."
msgstr "Adiós, mi hogar…"

#. [message], speaker=M'lena
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/04_Lightning_Strike.cfg:642
msgid "I fall, and so does Hiera'Shirsha..."
msgstr "Caigo yo, y cae Hiera’Shirsha…"

