msgid "Grenn Ohn"
msgstr "Grenn Ohn"

#. [side], type=Elvish Marshal
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:97
msgid "Galyon"
msgstr "Galyon"

#. [side], type=Elvish Marshal
#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:102
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:116
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:136
msgid "Varanyan Elves"
msgstr "Elfos Varanyan"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:138
msgid "Stand strong, elves, and we shall vanquish these tree-killers!"
msgstr "¡Manteneos firmes, elfos, y venceremos a estos asesinos de árboles!"

#. [message], speaker=Grenn Ohn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:142
msgid ""
"Burn everything, drakes! Without their precious forests, these skinny "
"weaklings will be helpless!"
msgstr ""
"¡Quemadlo todo, dracos! ¡Sin sus preciosos bosques, estos flacuchos "
"debiluchos estarán indefensos!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:146
msgid "Marshal, look! There come the dwarves and the Windsong!"
msgstr "¡Mariscal, mirad! ¡Ahí vienen los enanos y las Hijas del Viento!"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:150
msgid "Oh no, don't tell they have decided to harass us just now...!"
msgstr "¡Oh no, no me digáis que han decidido molestarnos justo ahora…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Greetings, elves. I could give you a speech on why we're here and where "
"we're going, but I think we have more urgent matters at hand, don't you "
"agree?"
msgstr ""
"Saludos, elfos. Podría daros un discurso sobre por qué estamos aquí y adónde "
"vamos, pero creo que tenemos asuntos más urgentes entre manos, ¿no creéis?"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:158
msgid ""
"Well... Although it's known to us that neither dwarves nor Windsong are much "
"trustworthy, I deem it better now to leave our differences aside to face a "
"common enemy, like we did in the war against Krathon. So yes, newcomers, "
"your aid will be very appreciated."
msgstr ""
"Bueno… Aunque sabemos que ni los enanos ni las Hijas del Viento son muy de "
"fiar, creo que ahora es mejor dejar nuestras diferencias a un lado para "
"enfrentar a un enemigo común, como hicimos en la guerra contra Krathon. Así "
"que sí, recién llegados, vuestra ayuda será muy apreciada."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Hrumph! Darn elves, acting all high and mighty even when having their asses "
"handed on a plate..."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Malditos elfos, actuando como si fueran superiores incluso cuando "
"les están dando una paliza…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:166
msgid "(snickers)"
msgstr "(risitas)"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:174
msgid ""
"I thank you for your aid, friends. Until your arrival, I had feared for the "
"worst."
msgstr ""
"Os agradezco vuestra ayuda, amigos. Hasta vuestra llegada, había temido lo "
"peor."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:178
msgid "You must be the daughter of the High Ascendant, am I correct?"
msgstr "¿Tú debes ser la hija de la Gran Ascendente, verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:182
msgid "None other!"
msgstr "¡Ninguna otra!"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:186
msgid ""
"I think I must retract what I said earlier about the Windsong and the "
"dwarves... Hiera'Shirsha has remembered its old allies then?"
msgstr ""
"Creo que debo retractarme de lo que dije antes sobre las Hijas del Viento y "
"los enanos… Entonces Hiera’Shirsha ha recordado a sus antiguos aliados?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:190
msgid ""
"Not really... We're just refugees seeking protection with the Aragwaithi. "
"Hiera'Shirsha has fallen."
msgstr ""
"No realmente… Solo somos refugiados buscando protección con los aragwaithi. "
"Hiera’Shirsha ha caído."

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:194
msgid ""
"What? But... No, it cannot be! Was Lady Maat herself unable to hold off the "
"dragon army?"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Qué?! Pero… ¡No, no puede ser! ¿Acaso lady Maat en persona no pudo "
"contener al ejército de dragones?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:198
msgid ""
"My mother's still away in her wanderings. Hiera'Shirsha was being guided by "
"the Librarian M'lena, and we were managing to hold off the invaders, until a "
"huge dragon called Khrakrahs appeared with another huge army, and we had to "
"flee."
msgstr ""
"Mi madre aún está lejos en sus viajes. Hiera’Shirsha estaba siendo guiada "
"por la Bibliotecaria M’lena y conseguimos contener a los invasores, hasta "
"que apareció un enorme dragón llamado Khrakrahs con otro enorme ejército y "
"tuvimos que huir."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:202
msgid ""
"No, not Khrakrahs! He is his father Shek'har's second-in-command; if he has "
"come here himself, then his father will soon follow. I think my mission to "
"Garet-Desh has just become more urgent, marshal."
msgstr ""
"¡No, Khrakrahs no! Es el segundo al mando de su padre Shek’har; si él mismo "
"ha venido aquí, entonces su padre lo seguirá pronto. Creo que mi misión a "
"Garet-Desh se ha vuelto más urgente, mariscal."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:206
msgid "Your mission?"
msgstr "¿Tu misión?"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Lady Alenya is a princess of Lintanir in the distant west. She was "
"originally to ask for Lady Maat's help, for the dragons have launched a "
"massive attack on all the western nations - be it elf, dwarf or troll."
msgstr ""
"Lady Alenya es una princesa de Lintanir en el lejano oeste. Originalmente "
"venía a pedir ayuda a lady Maat, porque los dragones han lanzado un ataque "
"masivo a todas las naciones occidentales —sean elfos, enanos o trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:214
msgid ""
"However, as I travelled to this region, I saw drakes as well as saurians "
"heading east as well. It seems that the Dragons' Land has decided to wage "
"war on all peoples of the continent."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, mientras viajaba a esta región, vi dracos y también saurios "
"dirigiéndose al este. Parece que la Tierra de los Dragones ha decidido hacer "
"la guerra a todos los pueblos del continente."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:218
msgid ""
"But... But what if all the humans, dwarves, elves and trolls unite against "
"them? If we do, I'm sure we could defeat the dragons!"
msgstr ""
"Pero… ¡Pero qué pasa si todos los humanos, enanos, elfos y trolls se unen "
"contra ellos! ¡Si lo hacemos, estoy segura de que podríamos derrotar a los "
"dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:222
msgid ""
"That's what my father intended: to speak with High King Abhai and forge an "
"alliance between the Aragwaithi and Lins-Elens itself. If we do, the elves "
"from other far western forests, such as Wesmere and Aethen, will follow us."
msgstr ""
"Eso es lo que pretendía mi padre: hablar con el Alto Rey Abhai y forjar una "
"alianza entre los aragwaithi y el propio Lins-Elens. Si lo logramos, los "
"elfos de otros bosques lejanos del oeste, como Wesmere y Edén, nos seguirán."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:226
msgid "So we must not tarry here any longer. Let's hurry to Garet-Desh!"
msgstr "¡Entonces no podemos demorarnos más aquí! ¡Corramos a Garet-Desh!"

#. [message], speaker=Galyon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:230
msgid ""
"You go and escort Alenya; I shall stay here and block the advance of any "
"other drake battalion that comes. This forest has been our home for ages, "
"and we shall not give it up without a bloody fight."
msgstr ""
"Vosotros id y escoltad a Alenya; yo me quedaré aquí y detendré el avance de "
"cualquier otro batallón de dracos que venga. Este bosque ha sido nuestro "
"hogar durante eras y no lo abandonaremos sin una lucha sangrienta."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:234
msgid "(whispering) For an elf, he's got quite the guts..."
msgstr "(susurrando) Para ser un elfo, tiene agallas…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:238
msgid "So be it. I wish you the best of luck."
msgstr "Que así sea. Te deseo la mejor de las suertes."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:304
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:543
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:458
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:874
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1083
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:302
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:704
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1420
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:573
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:263
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:962
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:517
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:804
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:802
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/20_Ring_Of_Fire.cfg:707
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:888
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/23_Holy_Fire.cfg:434
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:922
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:887
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:587
msgid "Alas, I shall never see my dear Lintanir again..."
msgstr "Ay, nunca volveré a ver mi querido Lintanir…"

#. [message], speaker=Grenn Ohn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/05_Forest_Ablaze.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Ha! Look boys, Krahkrahs has completed Hiera'Shirsha's destruction, and now "
"heads towards the Aragwaithi Meadows through this valley - let's cook him "
"some elvish meal to restore his strength!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Mirad, muchachos, Krahkrahs ha completado la destrucción de "
"Hiera’Shirsha y ahora se dirige a los Prados Aragwaithi a través de este "
"valle —preparémosle una comida élfica para que recupere fuerzas!"

#. [scenario], id=06_Council_With_The_King
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:4
msgid "Council With The King: The Throne Room"
msgstr "Consejo con el Rey: La Sala del Trono"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Aragwaith Ancient Banner
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:31
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:42
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:51
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:30
msgid "Garet-Desh"
msgstr "Garet-Desh"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Ancient Banner
#. [unit], id=Aracyn, type=Aragwaith Ancient Banner
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:37
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:94
msgid "Lord Aracyn"
msgstr "Señor Aracyn"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Aragwaith Shield Guard
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:51
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:55
msgid "Valon"
msgstr "Valon"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Swordsmaster
#. [unit], id=Vercyn, type=Aragwaith Swordsmaster
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:57
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:92
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:61
msgid "King Vercyn"
msgstr "Rey Vercyn"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Swordsmaster
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:62
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:66
msgid "Doldesh"
msgstr "Doldesh"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:120
msgid "Three young women and a dwarf, breezing past my finest guards..."
msgstr ""
"Tres jóvenes y un enano entrando como una brisa por delante de mis mejores "
"guardias…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:124
msgid "Myra! You... Thank the Gods of Light, you're alive!"
msgstr "¡Myra! Tú… ¡Gracias a los Dioses de la Luz, estás viva!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:128
msgid ""
"Yes, of course I am... I just took a detour, hasn't Headmistress Lashimi "
"told you?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, claro que sí… Solo tomé un rodeo, ¿no te lo contó la directora Lashimi?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Lashimi... Oh dear, you don't know yet...? She and the other students of "
"your haven were ambushed by saurians and drakes near Esthiel. Lord Thelian's "
"troops went to their aid, but it was already too late..."
msgstr ""
"Lashimi… Ay, querida, aún no lo sabes…? Ella y las demás alumnas de vuestro "
"refugio fueron emboscadas por saurios y dracos cerca de Esthiel. Las tropas "
"de lord Thelian fueron en su ayuda, pero ya era demasiado tarde…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:136
msgid "Oh, no... No, no, no, no!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no… No, no, no, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:140
msgid "How did <i>you</i> manage to cross the Windy Mountains unscathed?"
msgstr "¿Cómo <i>tú</i> lograste cruzar las Montañas Ventosas ilesa?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:144
msgid ""
"We... Majesty, we went underground, guided by the dwarves, whom we helped "
"defeat a drake vanguard. This is Dvalin, son of King Auroghar, who guided us."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros… Majestad, fuimos por debajo de la tierra, guiados por los enanos, "
"a los que ayudamos a derrotar una vanguardia de dracos. Este es Dvalin, hijo "
"del rey Auroghar, que nos guió."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:148
msgid ""
"Majesty, I know my presence here has not been requested, but I ask you to "
"let me stay, to serve as my father's representative."
msgstr ""
"Majestad, sé que no se ha solicitado mi presencia aquí, pero pido que me "
"permitáis quedarme, para servir como representante de mi padre."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:152
msgid ""
"In that case, you are forgiven for storming into the throne room; we all "
"need to orchestrate well our moves, or else we shall fall separately."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, estás perdonado por irrumpir en la sala del trono; todos "
"necesitamos coordinar bien nuestros movimientos, o caeremos por separado."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:156
msgid "Myra, please tell me: is it true about Hiera'Shirsha...?"
msgstr "Myra, por favor dime: ¿es cierto lo de Hiera’Shirsha…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:160
msgid ""
"Yes... We arrived there as the Foundation was under siege. We might... we "
"<i>might</i> have beaten them... Until another host led by the dragon "
"Khrakrahs appeared. Librarian M'lena stayed behind with the other elders, to "
"hold the enemies while I and the younger ones fled into the tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Sí… Llegamos allí cuando la Fundación estaba sitiada. Podríamos… "
"<i>podríamos</i> haberlos vencido… Hasta que apareció otro ejército liderado "
"por el dragón Khrakrahs. La bibliotecaria M’lena se quedó atrás con los "
"ancianos, para contener a los enemigos mientras yo y las más jóvenes huíamos "
"por los túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:164
msgid "No...!"
msgstr "¡No…!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:168
msgid "I... I'm sorry to hear that, Maat..."
msgstr "Yo… Lo siento mucho, Maat…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:172
msgid ""
"If mighty Hiera'Shirsha has fallen so early, will we stand any chance "
"against the dragons? And why are they attacking us now? I thought Lord "
"Agniballi was friendly to us!"
msgstr ""
"Si la poderosa Hiera’Shirsha ha caído tan pronto, ¿tendremos alguna "
"posibilidad contra los dragones? ¿Y por qué nos atacan ahora? ¡Pensaba que "
"lord Agniballi era amigo nuestro!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:176
msgid ""
"(recomposing) He is, as he has been for aeons, and for this reason I refuse "
"to believe he has turned against us! No, there is someone else behind it: if "
"Krahkrahs is here, then I believe Agniballi's right-hand, Shek'har, is the "
"one behind all this. He certainly has reasons to desire our destruction, but "
"the question is: how has he managed to launch so many armies without his "
"master's knowledge...?"
msgstr ""
"(recomponiéndose) Lo es, como lo ha sido durante eones, y por eso me niego a "
"creer que se haya vuelto en contra nuestra. No, hay alguien más detrás: si "
"Khrakrahs está aquí, entonces creo que la mano derecha de Agniballi, "
"Shek’har, es quien está detrás de todo esto. Sin duda tiene motivos para "
"desear nuestra destrucción, pero la pregunta es: ¿cómo ha logrado lanzar "
"tantos ejércitos sin que su amo lo sepa…?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:180
msgid ""
"After all the tales I have heard of your power, High Ascendant, I assumed "
"you would have the answer by now."
msgstr ""
"Tras todas las historias que he oído sobre tu poder, Gran Ascendente, supuse "
"que ya tendrías la respuesta."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:184
msgid "And you watch out how you talk to my mother, elf!"
msgstr "¡Y tú cuida cómo le hablas a mi madre, elfa!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:188
msgid ""
"Peace, ladies. As for you, elf lady, shall we assume you come on behalf of "
"Lord Thelian?"
msgstr ""
"Paz, señoras. En cuanto a ti, dama elfa, ¿debemos suponer que vienes en "
"nombre de lord Thelian?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:192
msgid ""
"Apologies, Lord Abhai. I am Alenya, daughter of Elliadan, Lord of Lintanir "
"Forest in the Far West, where we too are facing the dragons' offensive."
msgstr ""
"Disculpas, lord Abhai. Soy Alenya, hija de Elliadan, Señor del Bosque "
"Lintanir en el Lejano Oeste, donde también estamos sufriendo la ofensiva de "
"los dragones."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:196
msgid ""
"So the dragons are attacking the west <i>and</i> the heart of the Great "
"Continent?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces los dragones están atacando tanto al oeste <i>y</i> al corazón del "
"Gran Continente?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:200
msgid ""
"Exactly. I was sent here by the King-in-the-Woods himself to speak with the "
"Varanyan Elves in the Windy Mountains, as well as you Aragwaithi and whoever "
"else that's friendly, to join forces with the western elves. Only then, he "
"says, we'll be able to withstand our common foes."
msgstr ""
"Exacto. El mismo Rey del Bosque me envió aquí para hablar con los elfos "
"varanios de las Montañas Ventosas, así como con vosotros los aragwaithi y "
"con cualquiera más que sea amistoso, para unir fuerzas con los elfos del "
"oeste. Solo así, dice, podremos resistir a nuestros enemigos comunes."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:204
msgid ""
"The King-in-the-Woods speaks wisdom, princess, and know that I would ally "
"with him, but I fear you won't be able to deliver him my message; the roads "
"to the west must be too dangerous by now."
msgstr ""
"El Rey del Bosque habla con sabiduría, princesa, y sabed que me aliaría con "
"él, pero me temo que no podrás llevarle mi mensaje; los caminos al oeste "
"deben ser demasiado peligrosos ya."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:208
msgid ""
"Indeed, we hadn't expected the dragons to come east so soon... But I can "
"send him a message through a messenger gryphon."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, no esperábamos que los dragones llegaran al este tan pronto… Pero "
"puedo enviarle un mensaje a través de un grifo mensajero."

#. [message], speaker=King Vercyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:212
msgid ""
"It is well, but Lady Maat, with all due respect, you still haven't answered "
"the elf princess' question. How come you haven't seen the dragon attack?"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, pero lady Maat, con todos mis respetos, aún no has respondido a "
"la pregunta de la princesa elfa. ¿Cómo es que no viste el ataque de los "
"dragones?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:216
msgid ""
"I... I still don't know. It has never happened to me before, but I think... "
"I think that my foresight has been blocked. How I cannot say, but whoever "
"has achieved that must be powerful..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Aún no lo sé. Nunca me había pasado antes, pero creo… creo que mi "
"previsión ha sido bloqueada. No sé cómo, pero quien lo haya conseguido debe "
"ser poderoso…"

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:220
msgid "Someone mightier than you? Is that even possible?"
msgstr "¿Alguien más poderoso que tú? ¿Eso es siquiera posible?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:225
msgid ""
"(stung) Despite the epithets others have given me, I <i>am</i> only a mortal."
msgstr ""
"(ofendida) A pesar de los epítetos que otros me han dado, yo <i>solo</i> soy "
"una mortal."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Let it be clear, friends, that Lady Maat, in spite of her troubled vision, "
"noticed some danger was looming. It was following her warning that we "
"positioned sentries all around our Meadows, which will certainly protect us, "
"at least temporarily."
msgstr ""
"Quede claro, amigos, que lady Maat, a pesar de su visión perturbada, sí notó "
"que se avecinaba peligro. Gracias a su advertencia colocamos centinelas por "
"todos nuestros Prados, lo que sin duda nos protegerá, al menos temporalmente."

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:234
msgid "So what do we do now?"
msgstr "¿Entonces qué hacemos ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:238
msgid ""
"We must strengthen the Meadows' defences, and then hurry to the aid of our "
"neighbours in the mountains; the dwarves and the trolls should be able to "
"protect their caves for a good while, but the elves are completely exposed "
"to the drakes. Dvalin, I ask you to send word to your father that he may "
"count on the Aragwaithi; Maat, it will be my honour to shelter the surviving "
"Windsong in my own city, should you wish. Any other way I can help you, "
"simply say the word. You know you may always count on me."
msgstr ""
"Debemos reforzar las defensas de los Prados y luego acudir en ayuda de "
"nuestros vecinos de las montañas; los enanos y los trolls deberían poder "
"proteger sus cuevas durante un tiempo, pero los elfos están completamente "
"expuestos a los dracos. Dvalin, te pido que envíes recado a tu padre de que "
"puede contar con los aragwaithi; Maat, será un honor para mí acoger a las "
"Hijas del Viento supervivientes en mi propia ciudad, si así lo deseas. "
"Cualquier otra forma en que pueda ayudarte, solo di la palabra. Sabes que "
"siempre puedes contar conmigo."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King.cfg:242
msgid "Thank you, my friend..."
msgstr "Gracias, amigo mío…"

#. [scenario], id=06B_Council_With_The_King
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:4
msgid "Council With The King: At the Palace Garden"
msgstr "Consejo con el Rey: En el Jardín del Palacio"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:24
msgid "Move Myra to the north exit of the Gardens (8,1)"
msgstr "Lleva a Myra a la salida norte de los Jardines (8,1)"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:29
msgid "Speak with everyone else at the Gardens"
msgstr "Habla con todos los demás en los Jardines"

#. [unit], id=Thrandyl, type=Aragwaith Silver Shield
#. [side], type=Aragwaith Silver Shield
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:82
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:83
msgid "King Thrandyl"
msgstr "Rey Thrandyl"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:117
msgid ""
"*I haven't seen mother like this ever since aunt Deni died... No, I'm wrong; "
"she's even worse now. I must talk with her..."
msgstr ""
"*Nunca había visto a madre así desde que murió la tía Deni... No, me "
"equivoco; ahora está peor. Tengo que hablar con ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#. [part]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:124
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/utils/intros.cfg:206
msgid "Mother..."
msgstr "Madre..."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:128
msgid ""
"I told Dashien that, but I did lower my guard... After Krathon's War, I "
"didn't think it even possible for my foresight to fail, let alone fail this "
"much... And now look at what my failure has caused..."
msgstr ""
"Se lo advertí a Dashien, pero bajé la guardia... Después de la Guerra de "
"Krathon no creía posible que mi previsión fallara, y menos que fallara "
"tanto... Y ahora mirad lo que mi fracaso ha provocado..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:132
msgid "Mother, listen..."
msgstr "Madre, escucha..."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:136
msgid ""
"After all we fought, all we suffered and sacrificed to defend our "
"Foundation, I let it... (chuckles) Maat the Great... I should be Maat the "
"Failure, the Ascendant who let the last Foundation of the Windsong be "
"destroyed...!"
msgstr ""
"Después de todo lo que luchamos, todo lo que sufrimos y sacrificamos para "
"defender nuestra Fundación, yo la dejé... (ríe con amargura) Maat la "
"Grande... Debería llamarme Maat la Fracaso, la Ascendente que permitió que "
"la última Fundación de las Hijas del Viento fuera destruida...!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:140
msgid "<i>Maat strikes a tree in frustration</i>"
msgstr "<i>Maat golpea un árbol con frustración</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:144
msgid ""
"Mother, please stop blaming yourself! No one will ever see you as a failure-"
msgstr ""
"¡Madre, por favor deja de culparte! ¡Nadie te verá nunca como un fracaso-!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:148
msgid "(fighting tears) Perhaps they should..."
msgstr "(conteniendo las lágrimas) Tal vez deberían..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:152
msgid ""
"Is it because Hiera'Shirsha fell? An old pile of stones with sentimental "
"value; that's all it was, or so aunt Deni taught us! And <i>this</i> is what "
"you taught me: the Windsong are the wisdom we've gathered across the ages, "
"and the bonds between us and our sisters. Well, most of our sisters are "
"still alive, and we've salvaged most of our library, so I say our Order "
"stands strong. As for the pile of stones... we can put them back up once "
"we're done with this threat - but first we must fight, and in order to fight "
"we must not allow ourselves to lose hope!"
msgstr ""
"¿Es porque Hiera'Shirsha cayó? ¡Un viejo montón de piedras con valor "
"sentimental; eso era todo, o eso nos enseñó la tía Deni! Y <i>esto</i> es lo "
"que tú me enseñaste: las Hijas del Viento somos la sabiduría que hemos "
"acumulado a lo largo de las eras, y los lazos entre nosotras y nuestras "
"hermanas. ¡Pues la mayoría de nuestras hermanas siguen vivas, y salvamos "
"casi toda nuestra biblioteca, así que digo que nuestra Orden sigue fuerte! "
"En cuanto al montón de piedras... podemos volver a levantarlas cuando "
"acabemos con esta amenaza, ¡pero primero hay que luchar, y para luchar no "
"hay que mantener la esperanza!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:156
msgid ""
"(hugging her tight) Ah, Myra, how I envy your real mother for birthing such "
"a wonderful girl... You are right; self-pity is unbecoming of me, and a "
"waste of time as well. Now, you must rest and visit the healers; the last "
"days must have been extremely harsh for you..."
msgstr ""
"(abrazándola fuerte) Ay, Myra, cómo envidio a tu verdadera madre por haber "
"traído al mundo a una chica tan maravillosa... Tienes razón; la "
"autocompasión no me sienta bien, y además es una pérdida de tiempo. Ahora "
"debes descansar y visitar a los sanadores; estos últimos días debieron ser "
"muy duros para ti..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:160
msgid ""
"Don't worry about me, I'm fine... or as fine as the situation allows anyway."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes por mí, estoy bien... o todo lo bien que la situación "
"permite."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:164
msgid ""
"Still, go rest for a while, you deserve it. I, by my turn, must arrange for "
"our sisters' arrival and living in Garet-Desh."
msgstr ""
"Aún así, ve a descansar un rato, te lo mereces. Yo, mientras, debo organizar "
"la llegada y el alojamiento de nuestras hermanas en Garet-Desh."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:174
msgid ""
"*Not sure I really managed to cheer her up, even if just a little... If only "
"aunt Deni was here, she always knew how to make mother smile... Now, where's "
"that blondie? Can't let her get herself into a mess, not when she's kind of "
"under my responsibility...*"
msgstr ""
"*No estoy segura de haber logrado animarla, aunque sea un poco... Si al "
"menos estuviera aquí la tía Deni, ella siempre sabía cómo hacer sonreír a "
"madre... Ahora, ¿dónde está esa rubia? No puedo permitir que se meta en "
"líos, no cuando está más o menos bajo mi responsabilidad...*"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:190
msgid "Lord Vercyn."
msgstr "Señor Vercyn."

#. [message], speaker=Vercyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Ah, the High Ascendant's daughter. Much have I heard about you, both from "
"herself and from Lord Abhai. I was under the impression that you hail from a "
"village under Doldesh's protection?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, la hija de la Gran Ascendente. Mucho he oído sobre ti, tanto de ella "
"como de lord Abhai. Tenía entendido que provienes de una aldea bajo la "
"protección de Doldesh?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:198
msgid ""
"*Careful, Myra, you can't just treat a king like you would anyone else...* "
"You heard it right, lord. My mother was a former lancer in the armies of "
"Doldesh, forced to retire due to severe injuries during a raid against the "
"Hannuks."
msgstr ""
"*Cuidado, Myra, no puedes tratar a un rey como si fuera cualquiera...* "
"Escuchó bien, señor. Mi madre fue lancera en los ejércitos de Doldesh, "
"obligada a retirarse por heridas graves durante una incursión contra los "
"Hannuk."

#. [message], speaker=Vercyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:202
msgid ""
"It is a source of pride for me, as King of Doldesh, that the daughter of the "
"great Maat is herself a Doldeshian! I must apologise, though, for old age "
"may have troubled my hearing. You said your <i>mother</i> was a lancer in my "
"armies? 'Tis true our women ride as well as us, but, given your clearly "
"mixed heritage, I assumed-"
msgstr ""
"¡Es un orgullo para mí, como Rey de Doldesh, que la hija de la gran Maat sea "
"doldeshiana! Debo disculparme, sin embargo, pues la edad quizá haya afectado "
"mi oído. ¿Dijiste que tu <i>madre</i> fue lancera en mis ejércitos? Es "
"cierto que nuestras mujeres cabalgan tan bien como nosotros, pero, dada tu "
"evidente herencia mixta, yo asumí-"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Aragwaithi as my mother was, she seems to have found love with a man of the "
"Hannuk Steppes. Does that surprise you... my lord?"
msgstr ""
"Aragwaithi de pura cepa como era mi madre, parece que encontró el amor con "
"un hombre de las Estepas Hannuk. ¿Le sorprende... mi señor?"

#. [message], speaker=Vercyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Oh...! Well, I certainly suggested nothing harmful to her honour, and I "
"apologise if such was how I sounded. I must leave now, young Myra, but know "
"that Doldesh always has a place for its sons and daughters!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh...! Bueno, desde luego no quise insinuar nada que dañara su honor, y me "
"disculpo si sonó así. Debo irme ya, joven Myra, pero sabe que Doldesh "
"siempre tiene un lugar para sus hijos e hijas!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:214
msgid ""
"May the Winds carry you safely to fair Doldesh, Lord Vercyn. *and may they "
"turn into a gale and sweep that village off the map too...*"
msgstr ""
"Que los Vientos lo lleven a salvo a la hermosa Doldesh, señor Vercyn. *y que "
"se conviertan en vendaval y arrasen también esa aldea del mapa...*"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:235
msgid ""
"And so we meet, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha. I am Crown Prince Varthan, son of "
"High King Abhai III. I had no such chance earlier, given your... stormy "
"entrance... but allow me to properly greet you into our palace."
msgstr ""
"Así que nos conocemos, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha. Soy el príncipe heredero "
"Varthan, hijo del rey supremo Abhai III. No tuve oportunidad antes, dada "
"tu... tormentosa entrada... pero permíteme darte la bienvenida como es "
"debido a nuestro palacio."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Thank you, prince. I see you've heard of me; I've heard about you as well."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, príncipe. Veo que ha oído hablar de mí; yo también he oído de usted."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:243
msgid ""
"(smirking) Would it be presumptuous of me, to hope what you've heard was "
"flattering?"
msgstr "(sonriendo) ¿Sería presuntuoso esperar que lo que oyó fuera halagador?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Well, our parents did travel and fight side by side once, seems natural that "
"mother would speak much of your father... of you she spoke less, I'm afraid. "
"But she did speak well of you, especially given the circumstances..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, nuestros padres viajaron y lucharon juntos una vez, es natural que "
"madre hablara mucho de su padre... de usted habló menos, me temo. Pero habló "
"bien de usted, sobre todo dadas las circunstancias..."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:251
msgid "Circumstances?"
msgstr "¿Circunstancias?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:255
msgid ""
"(feigning abashment) Oh, silly me, I spoke too much...! Forgive me, prince, "
"I must refrain from continuing."
msgstr ""
"(fingiendo vergüenza) ¡Ay, qué tonta, hablé de más...! Perdóneme, príncipe, "
"debo abstenerme de continuar."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:259
msgid ""
"You tease me, Myra. Will I have to offer you our best rooms so you enlighten "
"this mystery?"
msgstr ""
"Me tomas el pelo, Myra. ¿Tendré que ofrecerte nuestras mejores habitaciones "
"para que aclares este misterio?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:263
msgid ""
"It's just that my mother and your father... Well, they seemed pretty close "
"to each other, back in their adventuring days..."
msgstr ""
"Es que mi madre y su padre... Bueno, parecían estar bastante unidos en sus "
"días de aventuras..."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:267
msgid ""
"(puzzled) Was that what she said? Father never mentioned anything of the "
"sort..."
msgstr "(confundido) ¿Eso dijo ella? Padre nunca mencionó nada parecido..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:271
msgid ""
"Oh, she never spoke of him like <i>that</i>. Such piece of history I learned "
"from aunt Deni... You know, Deianira the Scarlet Lightning, who also "
"travelled alongside your father. What do you know, Prince Varthan, we could "
"have been brother and sister!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, ella nunca habló de él <i>así</i> de él! Esa parte de la historia la "
"aprendí de la tía Deni... Ya sabes, Deianira el Relámpago Escarlata, que "
"también viajó con su padre. ¡Quién sabe, príncipe Varthan, podríamos haber "
"sido hermanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:275
msgid ""
"(even more puzzled) I... well, I... must leave now. Enjoy your stay, Myra..."
msgstr ""
"(aún más confundido) Yo... bueno... debo irme. Que disfrutes tu estancia, "
"Myra..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:285
msgid "(giggling) *Oopsie...*"
msgstr "(riendo bajito) *Ups...*"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:301
msgid "Your Majesty."
msgstr "Majestad."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:305
msgid ""
"(smiling) You need not bow to me, young Myra; your mother is my dearest "
"friend, and so you shall be mine as well."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No hace falta que me hagas reverencia, joven Myra; tu madre es "
"mi amiga más querida, y tú también lo serás para mí."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:309
msgid ""
"In that case, maybe it won't be too impudent to say I wish I could make my "
"own friendships among the Lords of the East? King Auroghar said the exact "
"same thing; I know mother casts <i>some</i> shadow, but still..."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, tal vez no sea demasiado atrevido decir que me gustaría hacer "
"mis propias amistades entre los Señores del Este? El rey Auroghar dijo "
"exactamente lo mismo; sé que madre proyecta <i>algo</i> de sombra, pero aun "
"así..."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:313
msgid ""
"(chuckling) I can relate, to a point... (in a more serious tone) Myra, if "
"you would tell me... How fares your mother? I did not wish to intrude in her "
"pain, but part of me says she shouldn't be alone in this moment..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Puedo entenderlo, hasta cierto punto... (en tono más serio) Myra, "
"si pudieras decirme... ¿Cómo está tu madre? No quería inmiscuirme en su "
"dolor, pero algo me dice que no debería estar sola en este momento..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:317
msgid ""
"If you want my opinion, Majesty, I'm pretty sure she'd appreciate you "
"standing by her side now."
msgstr ""
"Si quiere mi opinión, Majestad, estoy segura de que agradecería que "
"estuviera a su lado ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:321
msgid ""
"That makes sense; I lost Garet-Desh to dragonfire once, I should understand "
"how she feels-"
msgstr ""
"Tiene sentido; yo perdí Garet-Desh por fuego de draco una vez, debería "
"comprender cómo se siente-"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:325
msgid ""
"Even without that, she'd still appreciate your company. She just... "
"appreciates your company."
msgstr ""
"Aunque no fuera por eso, apreciaría tu compañía. Simplemente... aprecia tu "
"compañía."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:329
msgid ""
"Oh...! *coughs politely* Then I shall have your leave, young Myra, Lord "
"Thrandyl. Hopefully I can be of aid to an... old friend."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh...! *tose educadamente* Entonces tomaré su permiso, joven Myra, señor "
"Thrandyl. Espero poder ser de ayuda a una... vieja amiga."

#. [message], speaker=Thrandyl
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:340
msgid ""
"(chuckles) And thus, with but a few words, this young girl from the "
"mountains enlightens a doubt I'd had for decades... May the Winds guide you "
"safely, daughter of Maat."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Y así, con apenas unas palabras, esta joven de las montañas aclara "
"una duda que tenía desde hace décadas... Que los Vientos te guíen a salvo, "
"hija de Maat."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:344
msgid "And you too, Lord Thrandyl."
msgstr "A usted también, señor Thrandyl."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:363
msgid ""
"...and such is the sight of Knalga when Winter has laid her white blanket on "
"the world, and the Sun is given leave to shine again."
msgstr ""
"...y así es el paisaje de Knalga cuando el Invierno ha tendido su manta "
"blanca sobre el mundo y al Sol se le permite volver a brillar."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:367
msgid ""
"I may never go there myself, elf princess, but with the picture your words "
"have woven, I may at least say I have seen it in my mind's eye. I, Dvalin of "
"the Aigathol, thank you."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez nunca vaya yo mismo, princesa elfa, pero con la imagen que tus "
"palabras han tejido, al menos puedo decir que lo he visto con los ojos de la "
"mente. Yo, Dvalin de los Aigathol, te lo agradezco."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:371
msgid ""
"(smiling) We can dispense the formalities, good Dvalin; we're true siblings-"
"in-arms already, are we not? Now, tell me more about the Varanyans; it will "
"be interesting to have an outsider's view on our kin of the Far East."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Podemos dejar las formalidades, buen Dvalin; ya somos verdaderos "
"hermanos de armas, ¿no es así? Ahora cuéntame más sobre los varanios; será "
"interesante tener la visión de un forastero sobre nuestros parientes del "
"Lejano Oriente."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:375
msgid ""
"*What do you know, these two actually seem to be getting along pretty "
"well... Let's not bother them...*"
msgstr ""
"*Vaya, parece que estos dos se están llevando bastante bien... Mejor no "
"molestarlos...*"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:389
msgid ""
"*Nothing else to see here; I should rest while I still can... Ugh, I still "
"need to find that blondie...*"
msgstr ""
"*No hay nada más que ver aquí; debería descansar mientras pueda... Ay, aún "
"tengo que encontrar a esa rubia...*"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:407
msgid "*Oh, there she is...*"
msgstr "*Ah, ahí está...*"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:411
msgid "Myra, look! This prince wants to talk with you!"
msgstr "¡Myra, mira! ¡Este príncipe quiere hablar contigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:415
msgid "I told you already, I'm of noble blood but not a prince..."
msgstr "Ya te lo dije, tengo sangre noble pero no soy príncipe..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:419
msgid ""
"A word of advice: give up trying to convince this blondie otherwise, it'll "
"be a waste of your time. But is it true you want to talk with me?"
msgstr ""
"Un consejo: deja de intentar convencer a esta rubia de lo contrario, será "
"pérdida de tiempo. ¿Es cierto que quieres hablar conmigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Yes. I am Jevyan, son of Captain Aracyn. You may not have seen me, but I was "
"there at the meeting. I deeply lament what happened to your fellow students, "
"but if I may say, you did well following your own heart. The elders often "
"underestimate us youngsters' cleverness and decision-making; the fact that "
"you stand here while your Headmistress lamentably doesn't proves my point."
msgstr ""
"Sí. Soy Jevyan, hijo del capitán Aracyn. Quizá no me viste, pero estuve en "
"la reunión. Lamento profundamente lo ocurrido a tus compañeras, pero si me "
"permite decirlo, hiciste bien siguiendo tu corazón. Los mayores suelen "
"subestimar la astucia y la capacidad de decisión de los jóvenes; que estés "
"aquí y tu directora lamentablemente no lo demuestra."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:427
msgid ""
"There were youngsters among those who died too. I could've died just as "
"easily as I crossed the mountains... (sigh) You know what, I'm too tired to "
"even argue. All I want is to find a soft bed to throw myself upon and rest."
msgstr ""
"También había jóvenes entre los que murieron. Podría haber muerto igual de "
"fácil cuando crucé las montañas... (suspira) Sabes qué, estoy demasiado "
"cansada para discutir. Todo lo que quiero es encontrar una cama blanda donde "
"tirarme a dormir."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:431
msgid ""
"I understand, and I apologise if I offended you or your sisters. Have a nice "
"sleep; if you need to know anything about our city and customs, you can ask "
"me, and I may even guide you..."
msgstr ""
"Lo entiendo, y me disculpo si te ofendí o a tus hermanas. Que duermas bien; "
"si necesitas saber algo sobre nuestra ciudad y costumbres, puedes "
"preguntarme, y hasta podría guiarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:435
msgid "I do know your customs, I'm half-Aragwaithi."
msgstr "Conozco vuestras costumbres, soy mitad aragwaithi."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Oh, really...? Well, pardon my foolishness, I just thought, judging by your "
"dark complexion..."
msgstr ""
"¿En serio...? Bueno, perdona mi tontería, solo pensé que, por tu tez "
"oscura..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/06_Council_With_The_King_b.cfg:443
msgid ""
"Just... Just leave me, see? I really must go and sleep for a while; Heaven "
"knows when I'll have time to rest again..."
msgstr ""
"Solo... Déjame, ¿vale? De verdad tengo que irme a dormir un rato; el Cielo "
"sabe cuándo volveré a tener tiempo para descansar..."

#. [scenario], id=07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:4
msgid "Rise Of The Dragons"
msgstr "Ascenso de los Dragones"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:21
msgid "Kill Shek'har"
msgstr "Matar a Shek’har"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:33
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:43
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:818
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1204
msgid "Death of Maat"
msgstr "Muerte de Maat"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:37
msgid "Death of Abhai"
msgstr "Muerte de Abhai"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:49
msgid "Death of Aracyn"
msgstr "Muerte de Aracyn"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Ancient Banner
#. [side], type=Aragwaith Flagbearer
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:88
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:132
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:95
msgid "Kingdom of Garet-Desh"
msgstr "Reino de Garet-Desh"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:164
msgid "Grog"
msgstr "Grog"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Lord Abhai, Lady Maat, I'm very pleased to see you have accepted my "
"invitation. It heartens me to learn that not all humans are puny, cowardly "
"little pests."
msgstr ""
"Lord Abhai, lady Maat, me complace ver que habéis aceptado mi invitación. Me "
"reconforta saber que no todos los humanos son plagas débiles y cobardes."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:216
msgid ""
"You greet us with harsh words, dragon. Did you invite us to come all this "
"way only for puerile insults?"
msgstr ""
"Nos saludas con duras palabras, dragón. ¿Nos invitaste a venir hasta aquí "
"solo para insultos infantiles?"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:220
msgid ""
"Oh no, certainly not! In truth, I merely wished to gaze upon you again. I "
"remember you both from that time: you, Abhai, were able and fierce, "
"especially for a human. And you, Maat... You were the one being to ever "
"strike fear into my heart. Yet look at you now... Abhai the Slayer, a frail "
"old man; and Maat the Great, a shadow of the woman I once beheld. You humans "
"are such ephemeral flowers..."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh no, desde luego que no! En verdad, solo quería contemplaros de nuevo. Os "
"recuerdo a ambos de aquella época: tú, Abhai, eras hábil y feroz, "
"especialmente para un humano. Y tú, Maat… Fuiste el único ser que logró "
"infundirme miedo. Pero mirad ahora… Abhai el Matadragones, un frágil "
"anciano; y Maat la Grande, una sombra de la mujer que una vez contemplé. Los "
"humanos sois flores tan efímeras…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Well, he truly made us come all this way only to behave like a petulant "
"child. Come, Abhai, let us leave him to his-"
msgstr ""
"Pues sí, nos ha hecho venir hasta aquí solo para comportarse como un niño "
"mimado. Ven, Abhai, dejémosle con su-"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:228
msgid ""
"(roaring laughter) Oh forgive an old dragon's tongue, I have lived far too "
"long to bother about being courteous with lesser creatures... Yet even you "
"deserve to know why you are about to be destroyed, and so I have invited you "
"to this... meeting."
msgstr ""
"(risa atronadora) ¡Oh, perdonad la lengua de un viejo dragón, he vivido "
"demasiado para preocuparme por ser cortés con criaturas inferiores…! Sin "
"embargo, incluso vosotros merecéis saber por qué vais a ser destruidos, y "
"por eso os he invitado a esta… reunión."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:232
msgid ""
"And what folly could have motivated this insanity? I don't know how you've "
"managed to do all this without Lord Agniballi stopping you-"
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué locura pudo haber motivado esta demencia? No sé cómo has logrado "
"hacer todo esto sin que lord Agniballi te detuviera-"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:236
msgid "Lord Agniballi is no longer in the world of the living, Ascendant."
msgstr "Lord Agniballi ya no está en el mundo de los vivos, Ascendente."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:240
msgid "W...what...? Don't tell me he's..."
msgstr "Q-qué…? No me digas que está…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:244
msgid ""
"Yes, he's dead, overcome and succeeded by an even mightier dragon, one who's "
"truly worthy of being our ruler, one who does not serve the interests of "
"inferior races; a King who will usher his people into a new Golden Age!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, está muerto, vencido y sucedido por un dragón aún más poderoso, uno que "
"es verdaderamente digno de ser nuestro gobernante, uno que no sirve a los "
"intereses de razas inferiores; un Rey que llevará a su pueblo a una nueva "
"Era Dorada."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:248
msgid ""
"But... I have always heard that no dragon was even close to being as "
"powerful as Agniballi..."
msgstr ""
"Pero… Siempre he oído que ningún dragón estaba ni siquiera cerca de ser tan "
"poderoso como Agniballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Ah, puny human king, one could fill a Library as great as Hiera'Shirsha's "
"with all things you ignore..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, insignificante rey humano, se podría llenar una biblioteca tan grande "
"como la de Hiera’Shirsha con todo lo que ignoras…"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:257
msgid ""
"And you should wash your fetid mouth before even spelling Lord Abhai's name, "
"lizard!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y deberías lavarte esa boca apestosa antes de pronunciar siquiera el nombre "
"de lord Abhai, lagarto!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:261
msgid ""
"Aracyn, silence from you. Shek'har, everyone in Irdya acknowledges the might "
"of the dragons; but you should know that, if all the elves, humans, dwarves "
"and trolls in this world unite against you, even with all your power, you "
"shall not prevail. This is something that even I, a 'puny human king', know."
msgstr ""
"Aracyn, silencio. Shek’har, todo Irdya reconoce el poder de los dragones; "
"pero deberías saber que, si todos los elfos, humanos, enanos y trolls de "
"este mundo se unen contra vosotros, ni siquiera con todo vuestro poder "
"podréis prevalecer. Eso lo sabe incluso yo, un «insignificante rey humano»."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:265
msgid ""
"Shek'har, tell me... This dragon who killed Agniballi... Is he the one known "
"as the Sky Dragon?"
msgstr ""
"Shek’har, dime… Ese dragón que mató a Agniballi… ¿Es el que llaman el Dragón "
"del Cielo?"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:269
msgid ""
"You... (roars loudly) Even if I answered your question, Ascendant, the "
"information would not be of any use to you, for you shall be dead shortly."
msgstr ""
"Tú… (ruge con fuerza) Aunque respondiera a tu pregunta, Ascendente, la "
"información no te serviría de nada, porque pronto estaréis muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:276
msgid ""
"My brothers of fire! Before us stand the paramount leader of the humans, as "
"well as their precious sorceress, she of far-reaching fame, High Ascendant "
"Maat! But they're overwhelmingly outnumbered, and on our side we have the "
"Warden of Irdya, whose power eclipses Maat's like the sun's light eclipses "
"that of the brightest of stars! So, fall on them, and leave no survivors! "
"Today we avenge the death of our brother Krathon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermanos del fuego! ¡Ante nosotros están el líder supremo de los humanos y "
"su preciosa hechicera, la de fama lejana, la Gran Ascendente Maat! ¡Pero "
"están en inferioridad numérica abrumadora, y a nuestro lado tenemos al "
"Guardián de Irdya, cuyo poder eclipsa al de Maat como la luz del sol eclipsa "
"a la estrella más brillante! ¡Así que, atacad y no dejéis supervivientes! "
"¡Hoy vengamos la muerte de nuestro hermano Krathon!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:280
msgid ""
"As I expected, they treacherously try to kill us... Maat, are you sure you "
"want to try it?"
msgstr ""
"Tal como esperaba, intentan matarnos a traición… Maat, ¿estás segura de que "
"quieres intentarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:284
msgid ""
"I am. If they do have the Sky Dragon on their side, which I now think is "
"very likely, I <i>might</i> end up in trouble, but I don't think we'll have "
"Shek'har within our reach again so soon, and thus we must kill him here and "
"now; his death would trouble the dragons' campaign, which would give us more "
"time to mount a solid alliance with elves, dwarves, trolls and anyone else "
"who may join us. I will kill Shek'har, but I'll need the Aragwaithi, the "
"trolls, the dwarves and the elementals to cover me. As much as I hate to "
"admit, Shek'har is right when he says I'm past my prime..."
msgstr ""
"Sí. Si realmente tienen al Dragón del Cielo de su lado, que ahora creo muy "
"probable, <i>podría</i> tener problemas, pero no creo que volvamos a tener a "
"Shek’har a nuestro alcance tan pronto, y por eso debemos matarlo aquí y "
"ahora; su muerte entorpecería la campaña de los dragones, lo que nos daría "
"más tiempo para forjar una alianza sólida con elfos, enanos, trolls y "
"quienquiera que se nos una. Mataré a Shek’har, pero necesitaré que los "
"aragwaithi, trolls, enanos y elementales me cubran. Por mucho que me duela "
"admitirlo, Shek’har tiene razón cuando dice que ya pasé mi mejor momento…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:301
msgid "Yes, Assix, show them our new weapon!"
msgstr "¡Sí, Assix, muéstrales nuestra nueva arma!"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:306
msgid "What on Irdya are those things?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué demonios son esas cosas?!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:310
msgid ""
"Curse them! They must have stolen the Book of the Dead, and learned the arts "
"of Necromancy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean! ¡Deben haber robado el Libro de los Muertos y aprendido las "
"artes de la Nigromancia!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:314
msgid "*Book of the Dead? Can it be the tome I saw with that lizard Assix?*"
msgstr "*¿Libro de los Muertos? ¿Será el tomo que vi con ese lagarto Assix?*"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:319
msgid "Can you please put it in terms we common humans may understand?"
msgstr ""
"¿Podéis explicarlo en términos que los humanos comunes podamos entender?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:323
msgid ""
"Dead bodies filled with dark magic to do the necromancer's bidding - the "
"very arts with which Ashura of Hiera'Duath threatened to destroy our world. "
"Your soldiers' weapons will be of little use against them; they are weak "
"against Windsong or elven magic, but the only ones here are myself, Myra, "
"Veela and Alenya..."
msgstr ""
"Cuerpos muertos llenos de magia oscura para cumplir las órdenes del "
"nigromante —las mismas artes con las que Ashura de Hiera’Duath amenazó con "
"destruir nuestro mundo. Las armas de tus soldados serán de poca utilidad "
"contra ellos; son débiles ante magia de Hijas del Viento o élfica, pero los "
"únicos aquí somos yo, Myra, Veela y Alenya…"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Pah! They look frail enough to me. I'm sure our hammers and the trolls' "
"clubs can do quick work of them. C'mon boys, let's introduce those old bone "
"piles to our axes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bah! A mí me parecen bastante frágiles. Estoy seguro de que nuestros "
"martillos y las mazas de los trolls pueden acabar con ellos rápido. ¡Vamos, "
"muchachos, presentemos a esos montones de huesos viejos a nuestras hachas!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:341
msgid ""
"The puny apes are making progress! Lord Shek'har, I must fall back now, but "
"I will leave some of my strongest creations helping you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los insignificantes monos están avanzando! Lord Shek’har, debo retroceder "
"ahora, pero dejaré algunas de mis creaciones más fuertes ayudándote."

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Cowardly saurian, if I didn't need his monsters and his wits... But at least "
"he has really left strong undead."
msgstr ""
"Saurio cobarde, si no necesitara sus monstruos y su astucia… Pero al menos "
"ha dejado no-muertos fuertes de verdad."

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:369
msgid ""
"My son, I will not have you die today; fall back and see if there are any "
"reinforcements on the way! Meanwhile, I will lead your soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Hijo mío, no permitiré que mueras hoy; retrocede y mira si vienen refuerzos "
"por el camino. Mientras, yo lideraré a tus soldados."

#. [message], speaker=Khrakrahs
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:373
msgid "(sigh) Yes, father..."
msgstr "(suspira) Sí, padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:404
msgid "Aaargh! My... head..."
msgstr "¡Aaargh! Mi… cabeza…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:418
msgid "Mother!"
msgstr "¡Madre!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:422
msgid "No... MAAT! What is happening to her?!"
msgstr "¡No… MAAT! ¡Qué le pasa?!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:426
msgid ""
"Could it be the same being that blocked her foresight is pinning her down...?"
msgstr "¿Será que el mismo ser que bloqueó su previsión la está reteniendo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:430
msgid "No way... I'll fall... here...!"
msgstr "De ninguna manera… ¡Caeré… aquí…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:441
msgid ""
"Thank Heavens, she still had enough strength to teleport back to our camp!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias al Cielo, aún tuvo fuerzas para teletransportarse de vuelta al "
"campamento!"

#. [message], speaker=Khrakrahs
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:445
msgid ""
"Cursed be this Ascendant! Do not lose heart, my warriors, for Lord Shek'har "
"has just been wounded, and will retire for a while to recover - but while he "
"is withdrawn, let's rain fire on our enemies, and offer their roasted bodies "
"to him as a recovery meal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea esta Ascendente! ¡No perdáis el ánimo, guerreros míos, porque "
"lord Shek’har acaba de ser herido y se retirará un tiempo a recuperarse —"
"pero mientras esté retirado, llovamos fuego sobre nuestros enemigos y "
"ofrezcamos sus cuerpos asados como comida de recuperación!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Blast it, they've called on reinforcements! Without Lady Maat, there is "
"nothing else we can do here; we must retreat."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, han llamado refuerzos! Sin lady Maat, no podemos hacer nada más "
"aquí; debemos retroceder."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:453
msgid ""
"The Great Northern Gate is close by, we'll be safe once we get inside the "
"dwarves' tunnels. Come, I'll show you the way."
msgstr ""
"La Gran Puerta Norte está cerca, estaremos a salvo una vez dentro de los "
"túneles de los enanos. Venid, os mostraré el camino."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:493
msgid "No! How could I have let her die?!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Cómo he podido dejar que muriera!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:507
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1388
msgid "I... mustn't... fall..."
msgstr "No… debo… caer…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:511
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1392
msgid "MOTHER, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡MADRE, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:515
msgid ""
"Lady Maat is dead! There is no way we can't defeat the dragons without her! "
"We are doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lady Maat ha muerto! ¡No hay forma de derrotar a los dragones sin ella! "
"¡Estamos perdidos!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:557
msgid "I go join my ancestors... Keep fighting without me..."
msgstr "Voy a reunirme con mis antepasados… Seguid luchando sin mí…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:561
msgid ""
"Ha! Not even their mighty King Abhai can withstand our strength! Onwards, "
"Children of Morogor, and destroy everything and everyone you find on your "
"way!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Ni siquiera su poderoso rey Abhai puede resistir nuestra fuerza! "
"¡Adelante, Hijos de Morogor, destruid todo y a todos los que encontréis en "
"vuestro camino!"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:576
msgid "Sorry, Lord Abhai, I have fallen to our enemies..."
msgstr "Lo siento, lord Abhai, he caído ante nuestros enemigos…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:587
msgid ""
"I expected to crush these puny apes before the rest of the armies arrived, "
"but it doesn't matter: surround them where they are!"
msgstr ""
"Esperaba aplastar a estos insignificantes monos antes de que llegaran el "
"resto de los ejércitos, pero no importa: ¡rodeadlos donde están!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/07_Rise_Of_The_Dragons.cfg:591
msgid ""
"More and more dragon hordes come from the west! We won't be able to escape "
"anymore now..."
msgstr ""
"¡Cada vez vienen más hordas de dragones desde el oeste! ¡Ya no podremos "
"escapar…"

#. [scenario], id=08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:4
msgid "The Kalian Of Garet-Desh"
msgstr "El Kalian de Garet-Desh"

#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:44
msgid "Elvish Enclaves"
msgstr "Enclaves Élficos"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Shield Guard
#. [part]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:50
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/utils/characters.cfg:158
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/utils/intros.cfg:345
msgid "King Dashien"
msgstr "Rey Dashien"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Silver Shield
#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:88
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:27
msgid "Aragwaithi"
msgstr "Aragwaithi"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:152
msgid ""
"So, Lady Maat, could you please explain to all present who is this Sky "
"Dragon that is plotting the dragons' attack?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, lady Maat, ¿podríais explicar a todos los presentes quién es este "
"Dragón del Cielo que está detrás del ataque de los dragones?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:156
msgid ""
"Yes, but first I must tell you an ancient tale, one I believe I'm the only "
"one left who knows, save perhaps for Shek'har himself. It tells of the High "
"Dragons."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero primero debo contaros una antigua historia que creo que soy la "
"única que queda que la conoce, salvo quizá el propio Shek’har. Se trata de "
"los Dragones Supremos."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:160
msgid ""
"Thousands of years ago, the dragons were the supreme rulers of this world; "
"no other race could match their power and wit. However, they used their "
"might to tyrannise other races, and with their fires they unleashed great "
"devastation."
msgstr ""
"Hace miles de años, los dragones eran los gobernantes supremos de este "
"mundo; ninguna otra raza podía igualar su poder e ingenio. Sin embargo, "
"usaban su fuerza para tiranizar a otras razas y con sus fuegos desataban "
"gran devastación."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:164
msgid ""
"Seeing this, beings known as the Ancient Ones chose a dragon with great "
"compassion for weaker beings and imbued him with immense power, but changing "
"his element from fire to water. Thus the High Dragon of Water, Nitiballi, "
"was born; he stopped the dragons' rampage and saved the world's fauna and "
"flora. However, he exceeded himself, and threatened to bring an end to the "
"dragons themselves. Not willing to destroy any of Irdya's races, the Ancient "
"Ones chose another dragon, one whose honour and dedication to his own people "
"was remarkable, and made him as strong as Nitiballi, allowing him to retain "
"his original element. Thus Agniballi, the High Dragon of Fire, was born, and "
"he confronted Nitiballi in a battle which, as expected, ended in stalemate."
msgstr ""
"Al ver esto, seres conocidos como los Antiguos eligieron a un dragón con "
"gran compasión por los seres más débiles e infundieron en él un poder "
"inmenso, cambiando su elemento del fuego al agua. Así nació Nitiballi, el "
"Dragón Supremo del Agua; detuvo la masacre de los dragones y salvó la fauna "
"y flora del mundo. Sin embargo, se excedió y amenazó con acabar con los "
"propios dragones. No queriendo destruir ninguna de las razas de Irdya, los "
"Antiguos eligieron a otro dragón, uno cuyo honor y dedicación a su pueblo "
"eran notables, y lo hicieron tan fuerte como Nitiballi, permitiéndole "
"conservar su elemento original. Así nació Agniballi, el Dragón Supremo del "
"Fuego, y se enfrentó a Nitiballi en una batalla que, como era de esperar, "
"terminó en empate."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:168
msgid ""
"Finally, to make sure neither of the High Dragons would topple the other, "
"the Ancient Ones themselves created a third one, giving him not only a "
"strong sense of justice, but also a power so great than not even the joint "
"strength of Agniballi and Nitiballi could surpass it; and they commissioned "
"him to watch over them, making sure nature remained balanced. This third "
"dragon was Svarballi, the High Dragon of the Sky. Afterwards, the Ancient "
"Ones disappeared; some say they had decided to leave the world thriving on "
"its own, and withdrew to wherever they'd come from."
msgstr ""
"Finalmente, para asegurarse de que ninguno de los Dragones Supremos "
"derrocara al otro, los propios Antiguos crearon un tercero, dotándolo no "
"solo de un fuerte sentido de la justicia, sino también de un poder tan "
"grande que ni siquiera la fuerza conjunta de Agniballi y Nitiballi podía "
"superarlo; y le encargaron vigilarlos a ellos, asegurándose de que la "
"naturaleza permaneciera en equilibrio. Este tercer dragón fue Svarballi, el "
"Dragón Supremo del Cielo. Después, los Antiguos desaparecieron; algunos "
"dicen que decidieron dejar que el mundo prosperara por sí solo y se "
"retiraron a dondequiera que hubieran venido."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:172
msgid ""
"For a long time, Irdya was in peace under the constant watch of Svarballi, "
"and nature restored itself. The Sky Dragon fulfilled his duty well, and "
"maintained order in the world. However, he grew increasingly harsher, "
"resorting to whatever measure it took to maintain his notion of order; "
"ultimately, he concluded that life was bound to be self-destructive, and "
"decided that protecting it was no longer worthwhile. Thus he went on a "
"rampage all over Irdya, destroying vast extensions of land and killing "
"thousands."
msgstr ""
"Durante mucho tiempo, Irdya estuvo en paz bajo la constante vigilancia de "
"Svarballi y la naturaleza se restauró. El Dragón del Cielo cumplió bien su "
"deber y mantuvo el orden en el mundo. Sin embargo, se volvió cada vez más "
"duro, recurriendo a cualquier medida que hiciera falta para mantener su "
"noción de orden; al final, concluyó que la vida estaba destinada a "
"autodestruirse y decidió que protegerla ya no valía la pena. Así se lanzó a "
"una masacre por todo Irdya, destruyendo vastas extensiones de tierra y "
"matando a miles."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Agniballi and Nitiballi did not watch that idly, and joined forces to stop "
"the Sky Dragon's insanity, yet Svarballi was too powerful. It was then that "
"both the Water and the Fire Dragons were possessed by a power greater even "
"than Svarballi's, and with that power they finally defeated him. However, "
"for some reason he wasn't killed: instead, his soul was sealed away in a "
"secret place."
msgstr ""
"Agniballi y Nitiballi no se quedaron de brazos cruzados y unieron fuerzas "
"para detener la locura del Dragón del Cielo, pero Svarballi era demasiado "
"poderoso. Fue entonces cuando ambos, el Dragón del Agua y el del Fuego, "
"fueron poseídos por un poder aún mayor que el de Svarballi, y con ese poder "
"finalmente lo derrotaron. Sin embargo, por alguna razón no lo mataron: en su "
"lugar, sellaron su alma en un lugar secreto."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:180
msgid ""
"Svarballi was beaten, but the battle against him left most of the world "
"devastated. In order to heal it and make sure life would continue to exist, "
"Nitiballi unleashed rainfalls and floods, gathered stormclouds and birthed "
"rivers, all with magic waters that gradually healed the world, reviving its "
"soils and vegetation, restoring the environment to its former state. "
"Unfortunately, the effort was too great for Nitiballi, who died shortly "
"later; but his crystallized body kept unleashing an endless stream of life "
"water: thus he became the Fountain of Life. This is the Legend of the High "
"Dragons."
msgstr ""
"Svarballi fue derrotado, pero la batalla contra él dejó la mayor parte del "
"mundo devastado. Para sanarlo y asegurarse de que la vida continuara "
"existiendo, Nitiballi desató lluvias e inundaciones, reunió nubes de "
"tormenta y dio a luz ríos, todo con aguas mágicas que gradualmente sanaron "
"el mundo, reviviendo sus suelos y vegetación, restaurando el entorno a su "
"estado anterior. Desgraciadamente, el esfuerzo fue demasiado grande para "
"Nitiballi, que murió poco después; pero su cuerpo cristalizado siguió "
"liberando un flujo interminable de agua de vida: así se convirtió en la "
"Fuente de la Vida. Esta es la Leyenda de los Dragones Supremos."

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:185
msgid ""
"You mean to say that this dragon we face was too strong even for Lord "
"Agniballi? If such is our enemy's strength, we can never possibly prevail!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quieres decir que este dragón al que nos enfrentamos era demasiado fuerte "
"incluso para lord Agniballi? ¡Si tal es la fuerza de nuestro enemigo, nunca "
"podremos vencer!"

#. [message], speaker=King Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:190
msgid ""
"You shall pardon me, High Ascendant, but I refuse to believe your words! "
"It's unconceivable that our foe is so superior to us!"
msgstr ""
"Perdonadme, Gran Ascendente, ¡pero me niego a creer vuestras palabras! ¡Es "
"inconcebible que nuestro enemigo sea tan superior a nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Truth does not require belief, Lord Dashien; truth is simply what it is. But "
"despair not, for I believe I know the key to defeating Svarballi, either by "
"killing or by sealing him again. This key is my foster-daughter, Myra."
msgstr ""
"La verdad no requiere creencia, lord Dashien; la verdad es simplemente lo "
"que es. Pero no desesperéis, porque creo saber la clave para derrotar a "
"Svarballi, ya sea matándolo o volviendo a sellarlo. Esa clave es mi hija "
"adoptiva, Myra."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:198
msgid "Wait, what? Mother, if you're jesting..."
msgstr "Espera, ¿qué? Madre, si estás bromeando…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:202
msgid ""
"I'm not, daughter. I... I think I have never told you everything concerning "
"the day I found you in the Wilderness, when you were but a child. And for "
"this, I apologise."
msgstr ""
"No lo estoy, hija. Yo… Creo que nunca te conté todo lo referente al día en "
"que te encontré en la Selva, cuando eras solo una niña. Y por eso, te pido "
"perdón."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Please, Lady, tell us how this young and brave woman can help us defeat the "
"legendary dragon."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, lady, contadnos cómo esta joven y valiente mujer puede ayudarnos "
"a derrotar al legendario dragón."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:210
msgid ""
"I found her by accident during one of my 'meditation wanderings', in the "
"caves of a mountain. She told me she'd been there for weeks and, when "
"questioned about her means of survival, she claimed she had been just "
"drinking water from a fountain she'd found in a deeper cave. I investigated "
"it, and there I saw a dragon-shaped crystal statue from which a massive "
"water flow sprouted. It still bore vestiges of healing magic, and thus I "
"knew that was the Fountain of Life. I guessed that consuming and bathing in "
"those waters for so long would have some notable effect on Myra, and I was "
"proved right years later, when she showed her affinity with nature's spirits "
"by summoning her first elemental."
msgstr ""
"La encontré por accidente durante uno de mis «paseos de meditación», en las "
"cuevas de una montaña. Me dijo que llevaba semanas allí y, al preguntarle "
"cómo había sobrevivido, afirmó que solo había estado bebiendo agua de una "
"fuente que encontró en una cueva más profunda. La investigué y allí vi una "
"estatua de cristal con forma de dragón de la que brotaba un flujo masivo de "
"agua. Todavía tenía vestigios de magia curativa, y así supe que era la "
"Fuente de la Vida. Supuse que consumir y bañarse en esas aguas durante tanto "
"tiempo tendría algún efecto notable en Myra, y años después se demostró que "
"tenía razón, cuando mostró su afinidad con los espíritus de la naturaleza al "
"invocar su primer elemental."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:214
msgid ""
"So I have... the High Dragon of Water's power within me? But how does this "
"explain..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tengo… ¿el poder del Dragón Supremo del Agua dentro de mí? Pero "
"¿cómo explica eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:218
msgid ""
"...Your affinity with nature? Simple: it is because Nitiballi too had a "
"strong bound with nature's spirits, or so the legends claim."
msgstr ""
"¿…tu afinidad con la naturaleza? Simple: porque Nitiballi también tenía un "
"fuerte vínculo con los espíritus de la naturaleza, o eso dicen las leyendas."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:222
msgid "Then Myra has the power to defeat the Sky Dragon?"
msgstr "¿Entonces Myra tiene el poder para derrotar al Dragón del Cielo?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Not quite; what I think is that she may learn the secret of Svarballi's "
"defeat from the spirits of nature themselves. I also guess that she'll "
"better communicate with them at the Fountain of Life itself - which, "
"impregnated with nature's arcane energy as it is, may facilitate the contact."
msgstr ""
"No exactamente; lo que creo es que ella puede aprender el secreto de la "
"derrota de Svarballi de los propios espíritus de la naturaleza. También "
"supongo que podrá comunicarse mejor con ellos en la propia Fuente de la "
"Vida, que, impregnada como está de la energía arcana de la naturaleza, puede "
"facilitar el contacto."

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Then young Myra must make haste and find this Fountain! I shall choose a "
"hundred of my finest warriors to escort you if necessary, to crush anyone "
"who dare lay a finger on you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces la joven Myra debe darse prisa y encontrar esta Fuente! ¡Elegiré a "
"cien de mis mejores guerreros para escoltarte si es necesario, para aplastar "
"a cualquiera que se atreva a ponerte un dedo encima!"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:234
msgid "And my druids shall keep you healthy during your entire journey!"
msgstr "¡Y mis druidas te mantendrán sana durante todo el viaje!"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:239
msgid "And my horsemen shall take you swiftly to your goal!"
msgstr "¡Y mis jinetes te llevarán rápidamente a tu destino!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:243
msgid ""
"(blushing) Well, I... I am truly grateful for your kind offers, but methinks "
"too large a retinue will only make us slower and easier to find. I think my "
"elementals are enough to protect me, though I'd really appreciate it if you "
"came along, Dvalin..."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojándose) Bueno, yo… Estoy muy agradecida por vuestras amables ofertas, "
"pero creo que un séquito demasiado grande solo nos haría más lentos y más "
"fáciles de encontrar. Creo que mis elementales son suficientes para "
"protegerme, aunque realmente agradecería que vinieras conmigo, Dvalin…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:247
msgid "!!!"
msgstr "!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:251
msgid "...And you too, Veela..."
msgstr "…Y tú también, Veela…"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Och, I am sorry for not being able to follow you, my friend; I must return "
"home and take the news of this Kalian to my father. But some of my fighters "
"who have followed us since the battle at the Great Northern Gate want to "
"remain with you."
msgstr ""
"Och, lo siento por no poder seguirte, amiga mía; debo volver a casa y llevar "
"las noticias de este Kalian a mi padre. Pero algunos de mis guerreros que "
"nos han seguido desde la batalla en la Gran Puerta Norte quieren quedarse "
"contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:259
msgid "I am truly grateful for their dedication and loyalty."
msgstr "Estoy realmente agradecida por su dedicación y lealtad."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:263
msgid ""
"Ahem, if you have no objection, I'd like to come along with you as well..."
msgstr "Ejem, si no tienes inconveniente, a mí también me gustaría acompañar…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:267
msgid "And why would you risk yourself following someone you've just met?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y por qué te arriesgarías siguiendo a alguien a quien acabas de conocer?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:271
msgid ""
"Because... I am as interested as anyone else here in defeating the dragons, "
"and my arcane arts shall be useful if we come across magic monsters. "
"Besides, I know well both medicinal and edible herbs, and you'll need them "
"as you cross the Wilderness."
msgstr ""
"Porque… me interesa tanto como a cualquiera aquí derrotar a los dragones y "
"mis artes arcanas serán útiles si nos topamos con monstruos mágicos. Además, "
"conozco bien las hierbas medicinales y comestibles, y las necesitaréis "
"mientras crucéis la Selva."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:275
msgid "She is right, daughter; please think well about it."
msgstr "Tiene razón, hija; piénsalo bien."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:279
msgid "Well, if that is so, then you may follow me."
msgstr "Bueno, si es así, entonces puedes seguirme."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:283
msgid ""
"AND you would certainly need speed for the journey; I could lead a division "
"of horsemen if my father the captain and Lord Abhai allowed me to."
msgstr ""
"Y ciertamente necesitaréis velocidad para el viaje; podría liderar una "
"división de jinetes si mi padre el capitán y lord Abhai me lo permiten."

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:288
msgid ""
"You are no commander, Jevyan; your cousin Ravyan would be more fit for such "
"task... Though I appreciate your initiative, and will allow you to escort "
"Lady Myra if Lord Abhai gives his approval."
msgstr ""
"No eres comandante, Jevyan; tu primo Ravyan sería más adecuado para tal "
"tarea… Aunque aprecio tu iniciativa y te permitiré escoltar a lady Myra si "
"lord Abhai da su aprobación."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:292
msgid "Which is given: to both bright Ravyan and bold Jevyan."
msgstr "Que es concedida: tanto al brillante Ravyan como al audaz Jevyan."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:296
msgid ""
"*Father only wants Ravyan to watch over me...* I am gleeful for such honour, "
"milord."
msgstr ""
"*Padre solo quiere que Ravyan me vigile…* Estoy encantado por tal honor, "
"milord."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Then we must not waste any time: we must prepare the men for the journey and "
"set out as soon as possible!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces no debemos perder tiempo: debemos preparar a los hombres para el "
"viaje y partir lo antes posible!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:308
msgid ""
"And it shall be so. Myra, Veela, Alenya, Ravyan and Jevyan are allowed to "
"leave immediately, to begin preparations; but I still have some points to "
"discuss with the other lords, and so the Kalian of Garet-Desh continues."
msgstr ""
"Y así será. Myra, Veela, Alenya, Ravyan y Jevyan tienen permiso para partir "
"de inmediato y comenzar los preparativos; pero aún tengo algunos puntos que "
"discutir con los otros señores, y por eso continúa el Kalian de Garet-Desh."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:315
msgid ""
"(whispering) Go and start suiting yourself for the journey. I'm telling you "
"the Fountain of Life's whereabouts later; it's not that I don't trust the "
"other lords, but I wouldn't have this knowledge divulged to so many people."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Id y empezad a prepararos para el viaje. Os diré dónde está la "
"Fuente de la Vida después; no es que no confíe en los otros señores, pero no "
"quiero que este conocimiento se divulgue a tanta gente."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:319
msgid ""
"I understand, but... How am I supposed to communicate with the spirits? I "
"mean, I can control them, but not talk with them..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, pero… ¿Cómo se supone que me comunique con los espíritus? Quiero "
"decir, puedo controlarlos, pero no dialogar con ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/08_The_Kalian_Of_Garet_Desh.cfg:323
msgid "You will know it when the time comes, dear. I'm sure you will."
msgstr ""
"Lo sabrás cuando llegue el momento, hija. Estoy segura de que lo harás."

