#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Now, I know you may have your reasons for hiding this information, but would "
"you tell us where exactly are going?"
msgstr ""
"Sé que puedes tener tus razones para ocultar esta información, pero ¿nos "
"dirías a dónde vamos exactamente?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:191
msgid "Fine, but only to the four of you... We're going to Mount Hursag."
msgstr "Está bien, pero solo a ustedes cuatro... Vamos al Monte Hursag."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:195
msgid "The world's tallest mountain? Is there where the Fountain of Life is?"
msgstr "¿La montaña más alta del mundo? ¿Ahí está la Fuente de la Vida?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:199
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr "Exacto."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:203
msgid ""
"You <i>are</i> aware that we'll have to cross the vast Wilderness, from "
"whence no human expedition has ever returned, right?"
msgstr ""
"<i>Tienes</i> claro que tendremos que cruzar la vasta Región Salvaje, de "
"donde nunca ha regresado ninguna expedición humana, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:207
msgid "If you want to go back home, this is the right time..."
msgstr "Si quieren volver a casa, este es el momento..."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:211
msgid ""
"Of course not! I was just making sure you knew where you're taking us..."
msgstr "¡Claro que no! Solo me aseguraba de que supieras a dónde nos llevas..."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:215
msgid "We're Windsong! There's nothing we don't know!"
msgstr "¡Somos Hijas del Viento! ¡No hay nada que no sepamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Right, I'm not pointing out the holes in such a claim... Look, yonder is a "
"small human village; I'm certain they will let us spend a night there, if we "
"tell them who we are."
msgstr ""
"Claro, no voy a señalar los agujeros en esa afirmación... Miren, allá hay un "
"pequeño pueblo humano; estoy segura de que nos dejarán pasar la noche si les "
"decimos quiénes somos."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:223
msgid "No, forget about this village; let's just camp somewhere nearby..."
msgstr "No, olviden este pueblo; acampemos en algún lugar cercano..."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:227
msgid "Why? Those humans are friendly Aragwaithi."
msgstr "¿Por qué? Esos humanos son aragwaithi amistosos."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:231
msgid "Hold on, there is something wrong... What are they all screaming about?"
msgstr "Un momento, algo anda mal... ¿De qué están gritando todos?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Oh no, there are... lots of those horrible skeleton men coming from the "
"west... They're being attacked!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh no, hay... muchos de esos horribles esqueletos viniendo del oeste... "
"¡Los están atacando!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:239
msgid "Damn those undead! My arrows will be useless against them."
msgstr "¡Malditos no muertos! Mis flechas serán inútiles contra ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Let it not be a problem. Here, let me imbue your arrows with arcane power... "
"And your blades too, Ravyan. Now they'll be as deadly to the skeletons as "
"they are against normal humans."
msgstr ""
"No será problema. Aquí, déjame imbuir tus flechas con poder arcano... Y tus "
"espadas también, Ravyan. Ahora serán tan letales contra los esqueletos como "
"contra humanos normales."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:247
msgid "Thank you, Alenya."
msgstr "Gracias, Alenya."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:282
msgid "You speak as if we were actually going to help them..."
msgstr "Hablas como si de verdad fuéramos a ayudarlos..."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:286
msgid ""
"And aren't we? Wait, you're not saying we will let those villagers at the "
"mercy of the undead, are you?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y no vamos a hacerlo? Espera, no estarás diciendo que dejaremos a esos "
"aldeanos a merced de los no muertos, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:290
msgid "That's exactly what I am seriously tempted to do."
msgstr "Eso es exactamente lo que estoy muy tentada de hacer."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:294
msgid "(shocked) But... why? I don't understand..."
msgstr "(sorprendida) Pero... ¿por qué? No entiendo..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:298
msgid ""
"Once I told you that I fled from my birth village after my mother's death, "
"because the villagers mistreated me. Well, <i>this</i> is the village of "
"Kiera, where I was born."
msgstr ""
"Una vez les conté que huí de mi aldea natal después de la muerte de mi "
"madre, porque los aldeanos me maltrataban. Pues bien, <i>esta</i> es la "
"aldea de Kiera, donde nací."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:302
msgid ""
"But... Still, we can't just let the enemy advance into our lands! We must "
"stop it if we can!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero... de todos modos no podemos dejar que el enemigo avance en nuestras "
"tierras! ¡Debemos detenerlo si podemos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:306
msgid "So may this be the reason of fighting tonight."
msgstr "Entonces que esa sea la razón para luchar esta noche."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:310
msgid ""
"I advise not sending the horses to fight, for they're precious to us; the "
"riders can fight well as foot spearmen too."
msgstr ""
"Recomiendo no enviar a los caballos a pelear, son muy valiosos para "
"nosotros; los jinetes también pueden pelear bien como lanceros a pie."

#. [message], speaker=Gwaec
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Reinforcements at last! But wait, what are those monsters doing alongside "
"the soldiers... Is the kingdom of Doldesh training tame beasts now?"
msgstr ""
"¡Refuerzos por fin! Pero espera, ¿qué hacen esos monstruos junto a los "
"soldados...? ¿Acaso el reino de Doldesh está entrenando bestias domesticadas "
"ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:328
msgid "Um, I think I know that young woman leading the charge..."
msgstr "Eh, creo que conozco a la joven que lidera la carga..."

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:336
msgid ""
"We owe you our very own lives, noble masters. Without your help, we'd've "
"surely perished tonight. But wait a minute: aren't you Myra, the daughter of "
"Ysara?"
msgstr ""
"Les debemos nuestras propias vidas, nobles señores. Sin su ayuda, "
"seguramente habríamos perecido esta noche. Pero un momento: ¿no eres tú "
"Myra, la hija de Ysara?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:340
msgid "The one and only..."
msgstr "La única e inigualable..."

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:344
msgid "By Heavens, we thought you dead long ago!"
msgstr "¡Por los cielos, pensábamos que habías muerto hace mucho!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:348
msgid "Certainly you thought, and hoped, I was dead..."
msgstr "Seguro que lo pensaron... y lo esperaban..."

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:352
msgid "Uh... say again?"
msgstr "Eh... ¿cómo dices?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Elder, I now remember who you are. Everyone in this village tormented my "
"mother, accusing her of 'blood betrayal' for having a child by a Hannuk from "
"the steppes, but your voice was the worst of all. You weren't any gentler to "
"me either; I don't recall you ever raising a finger to stop your children, "
"or any other child, from calling me a 'mongrel', or riding me like the "
"'steppe mare' I was supposed to be..."
msgstr ""
"Anciano, ahora recuerdo quién eres. Todos en esta aldea atormentaron a mi "
"madre, acusándola de «traición de sangre» por tener una hija con un hannuk "
"de las estepas, pero tu voz fue la peor de todas. Conmigo tampoco fuiste más "
"amable; no recuerdo que alguna vez hayas movido un dedo para impedir que tus "
"hijos, o cualquier otro niño, me llamaran «mestiza», o me montaran como la "
"«yegua de la estepa» que se suponía que era..."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:360
msgid "Oh, Myra...!"
msgstr "¡Oh, Myra...!"

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Erm, well, I know we may have been harsh on you, but you must understand "
"that..."
msgstr ""
"Ehm, bueno, sé que tal vez fuimos duros contigo, pero debes entender que..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:368
msgid ""
"Understand what? That I was never one of you? That I deserved to be treated "
"as less than a person for that? Because that lesson, elder, was well learned "
"and never forgotten! Now, here's the thing: I don't see <i>you</i> as one of "
"<i>my</i> own either; were we not at war, I'd be content with letting that "
"saurian ravage this sorry village, for even my elementals' existence is "
"worth more than any of your wretched lives!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entender qué? ¿Que nunca fui una de ustedes? ¿Que merecía ser tratada como "
"menos que persona por eso? ¡Porque esa lección, anciano, la aprendí bien y "
"nunca la olvidé! Ahora, aquí está la cosa: yo tampoco los veo a <i>ustedes</"
"i> como de los <i>míos</i>; si no estuviéramos en guerra, me bastaría con "
"dejar que ese sauriano arrasara esta miserable aldea, ¡porque incluso la "
"existencia de mis elementales vale más que cualquiera de sus miserables "
"vidas!"

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Oh, be silent! We were willing to feed and shelter you when your mother "
"died, even though you're a mongrel, so you should be th-"
msgstr ""
"¡Cállate! Estábamos dispuestos a alimentarte y darte refugio cuando tu madre "
"murió, ¡aunque eres una mestiza, así que deberías estar agra-!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:380
msgid "CIPHER OF IMMOBILITY!"
msgstr "¡CIFRADO DE INMOVILIDAD!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:394
msgid "Myra, stop!"
msgstr "¡Myra, para!"

#. [message], speaker=Garcyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:398
msgid "W-what has happened?!"
msgstr "¡¿Q-qué ha pasado?!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Myra, erm, has put your friend to sleep for the rest of the night *maybe for "
"the rest of the year...* Now folks, I think it will really be best to camp "
"somewhere nearby."
msgstr ""
"Myra, ehm, ha puesto a tu amigo a dormir por el resto de la noche *tal vez "
"por el resto del año...* Ahora gente, creo que realmente será mejor acampar "
"en algún lugar cercano."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:406
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:259
msgid "I understand..."
msgstr "Entiendo..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:444
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:860
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1069
msgid "Veela, no! Please, don't die, I... I can't go on without you...! NO!"
msgstr "¡Veela, no! ¡Por favor, no mueras, yo… no puedo seguir sin ti…! ¡NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:472
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:888
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1097
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:316
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:718
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1434
msgid "No... father, help-"
msgstr "No… padre, ayúd-"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:486
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:902
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1111
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:330
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:732
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1448
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:601
msgid "I have failed in my duty..."
msgstr "He fallado en mi deber…"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Kiera's commander has died! Now, the village will be defenceless against "
"further attacks, and so the southern Meadows will be at the dragon armies' "
"mercy!"
msgstr ""
"¡El comandante de Kiera ha muerto! ¡Ahora la aldea quedará indefensa ante "
"más ataques, y los Prados del Sur quedarán a merced de los ejércitos de "
"dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/09_Bitter_Return.cfg:511
msgid ""
"We are taking far too much time in this place; will we ever be able to reach "
"our goal and return in time?"
msgstr ""
"Estamos tardando demasiado en este lugar; ¿alguna vez podremos alcanzar "
"nuestro objetivo y regresar a tiempo?"

#. [scenario], id=10_The_Wilderness
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:4
msgid "The Wilderness"
msgstr "La Selva"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:35
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:659
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:750
msgid "Reach the entrance to the caves of Mount Hursag with Myra"
msgstr "Llegar a la entrada de las cuevas del Monte Hursag con Myra"

#. [side], type=Saurian Prophet
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:85
msgid "Krinex"
msgstr "Krinex"

#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:106
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:117
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:128
msgid "Wilderness' Monsters"
msgstr "Monstruos de la Selva"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:400
msgid "So, is this the Wilderness? It's quite a beautiful region, actually."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿esta es la Selva? En realidad es una región bastante hermosa."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:404
msgid ""
"It may be so, but it's like a rose: its beauty hides a lot of sharp thorns, "
"so we must be very careful. This region is inhabited by insectoid monsters, "
"wolf packs, ogre tribes, even drakes have been reported to dwell here in the "
"past."
msgstr ""
"Puede ser, pero es como una rosa: su belleza esconde muchas espinas "
"afiladas, así que debemos ser muy cuidadosos. Esta región está habitada por "
"monstruos insectoides, manadas de lobos, tribus de ogros; incluso se ha "
"informado que dracos vivían aquí en el pasado."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:408
msgid ""
"Hopefully there will be no such report this time... but if there is, my "
"arcane flames are at the ready."
msgstr ""
"Con suerte no habrá tal informe esta vez… pero si lo hay, mis llamas arcanas "
"están listas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Well then, let's move on. DO NOT go out on your own, and stay on guard; I "
"could turn away wild monsters, but it would take too much time and effort, "
"so let's just hack our way through the wilderness."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, sigamos. NO salgáis solos y estad alerta; podría ahuyentar a los "
"monstruos salvajes, pero llevaría demasiado tiempo y esfuerzo, así que "
"simplemente abrámonos paso a través de la selva."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:416
msgid ""
"The river we've seen in Kiera also runs through the Wilderness; when I fled "
"from the village, I stole a small sailboat and went up the river. Next thing "
"I remember was the darkness of Hursag's caves, so, if we follow this river, "
"I'm sure we'll find a way into the mountain."
msgstr ""
"El río que vimos en Kiera también atraviesa la Selva; cuando huí del pueblo, "
"robé un pequeño velero y subí por el río. Lo siguiente que recuerdo es la "
"oscuridad de las cuevas de Hursag, así que, si seguimos este río, estoy "
"segura de que encontraremos una entrada a la montaña."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:420
msgid ""
"It may be a good idea to send a water elemental scouting the river ahead of "
"us; the way through which you entered the mountain may not be accessible "
"anymore, and if we find it out early enough, we may have better conditions "
"to search for another entrance."
msgstr ""
"Puede ser buena idea enviar un elemental de agua a explorar el río delante "
"de nosotros; el camino por el que entraste a la montaña puede que ya no sea "
"accesible, y si lo descubrimos lo bastante pronto, tendremos mejores "
"condiciones para buscar otra entrada."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Here, Myra, I've picked these flowers in a natural garden nearby; let me see "
"how they fit in your hair..."
msgstr ""
"Toma, Myra, he recogido estas flores en un jardín natural cercano; déjame "
"ver cómo te quedan en el pelo…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:443
msgid ""
"Blondie, we're in the middle of the damn Wilderness, and you're worried "
"about picking up flowers?!"
msgstr ""
"Rubiita, ¡estamos en medio de la maldita Selva y tú preocupada por recoger "
"flores!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:447
msgid ""
"(chuckles) But these flowers actually fit you very well, Myra; next time we "
"set camp, we'll craft you a garland, right, Veela?"
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Pero estas flores te quedan muy bien, Myra; la próxima vez que "
"acampemos, te haremos una guirnalda, ¿verdad, Veela?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:451
msgid "Sure!"
msgstr "¡Claro!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:455
msgid "(rolls eyes)"
msgstr "(pone los ojos en blanco)"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:478
msgid ""
"So... Please don't blast me away, but I was pondering on that episode back "
"in Kiera-"
msgstr ""
"Entonces… Por favor no me mandes a volar, pero estaba pensando en aquel "
"episodio en Kiera-"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:482
msgid "Choose your next words carefully."
msgstr "Elige bien tus próximas palabras."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:486
msgid ""
"I only hope you haven't assumed that, because I'm Aragwaithi, I am "
"sympathetic to those villagers in the slightest?"
msgstr ""
"Solo espero que no hayas pensado que, por ser aragwaithi, simpatizo ni un "
"poquito con esos aldeanos."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:490
msgid ""
"So you're not sympathetic to people who treated me like an animal. "
"Congratulations?"
msgstr ""
"Así que no simpatizas con la gente que me trató como a un animal. "
"¿Felicidades?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:494
msgid "I am, however, sympathetic to your anger."
msgstr "Sin embargo, sí simpatizo con tu rabia."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Really? Even when I said I'd rather let them all die? I <i>meant</i> that, "
"you know."
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad? ¿Incluso cuando dije que prefería dejarlos morir a todos? Lo "
"<i>decía</i> en serio, sabes."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:502
msgid ""
"I've never been through what you have, so I'm not one to judge. But what "
"made me become a warrior was the murder of my mother at the hands of the "
"Rebel Lord's thugs; I would have killed them all if I could, and so I "
"believe I understand your feeling... to some extent at least."
msgstr ""
"Nunca he pasado por lo que tú, así que no soy quién para juzgarte. Pero lo "
"que me convirtió en guerrero fue el asesinato de mi madre a manos de los "
"matones del Señor Rebelde; los habría matado a todos si hubiera podido, y "
"por eso creo que entiendo tu sentimiento… al menos en parte."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:506
msgid ""
"I heard of that, but I thought his devastation affected mostly the "
"countryside..."
msgstr ""
"Escuché sobre eso, pero pensaba que su devastación afectaba sobre todo al "
"campo…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:510
msgid ""
"It did, but my mother was kin to the Rebel Lord, and she believed she could "
"sway him to stop his folly before it caused bloodshed. As it turned out, "
"hers was the first to be shed."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero mi madre era pariente del Señor Rebelde y creía que podía "
"convencerlo de detener su locura antes de que causara derramamiento de "
"sangre. Al final, la suya fue la primera en derramarse."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:514
msgid "I... I'm sorry about that."
msgstr "Yo… Lo siento mucho."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:518
msgid "As I'm sorry about what that village made you go through."
msgstr "Como yo lo siento por lo que ese pueblo te hizo pasar."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:553
msgid "Myra, is it my impression, or there is something wrong here...?"
msgstr "Myra, ¿es impresión mía o hay algo raro aquí…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:557
msgid ""
"No, I too sense it: many beast packs are coming with sunrise. Be on guard, "
"you all."
msgstr ""
"No, yo también lo siento: muchas manadas de bestias vienen con el amanecer. "
"Estad alerta, todos."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:561
msgid "From which side will they come?"
msgstr "¿De qué lado vendrán?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:565
msgid "Everywhere."
msgstr "De todos lados."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:569
msgid "(gulp)"
msgstr "(traga saliva)"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:646
msgid "As expected, Shek'har's forces have already reached this region."
msgstr ""
"Como era de esperar, las fuerzas de Shek’har ya han llegado a esta región."

#. [message], speaker=Krinex
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:650
msgid ""
"Hissss! There comes a human patrol led by the despicable daughter of the "
"High Ascendant. Chop her companions down, my minions, but capture her alive; "
"Master Assix has some business with her."
msgstr ""
"¡Hisssss! Ahí viene una patrulla humana liderada por la despreciable hija de "
"la Gran Ascendente. ¡Cortad a sus compañeros en pedazos, mis súbditos, pero "
"capturadla viva; el maestro Assix tiene asuntos pendientes con ella!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:654
msgid "Let's just send these annoying fellows to the world of the dead."
msgstr "Simplemente mandemos a estos molestos tipos al mundo de los muertos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:663
msgid "Kill Krinex"
msgstr "Matar a Krinex"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:703
msgid ""
"There is a way into the mountain here, but the water's too deep for anyone "
"other than Razorbirds and water elementals to pass."
msgstr ""
"Aquí hay un camino hacia la montaña, pero el agua es demasiado profunda para "
"cualquiera que no sean aves navaja o elementales de agua."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:707
msgid ""
"Let's keep searching; there must be another entrance in the middle of this "
"forest, or my mother wouldn't have entered the caves either."
msgstr ""
"Seguimos buscando; tiene que haber otra entrada en medio de este bosque, o "
"mi madre tampoco habría entrado en las cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Krinex
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:718
msgid "Hisssss! Flee, my bat, and give Assix..."
msgstr "¡Hisssss! ¡Huye, murciélago mío, y dile a Assix…!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:722
msgid "Just shut your stinking mouth!"
msgstr "¡Cierra esa boca apestosa!"

#. [message], speaker=Krinex
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:726
msgid "Gaaahh!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Gaaahh!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:736
msgid "But the bat still escaped... Where is it going?"
msgstr "Pero el murciélago escapó… ¿Adónde va?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:740
msgid ""
"Probably alert Assix that his serf has perished. As much as I'd love to "
"blast that disgusting lizard, we must leave this place quickly, for we "
"cannot fight a force much larger than our own, not now."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente a avisar a Assix de que su siervo ha muerto. Por mucho que me "
"encantaría reventar a ese lagarto asqueroso, debemos abandonar este lugar "
"rápido, porque no podemos luchar contra una fuerza mucho mayor que la "
"nuestra, no ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:744
msgid "Wise words. Now, onwards to Mount Hursag!"
msgstr "Palabras sabias. ¡Ahora, hacia el Monte Hursag!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:789
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:809
msgid "Now, let's find the Fountain..."
msgstr "Ahora, busquemos la Fuente…"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:818
msgid "I think we should kill this saurian before going into the mountain."
msgstr "Creo que deberíamos matar a este saurio antes de entrar en la montaña."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/10_The_Wilderness.cfg:913
msgid ""
"Damn it, many days have passed already, and we still haven't reached Mount "
"Hursag! At this pace, we will return to Garet-Desh only to see it burning!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, han pasado muchos días y aún no hemos llegado al Monte Hursag! "
"¡A este paso, volveremos a Garet-Desh solo para verla arder!"

#. [scenario], id=11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:4
msgid "Legend Of The Water Dragon"
msgstr "Leyenda del Dragón del Agua"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:18
msgid "Find the Fountain of Life"
msgstr "Encontrar la Fuente de la Vida"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:70
msgid "Grokk"
msgstr "Grokk"

#. [side], type=Troll Shaman
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:88
msgid "Ag"
msgstr "Ag"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:188
msgid ""
"So this is the cave where the fabled Fountain is hidden? It seems quite "
"common for me."
msgstr ""
"¿Así que esta es la cueva donde se esconde la legendaria Fuente? A mí me "
"parece bastante normal."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:192
msgid ""
"That's because you have no magical sensibility. I can sense it, deep inside "
"the mountain, near its top: there is a strange source of energy there, an "
"energy that is now faint, but whose former intensity may still be noticed."
msgstr ""
"Es porque no tienes sensibilidad mágica. Yo la siento, en lo profundo de la "
"montaña, cerca de su cima: hay una extraña fuente de energía allí, una "
"energía ahora débil, pero cuya intensidad pasada aún se nota."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:196
msgid ""
"I can't sense it, but I hear the sound of running water; the Fountain is "
"certainly here."
msgstr ""
"Yo no la siento, pero oigo el sonido del agua corriendo; la Fuente está sin "
"duda aquí."

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:200
msgid ""
"Searching for this Fountain is a task for us dwarves; we can move far "
"quicker in these tunnels, so we should go ahead and see what we find. Who "
"knows what kind of dangers lurks here."
msgstr ""
"Buscar esta Fuente es tarea para nosotros los enanos; nos movemos mucho más "
"rápido en estos túneles, así que deberíamos ir por delante y ver qué "
"encontramos. Quién sabe qué clase de peligros acechan aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:204
msgid ""
"Ah, I'd thought these caves were safe, since they shelter the Fountain of "
"Life. And Myra managed to live here for weeks undisturbed, right Myra?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, pensaba que estas cuevas eran seguras, ya que albergan la Fuente de la "
"Vida. Y Myra logró vivir aquí durante semanas sin ser molestada, ¿verdad "
"Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:208
msgid ""
"Yes, but I was just a young, powerless girl then, and so I was no threat to "
"whoever dwells here. However, it is a military force that is entering the "
"caves now. Alenya is right, be prepared for whatever comes..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero entonces era solo una niña joven y sin poder, y no representaba "
"amenaza para quienquiera que viva aquí. Sin embargo, ahora es una fuerza "
"militar la que entra en las cuevas. Alenya tiene razón, estad preparados "
"para lo que sea…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:222
msgid ""
"See? We were not alone. But maybe these trolls are friendly, like those of "
"the Windy Mountains..."
msgstr ""
"¿Veis? No estábamos solos. Pero tal vez estos trolls sean amistosos, como "
"los de las Montañas Ventosas…"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:226
msgid "Ha, fresh meat! I didn't eat fresh meat in ages!"
msgstr "¡Ja, carne fresca! ¡Hace siglos que no como carne fresca!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:230
msgid "...or maybe not."
msgstr "…o tal vez no."

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Ah, I was getting bored of fighting puny saurians and frail skeletons! Now "
"there comes a real opponent!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, estaba aburrido de luchar contra saurios enclenques y esqueletos "
"frágiles! ¡Ahora llega un rival de verdad!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:310
msgid "It's... it's..."
msgstr "Es… es…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:314
msgid "<i>The Fountain of Life</i>! It... really is true!"
msgstr "¡<i>La Fuente de la Vida</i>! ¡Es… es verdad!"

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:318
msgid ""
"(falling on his knees) And this is the dragon who sacrificed himself to save "
"our world...! I have never bowed to anyone in my entire life, not even to "
"Lord Auroghar; but I bow to the magnificence of the Water Dragon..."
msgstr ""
"(cayendo de rodillas) ¡Y este es el dragón que se sacrificó para salvar "
"nuestro mundo…! Nunca me he inclinado ante nadie en toda mi vida, ni "
"siquiera ante lord Auroghar; pero me inclino ante la magnificencia del "
"Dragón del Agua…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Now, if I remember it well, Myra must try and communicate with nature's "
"spirits. Let's leave her alone, so that she may concentrate on her task."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, si lo recuerdo bien, Myra debe intentar comunicarse con los espíritus "
"de la naturaleza. Dejémosla sola para que pueda concentrarse en su tarea."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:326
msgid "(looks at Jevyan with gratitude)"
msgstr "(mira a Jevyan con gratitud)"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Fair enough. We shall guard all the tunnels leading to this chamber, to "
"protect Lady Myra from any undesired visitor."
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo. Vigilaremos todos los túneles que llevan a esta cámara para "
"proteger a lady Myra de cualquier visitante indeseado."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Once everyone left the chamber, Myra slowly entered the pool, shivering at "
"the cold of the waters, but also feeling somehow invigorated. Her heart beat "
"frantically as she moved further into the pool, her eyes fixed at the fallen "
"dragon, a strange feeling of satisfaction and pleasure taking her body. Such "
"was her pleasure that she nearly forgot what she was supposed to do; she "
"started communicating with the spirits similarly to the way she communicated "
"with her elementals, but to no avail. Then, as she tried to figure out a way "
"of talking to them, she suddenly fell unconscious, and her body was left "
"floating on its back over the water..."
msgstr ""
"Cuando todos salieron de la cámara, Myra entró lentamente en la poza, "
"tiritando por el frío del agua, pero sintiéndose también de alguna forma "
"vigorizada. Su corazón latía con fuerza mientras avanzaba más en la poza, "
"con los ojos fijos en el dragón caído, una extraña sensación de satisfacción "
"y placer invadiendo su cuerpo. Tal era su placer que casi olvidó lo que "
"debía hacer; intentó comunicarse con los espíritus de forma similar a como "
"lo hacía con sus elementales, pero sin éxito. Entonces, mientras buscaba la "
"forma de hablarles, cayó de repente inconsciente y su cuerpo quedó flotando "
"boca arriba sobre el agua…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:367
msgid "What... Who... Where am I?"
msgstr "¿Qué… Quién… Dónde estoy?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:371
msgid "<i>In Dreamland, where else?</i>"
msgstr "<i>En la Tierra de los Sueños, ¿dónde si no?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:375
msgid "Dreamland... So I'm asleep?"
msgstr "Tierra de los Sueños… ¿Entonces estoy dormida?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:379
msgid "<i>Yes, how else?</i>"
msgstr "<i>Sí, ¿cómo si no?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:383
msgid ""
"But I can't possibly sleep now, my friends are waiting for me... And who are "
"you anyway?"
msgstr ""
"Pero no puedo dormir ahora, mis amigos me están esperando… ¿Y quiénes sois, "
"por cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:387
msgid "<i>We are no one and everyone, who else?</i>"
msgstr "<i>Somos nadie y todos, ¿quién si no?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:391
msgid ""
"How can you be 'no one and everyone'? No, wait... You have no name, or have "
"many names, right?"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo podéis ser «nadie y todos»? No, espera… No tenéis nombre, o tenéis "
"muchos nombres, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:395
msgid "<i>Yes...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Sí…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:399
msgid "You are a bodiless being, a presence... You are spirits of nature!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sois un ser sin cuerpo, una presencia… Sois los espíritus de la naturaleza!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:403
msgid ""
"<i>We </i>are<i> Nature, my child. No, more than that, we are the soul of "
"Irdya, the original spark that gave rise to Life itself.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Nosotros </i>somos<i> la Naturaleza, hija mía. No, más aún, somos el alma "
"de Irdya, la chispa original que dio lugar a la Vida misma.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:407
msgid "Great! But how did I manage to contact you all of a sudden? Unless..."
msgstr ""
"¡Genial! Pero ¿cómo he logrado contactar con vosotros de repente? A menos "
"que…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:411
msgid ""
"<i>We were the ones who called out to you. We wanted you to come here, for "
"your ears are the ones most fitting to hear us, even more than those of your "
"foster mother, the High Ascendant.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Fuimos nosotros quienes te llamamos. Queríamos que vinieras aquí, porque "
"tus oídos son los más adecuados para escucharnos, incluso más que los de tu "
"madre adoptiva, la Gran Ascendente.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:415
msgid "So you already know what is happening right now, and why I came here?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces ya sabéis lo que está pasando ahora y por qué he venido aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:419
msgid ""
"<i>We know that the Destroyer has risen again, awakened by that foolish "
"Shek'har, who wants to see his own people rule the world as they did in the "
"past. However, he ignores the fact that the Destroyer has no intention of "
"recreating the Dragon Age: his only goal is to extinguish all life on Irdya; "
"in other words, to destroy our precious children, the living beings of this "
"world.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Sabemos que el Destructor ha vuelto a alzarse, despertado por ese necio "
"Shek’har, que quiere ver a su pueblo gobernar el mundo como en el pasado. "
"Sin embargo, ignora que el Destructor no pretende recrear la Era de los "
"Dragones: su único objetivo es extinguir toda vida en Irdya; en otras "
"palabras, destruir a nuestros preciosos hijos, los seres vivos de este mundo."
"</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:423
msgid ""
"But... you're powerful, aren't you? So why don't you kill Svarballi yourself?"
msgstr ""
"Pero… sois poderosos, ¿verdad? Entonces ¿por qué no matáis a Svarballi "
"vosotros mismos?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:427
msgid ""
"<i>You have answered it already. We are a bodiless being, and, although we "
"can influence and control most beings - namely the ones whose minds are less "
"burdened - we cannot take a form of our own without a summoner's aid. And "
"most importantly: even if we could create a single physical body of our own, "
"it would be incapable of sustaining our full energy without crumbling to "
"dust. But we are essentially energy, and this we can channel through a "
"vessel: a being whose ears can hear our voice.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Tú misma lo has respondido. Somos un ser sin cuerpo y, aunque podemos "
"influir y controlar a la mayoría de seres —especialmente aquellos cuyas "
"mentes están menos cargadas—, no podemos tomar forma propia sin la ayuda de "
"un invocador. Y lo más importante: incluso si pudiéramos crear un solo "
"cuerpo físico propio, sería incapaz de sostener toda nuestra energía sin "
"explotar. Pero nosotros somos esencialmente energía, y esta podemos "
"canalizarla a través de un recipiente: un ser cuyos oídos puedan escuchar "
"nuestra voz.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Then, someone who has an affinity with you can use your powers... Was that "
"what you did with Agniballi and Nitiballi, ages ago?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, alguien que tenga afinidad con vosotros puede usar vuestros "
"poderes… ¿Eso fue lo que hicisteis con Agniballi y Nitiballi hace eras?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:435
msgid ""
"<i>Precisely. As they were, they could not hope to defeat the Destroyer, but "
"then we gave them access to our power; and, drawing from it, they managed to "
"defeat their foe. Nitiballi was grievously wounded, and even though he could "
"heal himself he chose to spread his healing waters throughout the world, to "
"restore natural life. For this, he drew upon our full energy, which "
"empowered his healing waters immensely; so much, in fact, that even "
"nowadays, thousands of years later, they still conserve some of their power. "
"And it was this power that you also absorbed as you bathed and drank from it "
"for so many weeks.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Exacto. Tal como estaban, no podían esperar derrotar al Destructor, pero "
"entonces les dimos acceso a nuestro poder; y, extrayéndolo, lograron vencer "
"a su enemigo. Nitiballi quedó gravemente herido, y aunque podía curarse a sí "
"mismo, eligió extender sus aguas curativas por todo el mundo para restaurar "
"la vida natural. Para ello, extrajo toda nuestra energía, lo que potenció "
"inmensamente sus aguas curativas; tanto, que incluso hoy en día, miles de "
"años después, aún conservan parte de su poder. Y ese poder también lo "
"absorbiste tú al bañarte y beber de ellas durante tantas semanas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:439
msgid ""
"But these waters have spread throughout the world, so many other beings must "
"have absorbed their power as well, correct?"
msgstr ""
"Pero estas aguas se han extendido por todo el mundo, así que muchos otros "
"seres deben haber absorbido su poder también, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:443
msgid ""
"<i>You didn't pay full attention to what I said. You </i>also<i> absorbed "
"the waters' healing powers, which kept you alive for all those weeks. "
"However, you also absorbed a small remnant of Nitiballi's own soul, which "
"was lingering here, in his tomb. Even we did not expect that, but we seized "
"the chance to bond with you, since the Water Dragon's soul was already "
"bonded with us. The other beings which live in these caves could have drunk "
"it too, it's true; and they actually did drink these waters in the past. But "
"they've learned that drinking it is, for them, like drinking death; just as "
"the sun gives life, but can burn you should you fly too close to it.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>No prestaste toda la atención a lo que dije. Tú </i>también<i> absorbiste "
"los poderes curativos de las aguas, que te mantuvieron viva durante todas "
"esas semanas. Sin embargo, también absorbiste un pequeño remanente del alma "
"del propio Nitiballi, que estaba aquí, en su tumba. Ni siquiera nosotros lo "
"esperábamos, pero aprovechamos la oportunidad para unirnos a ti, ya que el "
"alma del Dragón del Agua ya estaba unida a nosotros. Es cierto que los otros "
"seres que viven en estas cuevas podrían haberla bebido también; y de hecho "
"bebieron estas aguas en el pasado. Pero aprendieron que beberla es, para "
"ellos, como beber muerte; igual que el sol da vida, pero te quema si vuelas "
"demasiado cerca de él.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:447
msgid "So why was I able to drink it?"
msgstr "¿Entonces por qué pude beberla yo?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:451
msgid ""
"<i>You were but a helpless child then, shunned by your fellow humans, "
"desperate for protection and care; and Nitiballi, as you may have noticed "
"from his legend, was a compassionate dragon who cared deeply about weaker "
"beings, especially those with a pure heart. You weren't the first to drink "
"from this Fountain, but that remnant of Nitiballi's soul... you were the "
"only one to be embraced by it, and thus you were protected from these "
"waters' overwhelming power.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Entonces eras solo una niña indefensa, rechazada por tus congéneres "
"humanos, desesperada por protección y cuidado; y Nitiballi, como habrás "
"notado por su leyenda, era un dragón compasivo que se preocupaba "
"profundamente por los seres más débiles, especialmente los de corazón puro. "
"No fuiste la primera en beber de esta Fuente, pero ese remanente del alma de "
"Nitiballi… tú fuiste la única que fue acogida por él, y por eso quedaste "
"protegida del abrumador poder de estas aguas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:455
msgid ""
"I see... That certainly enlightens many questions I've always had about "
"myself... but there are other questions I must enlighten - and far more "
"important ones."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Eso aclara muchas preguntas que siempre tuve sobre mí misma… pero "
"hay otras preguntas que debo aclarar —y mucho más importantes."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:459
msgid ""
"<i>Both Agniballi and Nitiballi saw that, in spite of all their newly gained "
"power, they could not ultimately kill Svarballi, who was endowed with the "
"power of the beings you call the Ancient Ones themselves. Therefore, they "
"destroyed his body and then sealed his soul in a magical prison. "
"Unfortunately, we cannot explain how they created this prison, though the "
"wise High Ascendant certainly knows.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Tanto Agniballi como Nitiballi vieron que, a pesar de todo el poder "
"recién adquirido, no podían matar definitivamente a Svarballi, que estaba "
"dotado con el poder de los seres que llamáis los Antiguos. Por eso "
"destruyeron su cuerpo y luego sellaron su alma en una prisión mágica. "
"Desgraciadamente, no podemos explicar cómo crearon esa prisión, aunque la "
"sabia Gran Ascendente sin duda lo sabe.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:463
msgid ""
"But if we seal him, he may be able to break free one day and unleash "
"destruction again, right? Isn't there any way to put a definitive end to "
"his...?"
msgstr ""
"Pero si lo sellamos, podría liberarse algún día y volver a desatar la "
"destrucción, ¿verdad? ¿No hay forma de ponerle un fin definitivo a su…?"

#. [unit], id=Arix, type=Saurian Flanker
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:514
msgid "Arix"
msgstr "Arix"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:566
msgid "What is- You!"
msgstr "¡Qué es- ¡Tú!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:570
msgid "Surprised, human girl?"
msgstr "¿Sorpresa, niña humana?"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:574
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, Myra, they came too silently, and we only noticed their presence "
"when it was too late..."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, Myra, llegaron demasiado silenciosos y solo notamos su presencia "
"cuando ya era tarde…"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:578
msgid ""
"It iss unfortunately true that saurianss are... frail if compared to "
"drakess, dwarvess or trollss. To compensate our weakness, however, we "
"improved our agility and speed, and so we became as imponderable as a shadow "
"in the night. Thus we caught your petty friendss off guard and tied them!"
msgstr ""
"Es lamentablemente cierto que los saurios somos… frágiles comparados con "
"dracos, enanos o trolls. Sin embargo, para compensar nuestra debilidad "
"mejoramos nuestra agilidad y velocidad, y así nos volvimos tan impredecibles "
"como una sombra en la noche. ¡Por eso pillamos desprevenidos a tus "
"insignificantes amigos y los atamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:582
msgid ""
"I should've expected that from sneaky bastards like you; after all, that was "
"how you managed to slid into Hiera'Shirsha's Library to steal the Book of "
"the Dead..."
msgstr ""
"Debería haberlo esperado de bastardos sigilosos como vosotros; al fin y al "
"cabo, así fue como lograsteis colaros en la Biblioteca de Hiera’Shirsha para "
"robar el Libro de los Muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:586
msgid "How did you know...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo lo sabías…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:590
msgid "Ah, so you did steal that book in particular..."
msgstr "Ah, así que sí robasteis ese libro en particular…"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:594
msgid ""
"You... petulant, annoying little girl! You are quite bold for someone who "
"iss surrounded, and whose friendss are all in the handss of the enemy. But I "
"don't want to taint the sacred Fountain of Life with the dirty blood of "
"humanss, so you just have to tell me what your business here iss, what these "
"waterss do, and also something I have craved to know since the fall of your "
"puny city: how do you manage to control those elemental beastss?"
msgstr ""
"Tú… ¡niña petulante e insufrible! Eres bastante audaz para alguien que está "
"rodeada y cuyas amigas están todas en manos del enemigo. Pero no quiero "
"manchar la sagrada Fuente de la Vida con la sucia sangre humana, así que "
"solo tienes que decirme qué hacéis aquí, qué hacen estas aguas y también "
"algo que ansío saber desde la caída de tu insignificante ciudad: ¿cómo "
"logras controlar a esas bestias elementales?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:598
msgid "Don't tell him, Myra!"
msgstr "¡No se lo digas, Myra!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:602
msgid "Ssomeone silence her!"
msgstr "¡Que alguien la calle!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:609
msgid "No! Wait, I'll tell you everything, just don't harm my friends!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Espera, te lo contaré todo, solo no hagáis daño a mis amigas!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:613
msgid "Yess, that iss better! Now, start speaking!"
msgstr "¡Sí, eso está mejor! ¡Ahora, empieza a hablar!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:617
msgid ""
"I have been here already, as a child; I'd gotten lost, and found this cave "
"by accident. I drank these waters and bathed in them for a long time, until "
"High Ascendant Maat found me. She believes that my prolonged exposition to "
"the Fountain's waters gave me my powers over the elementals."
msgstr ""
"Ya estuve aquí de niña; me perdí y encontré esta cueva por accidente. Bebí "
"estas aguas y me bañé en ellas durante mucho tiempo, hasta que la Gran "
"Ascendente Maat me encontró. Ella cree que mi prolongada exposición a las "
"aguas de la Fuente me dio mis poderes sobre los elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:621
msgid "Interesting... But you musst still tell me what are you doing here?"
msgstr "Interesante… Pero aún debes decirme qué hacéis aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:625
msgid ""
"My... mother believes that, if I exposed myself to these water for a longer "
"time, I'd be able to absorb all its power: the power with which Nitiballi "
"defeated Svarballi long ago."
msgstr ""
"Mi… madre cree que, si me expongo a estas aguas durante más tiempo, podré "
"absorber todo su poder: el poder con el que Nitiballi derrotó a Svarballi "
"hace tanto."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:629
msgid ""
"So... If you had drunk these waterss, you would have become stronger than "
"the Sky Dragon? You really expect me to believe such silliness?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces… ¿Si hubieras bebido estas aguas te habrías vuelto más fuerte que "
"el Dragón del Cielo? ¿De verdad esperas que crea tal tontería?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:633
msgid ""
"Not stronger, no; I... I was to absorb Nitiballi's power, and then, together "
"with the High Ascendant's power, we hoped to... we hoped to be able to "
"vanquish Svarballi, like Agniballi and Nitiballi in the past."
msgstr ""
"No más fuerte, no; yo… iba a absorber el poder de Nitiballi y luego, junto "
"con el poder de la Gran Ascendente, esperábamos… esperábamos poder vencer a "
"Svarballi, como Agniballi y Nitiballi en el pasado."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:637
msgid ""
"So that's it! I have unraveled our enemy's entire plan! I would be immensely "
"rewarded by Lord Shek'har, but... If I became as powerful as the Water "
"Dragon, together with the power given me by the Book of the Dead, I might as "
"well overthrow Shek'har, maybe even the Sky Dragon himself, and then... and "
"then rule thiss world myself!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que eso es! ¡He desentrañado todo el plan del enemigo! Lord Shek’har me "
"recompensaría inmensamente, pero… Si me vuelvo tan poderoso como el Dragón "
"del Agua, junto con el poder que me da el Libro de los Muertos, podría "
"derrocar a Shek’har, ¡quizá incluso al propio Dragón del Cielo, y luego… y "
"luego gobernar este mundo yo mismo!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:641
msgid ""
"Don't be ridiculous, even if you absorb Nitiballi's strength you would still "
"need another great power to face him!"
msgstr ""
"No seas ridículo, aunque absorbas la fuerza de Nitiballi aún necesitarías "
"otro gran poder para enfrentarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:645
msgid ""
"I doubt that even the Sky Dragon can easily defeat an undead army composed "
"of all fallen warriorss from all erass! And besidess, who know what new "
"artss I can find in the bookss I collected from your Library... Now, stand "
"aside, that I shall bathe in these waterss. Enjoy well the time you have "
"left, for I shall test my new powerss in you; thiss iss how I honour your "
"valour."
msgstr ""
"Dudo que ni siquiera el Dragón del Cielo pueda derrotar fácilmente a un "
"ejército de no muertos compuesto por todos los guerreros caídos de todas las "
"eras. Y además, quién sabe qué nuevas artes puedo encontrar en los libros "
"que recogí de vuestra Biblioteca… Ahora, apartaos, que voy a bañarme en "
"estas aguas. Disfrutad bien el tiempo que os queda, porque probaré mis "
"nuevos poderes en vosotros; así honro vuestro valor."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:649
msgid "Myra, please do something to stop him!"
msgstr "¡Myra, por favor haz algo para detenerlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:653
msgid "There is nothing we can do now, blondie. We... we have lost this time."
msgstr ""
"No hay nada que podamos hacer ahora, rubia. Nosotros… hemos perdido esta vez."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:660
msgid ""
"Consternated, the friends watched as Assix took off his dark robes and "
"jumped in the pool, drinking mouthfuls of its water, squealing in "
"anticipation of his promised new powers. However, not a minute had passed "
"since he'd dived in the fountain, when he choked strangely; then, his eyes "
"became horribly injected, his scales bristled and then fell off, blood "
"gushed out of his ears and mouth, and his flesh melted as if he had jumped "
"into a pool of acid..."
msgstr ""
"Consternados, los amigos vieron cómo Assix se quitaba sus túnicas oscuras y "
"saltaba a la poza, bebiendo tragos de su agua y chillando de anticipación "
"ante sus prometidos nuevos poderes. Sin embargo, no había pasado ni un "
"minuto desde que se sumergió en la fuente cuando empezó a ahogarse de forma "
"extraña; luego sus ojos se inyectaron de sangre, sus escamas se erizaron y "
"cayeron, la sangre brotó de sus orejas y boca, y su carne se derritió como "
"si hubiera saltado a una poza de ácido…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:685
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:233
msgid "What the..."
msgstr "Qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:689
msgid ""
"Forgot to mention, these waters are poison to those who drink straight from "
"their fountain. Now, friends, our turn!"
msgstr ""
"Olvidé mencionar que estas aguas son veneno para quien bebe directamente de "
"su fuente. ¡Ahora, amigos, nuestro turno!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:737
msgid "Move Myra back to her keep (34,3)"
msgstr "Llevar a Myra de vuelta a su torreón (34,3)"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:787
msgid "We're almost there! Just a little longer, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Ya casi estamos! ¡Solo un poco más, amigos!"

#. [unit], id=Anexir, type=Saurian Flanker
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:796
msgid "Anexir"
msgstr "Anexir"

#. [message], speaker=Anexir
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:800
msgid "Masster Assix iss dead, but you shall accompany him to the other world!"
msgstr ""
"¡El maestro Assix ha muerto, pero vosotros lo acompañaréis al otro mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:824
msgid "Veela...!"
msgstr "¡Veela…!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:832
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/34_Last_Revelations.cfg:70
msgid "You..."
msgstr "Tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:862
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/34_Last_Revelations.cfg:279
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:1111
msgid "Myra..."
msgstr "Myra…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:866
msgid "Stop talking, girl, or you will get tired..."
msgstr "Deja de hablar, chica, o te cansarás…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:870
msgid ""
"I'm dizzy... I think that spear was poisoned, and it hit me in the heart..."
msgstr "Me mareo… Creo que el dardo estaba envenenado y me dio en el corazón…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:874
msgid ""
"Of course it's not poisoned, what do you understand of poisons? I... I know! "
"I will take you back to the Fountain; its waters will surely heal you."
msgstr ""
"¡Claro que no está envenenada, qué sabes tú de venenos! Yo… ¡Ya sé! Te "
"llevaré de vuelta a la Fuente; sus aguas seguro que te curan."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:878
msgid "I thought only those pure of heart could drink it..."
msgstr "Pensaba que solo los de corazón puro podían beberla…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:882
msgid ""
"But you are pure! If even a callous woman like me could drink the water, I'm "
"sure a kind-hearted girl like you will be able to drink mouthfuls of it..."
msgstr ""
"¡Pero tú eres pura! Si hasta una mujer dura como yo pudo beber el agua, "
"estoy segura de que una chica de buen corazón como tú podrá beber tragos "
"enteros…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:886
msgid "You're not... callous... You're my... dear friend..."
msgstr "No eres… dura… Eres mi… querida amiga…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:890
msgid "And you're the best friend I've ever had, now please, let's..."
msgstr "Y tú eres la mejor amiga que he tenido, ahora por favor, vamos…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:894
msgid ""
"(laughing and crying) And this is the first time you said I'm your friend... "
"And the <i>very best one</i>... By Heaven, now I may die happy..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo y llorando) Y esta es la primera vez que dices que soy tu amiga… y "
"la <i>mejor</i>… Por el Cielo, ahora puedo morir feliz…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:898
msgid "(in despair) YOU WILL NOT DIE, ARE YOU LISTENING?"
msgstr "(desesperada) ¡NO VAS A MORIR, ME ESTÁS ESCUCHANDO?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:902
msgid ""
"Go... I will stay behind and destroy the caves... so the saurians won't... "
"escape..."
msgstr ""
"Vete… Yo me quedaré atrás y destruiré las cuevas… para que los saurios no… "
"escapen…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:906
msgid "No way I'm leaving..."
msgstr "De ninguna manera me voy a ir…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:910
msgid "Cipher of Immobility!"
msgstr "¡Cifrado de Inmovilidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:923
msgid "See, I do know how to cast a Cipher of Immobility... Jevyan!"
msgstr "Mira, sí sé lanzar un Cifrado de Inmovilidad… ¡Jevyan!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:927
msgid "W-what?"
msgstr "¿Q-qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:931
msgid ""
"Please... take her and the others out. I'm doomed, but... I can still do "
"something for... all of you."
msgstr ""
"Por favor… sácala a ella y a los demás. Yo estoy perdida, pero… aún puedo "
"hacer algo por… todos vosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:935
msgid "I... I shall do as you ask..."
msgstr "Yo… Haré lo que pides…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:955
msgid "Now, Ci-"
msgstr "Ahora, Ci-"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:964
msgid "Cipher-"
msgstr "Cif-"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:973
msgid "CIPHER OF DESTRUCTION!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡CIFRADO DE DESTRUCCIÓN!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/11_Legend_Of_The_Water_Dragon.cfg:1122
msgid "At this pace, we will return to Garet-Desh only to see it burning!"
msgstr "¡A este paso, volveremos a Garet-Desh solo para verla arder!"

#. [scenario], id=12_Burning_Revenge
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:4
msgid "Burning Revenge"
msgstr "Venganza Ardiente"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:20
msgid "Kill Lados with Myra"
msgstr "Matar a Lados con Myra"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:40
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:40
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:448
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:39
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:814
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:25
msgid "Death of Varthan"
msgstr "Muerte de Varthan"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:44
msgid "Death of King Gaeth"
msgstr "Muerte del rey Gaeth"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Captain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:83
msgid "King Gaeth"
msgstr "Rey Gaeth"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Captain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:88
msgid "Kingdom of Alancyn"
msgstr "Reino de Alancyn"

#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:103
msgid "Lados"
msgstr "Lados"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Flagbearer
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:127
msgid "Aravyn"
msgstr "Aravyn"

#. [message], speaker=King Gaeth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:173
msgid ""
"At long last! The reinforcements promised by Lord Abhai have arrived, and "
"they bring the daughter of the High Ascendant with them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! ¡Han llegado los refuerzos prometidos por lord Abhai, y traen "
"consigo a la hija de la Gran Ascendente!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:177
msgid ""
"My subordinate, Flagbearer Aravyn, will aid in Alancyn's defence, so we must "
"focus on killing Lados."
msgstr ""
"Mi subordinado, el abanderado Aravyn, ayudará en la defensa de Alancyn, así "
"que debemos concentrarnos en matar a Lados."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:181
msgid "I understand."
msgstr "Entiendo."

#. [message], speaker=Lados
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:185
msgid ""
"Look, yonder comes the famous Myra! Assix was a fool for being defeated by "
"such a brat, but we must not underestimate her forces."
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad, allá viene la famosa Myra! Assix fue un necio al dejarse derrotar "
"por una mocosa así, ¡pero no debemos subestimar sus fuerzas!"

#. [message], speaker=Lados
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:199
msgid "How could this...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo ha podido ser…?"

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:207
msgid ""
"General Lados is dead, and our forces are being routed. Let's retreat and "
"regroup!"
msgstr ""
"¡El general Lados está muerto y nuestras fuerzas están siendo derrotadas! "
"¡Retirémonos y reagrupémonos!"

#. [message], speaker=King Gaeth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:214
msgid ""
"So the rumours of young Myra's power were true after all! Like mother, like "
"daughter!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que los rumores sobre el poder de la joven Myra eran ciertos después de "
"todo! ¡De tal palo, tal astilla!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:218
msgid ""
"It was a great battle indeed, Myra, but that certainly won't be the last; I "
"intend on patrolling the northern Meadows, assisting other kingdoms in "
"holding off the dragons' attack, and I expect you to march alongside me "
"again."
msgstr ""
"Fue una gran batalla, Myra, pero seguro que no será la última; pienso "
"patrullar los Prados del norte, ayudando a otros reinos a contener el ataque "
"de los dragones, y espero que marches a mi lado otra vez."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:222
msgid "And it shall be so."
msgstr "Y así será."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Should we risk ourselves this much? After all, your mother needs you to "
"fight the Sky Dragon."
msgstr ""
"¿Deberíamos arriesgarnos tanto? Al fin y al cabo, tu madre te necesita para "
"luchar contra el Dragón del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:230
msgid ""
"I will not fall before facing Svarballi, this I can assure you. Now, if you "
"want to return to Garet-Desh, you're free to go; however, if you want to "
"follow me, then we'll do things my way."
msgstr ""
"No caeré antes de enfrentar a Svarballi, eso te lo puedo asegurar. Ahora, si "
"quieres volver a Garet-Desh, eres libre de irte; pero si quieres seguirme, "
"entonces haremos las cosas a mi manera."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:234
msgid "(rolling eyes discreetly) As you say, commander..."
msgstr "(poniendo los ojos en blanco discretamente) Como digas, comandante…"

#. [message], speaker=Lados
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Fools! I am the Beast of the Death Desert! Do you really think that puny "
"weaklings like you can defeat me?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Necios! ¡Soy la Bestia del Desierto de la Muerte! ¡¿De verdad creéis que "
"debiluchos insignificantes como vosotros podéis derrotarme?!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:263
msgid "Stand aside, he's mine!"
msgstr "¡Atrás, es mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:274
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:676
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1374
msgid "How can I fall without avenging Veela...?!"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo caer sin haber vengado a Veela…?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:288
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:690
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"I have fallen; now, who will succeed my father as the King of Garet-Desh...?"
msgstr "He caído; ahora, ¿quién sucederá a mi padre como Rey de Garet-Desh…?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Damn it! Without Gaeth's leadership, Alancyn will be defenceless against the "
"dragons - and without Alancyn, the northern Meadows will be at the lizards' "
"mercy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición! ¡Sin el liderazgo de Gaeth, Alancyn quedará indefensa ante los "
"dragones y sin Alancyn, los Prados del norte estarán a merced de los "
"lagartos!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/12_Burning_Revenge.cfg:355
msgid ""
"We were unable to defeat Lados in time, now more dragon armies loom in the "
"west! There is no hope for victory now!"
msgstr ""
"No pudimos derrotar a Lados a tiempo, ¡ahora más ejércitos de dragones se "
"acercan por el oeste! ¡Ya no hay esperanza de victoria!"

#. [scenario], id=13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:4
msgid "Twilight Of The Kingdoms"
msgstr "Crepúsculo de los Reinos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:20
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:428
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:23
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:32
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:394
msgid "Resist till the end of turns"
msgstr "Resistir hasta que acaben los turnos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:44
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:456
msgid "Death of any allied leader"
msgstr "Muerte de cualquier líder aliado"

#. [objectives]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:52
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:464
msgid ""
"HINT: do not attempt to kill the enemy leaders; rather, focus on defending "
"Valon"
msgstr ""
"PISTA: no intentéis matar a los líderes enemigos; concentraos en defender "
"Valon"

#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:83
msgid "Kingdom of Valon"
msgstr "Reino de Valon"

#. [side], type=Armageddon Drake
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:95
msgid "Kerath Ihn"
msgstr "Kerath Ihn"

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Greetings, Prince Varthan. I have received your message, and pledge myself "
"to help in our allies' evacuation. That is, if they do manage to escape the "
"mountains; knowing dwarves, trolls and elves, methinks fleeing from their "
"home would harm their pride."
msgstr ""
"Saludos, príncipe Varthan. He recibido vuestro mensaje y me comprometo a "
"ayudar en la evacuación de nuestros aliados. Eso si logran escapar de las "
"montañas; conociendo a enanos, trolls y elfos, creo que huir de su hogar "
"heriría su orgullo."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:218
msgid ""
"That is likely, but let's hope they come. If all our forces are concentrated "
"in a single place, we would become far stronger."
msgstr ""
"Es probable, pero esperemos que vengan. Si todas nuestras fuerzas se "
"concentran en un solo lugar, seremos mucho más fuertes."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:222
msgid ""
"I fear for Dvalin; I haven't heard from him since he returned to his own "
"home."
msgstr "Temo por Dvalin; no he sabido nada de él desde que regresó a su hogar."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:226
msgid ""
"I feel the same, but all we can do now is hope that he and his father find a "
"safe way to the Meadows."
msgstr ""
"Yo siento lo mismo, pero ahora solo podemos esperar que él y su padre "
"encuentren un camino seguro hacia los Prados."

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Behold! A new wave of drakes and saurians has come! Let's obliterate them to "
"make way for our allies, should they come!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad! ¡Llega una nueva oleada de dracos y saurios! ¡Acabemos con ellos "
"para despejar el camino a nuestros aliados, por si vienen!"

#. [message], speaker=Elvund
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:243
msgid ""
"I bring word of Lord Thelian. He should arrive here next morning, and he "
"brings with them all the elves he could rescue from the enclaves."
msgstr ""
"Traigo noticias de lord Thelian. Debería llegar aquí mañana por la mañana, y "
"trae consigo a todos los elfos que pudo rescatar de los enclaves."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:247
msgid "I hope he is bringing soldiers with him as well?"
msgstr "¿Espero que traiga soldados también?"

#. [message], speaker=Elvund
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:251
msgid "The finest among the Varanyans, milord."
msgstr "Los mejores de los varanyan, milord."

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:264
msgid ""
"At long last! Yonder is the Kingdom of Valon, my people, whose noble "
"citizens are opening their gates for us! Gil-Gawien, take the children, the "
"elders and the wounded to a shelter, and treat them; as for the healthy "
"warriors and druids, we must help defending the city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! ¡Allá está el Reino de Valon, pueblo mío, cuyos nobles ciudadanos "
"abren sus puertas para nosotros! Gil-Gawien, lleva a los niños, ancianos y "
"heridos a un refugio y atiéndelos; en cuanto a los guerreros y druidas "
"sanos, ¡debemos ayudar a defender la ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:277
msgid "Lord Thelian, have you heard word from dwarves or trolls?"
msgstr "Lord Thelian, ¿has tenido noticias de enanos o trolls?"

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:281
msgid ""
"The trolls should be coming after us, led by Groth, but the last message I "
"received from Auroghar assured me that the dwarves shall either defend their "
"caves or die trying."
msgstr ""
"Los trolls deberían venir detrás de nosotros, liderados por Groth, pero el "
"último mensaje que recibí de Auroghar me aseguró que los enanos defenderán "
"sus cuevas o morirán en el intento."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Stubborn dwarves! Can't they see we would be far stronger if we fought side "
"by side?"
msgstr ""
"¡Enanos cabezotas! ¿Es que no ven que seríamos mucho más fuertes si "
"lucháramos codo con codo?"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:301
msgid ""
"We have just smashed an army of drakes, only to find another one at our "
"goal! My warriors, heal your wounds, for we shall help defend Valon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Acabamos de destrozar un ejército de dracos, solo para encontrarnos con "
"otro al llegar! ¡Guerreros míos, curad vuestras heridas, porque vamos a "
"ayudar a defender Valon!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:314
msgid "Chief Groth! Do you bring any news from the dwarves?"
msgstr "¡Jefe Groth! ¿Traes noticias de los enanos?"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:318
msgid ""
"I do, young Myra. A dwarf scout found us some hours ago, and told us that "
"Chief Auroghar is dead."
msgstr ""
"Sí, joven Myra. Un explorador enano nos encontró hace unas horas y nos dijo "
"que el jefe Auroghar ha muerto."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:322
msgid "No! So the dwarves have perished?"
msgstr "¡No! ¿Entonces los enanos han perecido?"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:326
msgid ""
"They haven't. Auroghar's only surviving son, Dvalin, has convinced the "
"remaining dwarves to retreat and join us in the Meadows. I have sent them "
"one of my shamans, to lead them through our tunnels towards the Meadows."
msgstr ""
"No lo han hecho. El único hijo superviviente de Auroghar, Dvalin, ha "
"convencido a los enanos restantes de retroceder y unirse a nosotros en los "
"Prados. Les he enviado uno de mis chamanes para guiarlos por nuestros "
"túneles hasta los Prados."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:330
msgid "Excellent! So we must hold the dragons off just a little longer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente! ¡Entonces solo tenemos que contener a los dragones un poco más!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:348
msgid ""
"I hope your dwarf friend doesn't take much longer to arrive, Myra; resisting "
"these relentless drake attacks is getting more and more difficult."
msgstr ""
"Espero que tu amigo enano no tarde mucho más en llegar, Myra; resistir estos "
"implacables ataques de dracos se está volviendo cada vez más difícil."

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Let them come! Some of my wounded warriors have recovered, and they shall "
"join the kingdom's defences!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que vengan! Algunos de mis guerreros heridos se han recuperado y se unirán "
"a las defensas del reino."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:372
msgid "Dvalin! I'm so glad to see you safe and sound!"
msgstr "¡Dvalin! ¡Qué alegría verte sano y salvo!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Och, not so safe, my friend. There is another dragon army on the way, and "
"this one is led by Shek'kahan, another son of Shek'har. He may not be as "
"strong as Krahkrahs, but he's quite a tactician, and his army has many "
"hardened veterans."
msgstr ""
"Och, no tan a salvo, amiga mía. Viene otro ejército de dragones en camino, y "
"este lo lidera Shek’kahan, otro hijo de Shek’har. Puede que no sea tan "
"fuerte como Khrakrahs, pero es un gran estratega, y su ejército tiene muchos "
"veteranos curtidos."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:380
msgid ""
"Lord Dashien, it may be a good idea to evacuate your kingdom. I warrant you "
"that your people shall be welcome in Garet-Desh."
msgstr ""
"Lord Dashien, puede ser buena idea evacuar tu reino. Te aseguro que tu "
"pueblo será bienvenido en Garet-Desh."

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:384
msgid "I cannot abandon my kingdom! We shall hold any enemy wave that comes!"
msgstr ""
"¡No puedo abandonar mi reino! ¡Mantendremos a raya cualquier oleada enemiga "
"que venga!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:388
msgid ""
"With all due respect, king, my father thought like you, and he perished all "
"the same, together with all those who, like him, chose to fight a lost "
"battle."
msgstr ""
"Con todos mis respetos, rey, mi padre pensó como tú, y pereció igual, junto "
"con todos los que, como él, eligieron luchar una batalla perdida."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:405
msgid ""
"Apologies for being so late, my friend. Here, this is all the gold we "
"managed to salvage from my father's treasury; I also place my finest "
"warriors under your command."
msgstr ""
"Perdona por llegar tan tarde, amiga. Aquí tienes todo el oro que pudimos "
"salvar del tesoro de mi padre; también pongo a mis mejores guerreros bajo tu "
"mando."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:409
msgid "You may now recruit Steelclads, Pathfinders and Thunderguards!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora puedes reclutar Guardias de acero enano, Exploradores y Guardias del "
"trueno!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:418
msgid "Dvalin gives you 400 pieces of gold!"
msgstr "¡Dvalin te da 400 piezas de oro!"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'kahan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Finally we have found those stinky, hairy little pests! And, as bonus, we "
"have found the puny elves, the brutish trolls and the despicable humans as "
"well!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin hemos encontrado a esos apestosos y peludos bichitos! ¡Y, de "
"propina, también hemos encontrado a los débiles elfos, los brutos trolls y a "
"los despreciables humanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:535
msgid "You were right, Dvalin, this army is <i>huge</i>!"
msgstr "Tenías razón, Dvalin, ¡este ejército es <i>enorme</i>!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:539
msgid "My king, you must decide now!"
msgstr "¡Mi rey, debes decidir ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:543
msgid ""
"I... Fine, I shall heed Dvalin's words, and begin preparing my people's "
"evacuation."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Está bien, seguiré las palabras de Dvalin y empezaré a preparar la "
"evacuación de mi pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:547
msgid ""
"Allies, you also should send your elders, women, wounded and children to "
"Garet-Desh; as for us, we must defeat the brunt of Shek'kahan's army as "
"quickly as possible, and then retreat before the drakes receive more "
"reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"Aliados, vosotros también deberíais enviar a vuestros ancianos, mujeres, "
"heridos y niños a Garet-Desh; en cuanto a nosotros, debemos derrotar lo "
"antes posible el grueso del ejército de Shek’kahan y luego retroceder antes "
"de que los dracos reciban más refuerzos."

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:580
msgid "Oh, no... What is that large army that comes from the east?!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no…! ¿Qué es ese gran ejército que viene del este?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:584
msgid ""
"That is... That is my father, leading his veterans from Krathon's War! Is it "
"possible that he too came to help us?"
msgstr ""
"Eso es… ¡Es mi padre, liderando a sus veteranos de la Guerra de Krathon! ¿Es "
"posible que también haya venido a ayudarnos?"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:588
msgid ""
"Lords Dashien, Groth, Dvalin, Thelian, heed my words: you must hurry to "
"Garet-Desh, where the survivors from the other Aragwaithi kingdoms have "
"gathered. The dragons have us completely surrounded: Shek'har leads a "
"massive host in the north, whereas Khrakrahs, Niddhon and Shakkha attack "
"from the south. And, as I can now see, Shek'kahan is attacking from the west."
msgstr ""
"Señores Dashien, Groth, Dvalin, Thelian, escuchadme: debéis daros prisa "
"hacia Garet-Desh, donde se han reunido los supervivientes de los otros "
"reinos aragwaithi. Los dragones nos tienen completamente rodeados: Shek’har "
"lidera un enorme hueste en el norte, mientras que Khrakrahs, Niddhon y "
"Shakkha atacan desde el sur. Y, como ahora veo, Shek’kahan ataca desde el "
"oeste."

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:592
msgid "So Garet-Desh shall be our last stand...?"
msgstr "¿Entonces Garet-Desh será nuestro último bastión…?"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:596
msgid ""
"I fear so. Lady Maat is commanding the city in my absence, but you will take "
"our kingdom's reins when you get there, my son."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que sí. Lady Maat está al mando de la ciudad en mi ausencia, pero tú "
"tomarás las riendas del reino cuando llegues, hijo mío."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:600
msgid "But... what about you?"
msgstr "Pero… ¿y tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:604
msgid ""
"You shall lead our people from now on, Varthan. I shall stay here and delay "
"the dragons for as long as I can; hopefully we shall win Garet-Desh enough "
"time to fully prepare itself."
msgstr ""
"Tú liderarás a nuestro pueblo de ahora en adelante, Varthan. Yo me quedaré "
"aquí y retrasaré a los dragones todo lo que pueda; con suerte conseguiremos "
"que Garet-Desh gane tiempo suficiente para prepararse por completo."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:608
msgid ""
"But... Father, you cannot throw your life away like this! When they see you "
"leading Valon's defences, they will fall on your forces like a storm!"
msgstr ""
"Pero… ¡Padre, no puedes tirar tu vida así! ¡Cuando vean que lideras las "
"defensas de Valon, caerán sobre tus fuerzas como una tormenta!"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:612
msgid ""
"(smirking) Precisely what I am counting on. When they hear the hated Abhai "
"of Garet-Desh is here, dragons from all fronts shall converge on this city, "
"thus winning you even more time."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Eso es exactamente en lo que confío. Cuando oigan que el odiado "
"Abhai de Garet-Desh está aquí, los dragones de todos los frentes convergerán "
"en esta ciudad, ganando así aún más tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:616
msgid "But when they seize you..."
msgstr "Pero cuando te capturen…"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:620
msgid ""
"Not alive, they won't; I'll make sure of that. Son, I have lived too "
"intensely, done too much and travelled too far to end as a sickly and frail "
"wreck on a deathbed. I'd rather die in fire and storm, fighting for all that "
"is precious to me... You and my people included. My loyal brothers-in-arms "
"are of the same mind: we are old, and the old must make sure that the new "
"generations survive. But you're young, and it is the young who will rebuild "
"our civilization."
msgstr ""
"No lo harán vivo; de eso me encargaré yo. Hijo, he vivido demasiado "
"intensamente, he hecho demasiado y he viajado demasiado lejos para acabar "
"como un despojo enfermo y frágil en un lecho de muerte. Prefiero morir entre "
"fuego y tormenta, luchando por todo lo que me es preciado… Incluido tú y mi "
"pueblo. Mis leales hermanos de armas piensan igual: somos viejos, y los "
"viejos debemos asegurar que las nuevas generaciones sobrevivan. Pero tú eres "
"joven, y son los jóvenes quienes reconstruirán nuestra civilización."

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:624
msgid ""
"A bright star shall fade this day; I am honoured to have lived in the time "
"of King Abhai Raidhaz, the Dragonkiller."
msgstr ""
"Una estrella brillante se apagará este día; me siento honrado de haber "
"vivido en la época del rey Abhai Raidhaz, el Matadragones."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:628
msgid ""
"Even the stars fade out one day, old friend; what really matters is that new "
"stars are always born; right, Myra?"
msgstr ""
"Incluso las estrellas se apagan un día, viejo amigo; lo que realmente "
"importa es que siempre nacen nuevas estrellas; ¿verdad, Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:632
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:430
msgid "(blushes)"
msgstr "(se sonroja)"

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:636
msgid ""
"Now, my son, I want you to receive the Rod of Justice from me, as I have "
"received it from my forefathers. You will not be able to harness its full "
"powers for now, for you must still mature to be worthy of it, but I am sure "
"that, one day, you shall wield it as I have."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, hijo mío, quiero que recibas de mí la Vara de la Justicia, como yo la "
"recibí de mis antepasados. Por ahora no podrás aprovechar todo su poder, "
"porque aún debes madurar para ser digno de ella, pero estoy seguro de que un "
"día la empuñarás como yo lo hice."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:640
msgid "And Myra, tell Maat..."
msgstr "Y Myra, dile a Maat…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:644
msgid "Anything, Lord Abhai."
msgstr "Lo que sea, lord Abhai."

#. [message], speaker=Abhai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:648
msgid ""
"(smiles) No, everything I've ever had to tell her has already been said... "
"Now, everyone, you must all make haste to Garet-Desh!"
msgstr ""
"(sonríe) No, todo lo que alguna vez tuve que decirle ya se lo he dicho… "
"Ahora, ¡todos, daos prisa hacia Garet-Desh!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:652
msgid ""
"Let's hurry, then! *Father, I shall not disappoint you. Look after us from "
"wherever your soul rests, so you see our people thrive and live happily "
"again...!*"
msgstr ""
"¡Démonos prisa, entonces! *Padre, no te decepcionaré. Cuídanos desde donde "
"repose tu alma, para que veas a nuestro pueblo prosperar y volver a vivir "
"feliz…*"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'kahan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:656
msgid ""
"Ha! Look at the chicken running! But you cannot hide from us forever, petty "
"creatures!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Mirad al cobarde huyendo! ¡Pero no podréis esconderos de nosotros para "
"siempre, criaturas insignificantes!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:660
msgid "Ignore him; in Garet-Desh we shall give him the payback..."
msgstr "Ignoradlo; en Garet-Desh le daremos su merecido…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:760
msgid ""
"No! Without King Dashien and his soldiers, we won't be able to hold off the "
"dragon offensive for long!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin el rey Dashien y sus soldados, no podremos contener mucho tiempo "
"la ofensiva de los dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:774
msgid ""
"No! Without Chief Groth and the trolls, we won't be able to hold off the "
"dragon offensive for long!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin el jefe Groth y los trolls, no podremos contener mucho tiempo la "
"ofensiva de los dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/13_Twilight_Of_The_Kingdoms.cfg:788
msgid ""
"No! Without Lord Thelyan and the elves, we won't be able to hold off the "
"dragon offensive for long!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin el señor Thelyan y los elfos no podremos contener la ofensiva de "
"los dragones por mucho tiempo!"

#. [scenario], id=14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:4
msgid "The Sky Dragon Descends"
msgstr "El Dragón del Cielo Desciende"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:23
msgid "Resist the dragons' attack for 3 days (18 turns)"
msgstr "Resistir el ataque de los dragones durante 3 días (18 turnos)"

#. [label]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:75
msgid "Sky Mountains"
msgstr "Montañas del Cielo"

#. [unit], id=Aracyn, type=Aragwaith Ancient Banner
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:107
msgid "General Aracyn"
msgstr "General Aracyn"

#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:177
msgid "Niddhon"
msgstr "Niddhon"

#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:198
msgid "Shakkha"
msgstr "Shakkha"

#. [side], type=Fire Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:219
msgid "Agadhor"
msgstr "Agadhor"

#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:275
msgid "???"
msgstr "???"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'kahan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:426
msgid ""
"As I told you, father: the elves, the trolls and the dwarves have all "
"gathered with the humans."
msgstr ""
"Como te dije, padre: los elfos, los trolls y los enanos se han reunido todos "
"con los humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Khrakrahs
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:430
msgid ""
"So, if we kill them all here we won't have to search for scattered survivors "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, si los matamos a todos aquí no tendremos que buscar supervivientes "
"dispersos después."

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:434
msgid ""
"You are aware of the fate that is about to befall you, aren't you, puny "
"creatures?"
msgstr ""
"¿Sois conscientes del destino que os aguarda, criaturas insignificantes?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:438
msgid ""
"We make our own fate, dragon. The time for words is over; now, we fight!"
msgstr ""
"Nosotros forjamos nuestro propio destino, dragón. Se acabaron las palabras; "
"¡ahora, luchamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:442
msgid "So be it... Children of Morogor, warriors of the Sky Dragon: CHARGE!"
msgstr ""
"Que así sea… ¡Hijos de Morogor, guerreros del Dragón del Cielo: ¡CARGA!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:446
msgid "It is time, my friends! Fight for our future!"
msgstr "¡Es la hora, amigos míos! ¡Luchad por nuestro futuro!"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:458
msgid "I now go to Lord Abhai's side... Defend our people, my sons..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora voy al lado de lord Abhai… Defended a nuestro pueblo, hijos míos…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:462
msgid "FATHER!"
msgstr "¡PADRE!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:466
msgid ""
"No, Jevyan! There are too many enemies on that side, if you go alone you'll "
"die!"
msgstr ""
"¡No, Jevyan! ¡Hay demasiados enemigos por ese lado, si vas solo morirás!"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:470
msgid ""
"She's right, cousin... Don't forfeit your life, but vent your anger on these "
"drakes! Come, I shall fight alongside you!"
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón, primo… ¡No tires tu vida, pero desahoga tu rabia con estos "
"dracos! ¡Ven, lucharé a tu lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:481
msgid "I die a warrior's death... Fight on without me, my people!"
msgstr "¡Muero como guerrero… Seguid luchando sin mí, pueblo mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:485
msgid ""
"(furious) Dwarves! Let's give Chief Groth a retinue of drakes to serve him "
"in the World of the Dead!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡Enanos! ¡Démosle al jefe Groth un séquito de dracos que lo sirvan "
"en el Mundo de los Muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:496
msgid "Alas, never shall I see the green woods again..."
msgstr "Ay, nunca volveré a ver los verdes bosques…"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Lord Thelian! I shall not let your death be in vain... Elves, follow me! We "
"will show the dragons what happens to the fools who make an enemy out of an "
"elf!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lord Thelian! ¡No dejaré que tu muerte sea en vano…! ¡Elfos, seguidme! ¡Les "
"mostraremos a los dragones lo que les pasa a los necios que se enfrentan a "
"un elfo!"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:526
msgid "My love...!"
msgstr "¡Amor mío…!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:530
msgid "Gil-Gawien, NO!"
msgstr "¡Gil-Gawien, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:536
msgid "Lord Thelian, I now go join you in the other world..."
msgstr "Lord Thelian, ahora voy a reunirme contigo en el otro mundo…"

#. [message], speaker=Dashien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:549
msgid ""
"Thus falls the last King of Valon... At long last, I shall be reunited with "
"my wife and daughters..."
msgstr ""
"Así cae el último Rey de Valon… Por fin me reuniré con mi esposa y mis hijas…"

#. [message], speaker=Niddhon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:570
msgid ""
"Unbelievable, the vermin are making advance! But not for long... Call in the "
"reserves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Increíble, la plaga está avanzando! ¡Pero no por mucho tiempo… Llamad a las "
"reservas!"

#. [message], speaker=Shakkha
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:591
msgid "How shameful that I'm forced to send even my reserve troops to battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué vergüenza tener que enviar hasta mis tropas de reserva a la batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:612
msgid "Accursed apes, I will burn you all to a cinder! Send in the reserves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos monos, os quemaré a todos hasta las cenizas! ¡Enviad las reservas!"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:633
msgid ""
"Son, you have been wounded; leave this battlefield at once! As for you, "
"pesky apes, you will regret what you have just done..."
msgstr ""
"Hijo, estás herido; ¡abandona este campo de batalla ahora mismo! En cuanto a "
"vosotros, molestos monos, os arrepentiréis de lo que acabáis de hacer…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:672
msgid ""
"We have been giving these overgrown lizards hell for days already, and we "
"still stand! SEE THAT, SKY DRAGON? YOUR WARRIORS ARE NO MATCH FOR OUR MIGHT!"
msgstr ""
"¡Llevamos días dándoles infierno a estos lagartos crecidos y aún seguimos en "
"pie! ¡MIRA ESO, DRAGÓN DEL CIELO! ¡TUS GUERREROS NO SON RIVALES PARA NUESTRO "
"PODER!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:689
msgid "It's him... Svarballi is coming!"
msgstr "Es él… ¡Svarballi viene!"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:693
msgid ""
"No... Destroy them at once, you incompetent fools, before Lord Svarballi "
"arrives!"
msgstr ""
"¡No… Destruidlos ahora mismo, inútiles incompetentes, antes de que llegue "
"lord Svarballi!"

#. [unit], id=Svarballi, type=Sky Dragon
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:721
msgid "Svarballi"
msgstr "Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:734
msgid "The-"
msgstr "¡El-"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:738
msgid "The legendary...!"
msgstr "¡El legendario…!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:742
msgid "...Sky Dragon!"
msgstr "…¡Dragón del Cielo!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:747
msgid ""
"You fools... You had your foes completely at your mercy, heavily "
"outnumbered, and yet here I am, forced to settle this matter myself..."
msgstr ""
"Idiotas… Teníais a vuestros enemigos completamente a vuestra merced, en "
"enorme inferioridad numérica, y aun así aquí estoy yo, obligado a resolver "
"esto personalmente…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:751
msgid "Forgive me, Lord Svarballi, I..."
msgstr "Perdonadme, lord Svarballi, yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:756
msgid ""
"But that was to be expected; mere fire dragons like you would have never "
"defeated this High Ascendant, whom some seem to call the 'Chosen of Gods'..."
msgstr ""
"Pero era de esperar; simples dragones de fuego como vosotros nunca habríais "
"derrotado a esta Gran Ascendente, a la que algunos llaman la «Elegida de los "
"Dioses»…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:760
msgid ""
"Goddess I am not, Sky Dragon, but I can still do everything in my power to "
"stop you from destroying this world."
msgstr ""
"No soy diosa, Dragón del Cielo, pero aún puedo hacer todo lo que esté en mi "
"poder para impedir que destruyas este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:765
msgid ""
"Which world? This world of endless violence? This world where living beings "
"feed on their fellow living beings to survive? Pitiful creature! (roaring to "
"the skies) Was that what you died for, Nitiballi? So that these miserable "
"wretches might suffer with endless wars and strife? (turning back to Maat) "
"All I want is to put an end to the misery of this so-called 'Miracle of "
"Life', but you insist on seeing it persist; <i>you</i> are the real villain "
"here, Maat of Hiera'Shirsha!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué mundo? ¿Este mundo de violencia sin fin? ¿Este mundo donde los seres "
"vivos se alimentan de sus semejantes para sobrevivir? ¡Criatura lamentable! "
"(rugiendo al cielo) ¿Fue por eso por lo que moriste, Nitiballi? ¿Para que "
"estos miserables desdichados sufrieran guerras y conflictos sin fin? "
"(volviéndose hacia Maat) Todo lo que quiero es poner fin a la miseria de "
"este supuesto «Milagro de la Vida», pero tú insistes en que persista; <i>tú</"
"i> eres la verdadera villana aquí, ¡Maat de Hiera’Shirsha!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:769
msgid ""
"I cannot deny that wherever there is life, there is conflict and strife... "
"But you cannot deny that, wherever there is life, there is also love, "
"friendship, joy, dreams... It is your fault that you could not see that life "
"is not only peace and harmony, but also war and chaos; and neither of them "
"changes the fact that many beings of this planet do manage to find "
"happiness..."
msgstr ""
"No puedo negar que donde hay vida hay conflicto y lucha… Pero tú no puedes "
"negar que, donde hay vida, también hay amor, amistad, alegría, sueños… Es "
"culpa tuya no haber visto que la vida no es solo paz y armonía, sino también "
"guerra y caos; y ninguno de los dos cambia el hecho de que muchos seres de "
"este planeta logran encontrar la felicidad…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:774
msgid ""
"Nonsense. Peace, love and joy are mere illusions created by the living to "
"disguise the truth about life: that it is <i>made</i> of chaos and strife, "
"and will always be."
msgstr ""
"Tonterías. Paz, amor y alegría son meras ilusiones creadas por los vivos "
"para disfiar la verdad sobre la vida: que está <i>hecha</i> de caos y lucha, "
"y siempre lo estará."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:778
msgid "No, it is not, Svarballi, can't you see that?"
msgstr "No, no lo es, Svarballi, ¿es que no lo ves?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:783
msgid "I can only see the undisguised truth."
msgstr "Solo puedo ver la verdad sin disfraz."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:787
msgid ""
"No, you have only twisted it because it did not fit your belief in a "
"perfectly calm world-"
msgstr ""
"No, solo la has retorcido porque no encajaba con tu creencia en un mundo "
"perfectamente tranquilo-"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:792
msgid ""
"(roaring) There is no use in arguing anymore! I shall crush you and your "
"beloved little pests, and then we'll see who is right!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡No tiene sentido seguir discutiendo! ¡Te aplastaré a ti y a tus "
"queridas plagas, y entonces veremos quién tenía razón!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:798
msgid "Fight Svarballi"
msgstr "Luchar contra Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:846
msgid ""
"Now you see that your precious lord was never interested in helping the "
"dragons, Shek'har?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora ves que tu precioso señor nunca estuvo interesado en ayudar a los "
"dragones, ¿verdad, Shek’har?"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:850
msgid "No, that... that can't be... What have I..."
msgstr "No, eso… eso no puede ser… ¿Qué he hecho…?"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'kahan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:854
msgid ""
"(whispering) Father, maybe we should, you know, help the Ascendant; at least "
"she will not kill us..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Padre, quizá deberíamos, ya sabes, ayudar a la Ascendente; al "
"menos ella no nos matará…"

#. [message], speaker=Shek'har
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:858
msgid ""
"I will never side with inferior races! My sons, gather your drakes and leave "
"this accursed battlefield!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jamás me pondré del lado de razas inferiores! ¡Hijos míos, reunid a "
"vuestros dracos y abandonad este maldito campo de batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:865
msgid ""
"The cowards are fleeing! Do not let yourselves be deceived, my warriors, for "
"Lord Svarballi <i>will</i> usher us into a new Dragon Age!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los cobardes huyen! ¡No os dejéis engañar, guerreros míos, porque lord "
"Svarballi <i>sí</i> nos llevará a una nueva Era de los Dragones!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:886
msgid "Mother, now it's time for us to face Svarballi!"
msgstr "¡Madre, ahora nos toca enfrentarnos a Svarballi!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:890
msgid "(sighing) For me, not for you..."
msgstr "(suspirando) Para mí, no para ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:894
msgid "What do you-"
msgstr "¿Qué qui-"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:898
msgid "Cipher of Sleep."
msgstr "Cifrado del Sueño."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:919
msgid "Lady Maat! What have you done?!"
msgstr "¡Lady Maat! ¡¿Qué has hecho?!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:923
msgid ""
"Alenya, please tell her I am sorry for deceiving her once again, but... I "
"just cannot allow her to die here; she would kill herself trying to vanquish "
"Svarballi, just like Nitiballi did. I've seen someone I love sacrifice "
"herself right before my eyes, once... I will not have it happen again, not "
"if I can stop it myself."
msgstr ""
"Alenya, por favor dile que lo siento por engañarla una vez más, pero… "
"simplemente no puedo permitir que muera aquí; se mataría intentando vencer a "
"Svarballi, igual que hizo Nitiballi. Ya vi una vez a alguien a quien amaba "
"sacrificarse delante de mis ojos… No dejaré que vuelva a pasar, no si puedo "
"evitarlo yo misma."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:927
msgid ""
"But you were supposed to fight together, like the Water and Fire Dragons "
"did, right?"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero se suponía que lucharíais juntas, como hicieron los Dragones del Agua "
"y del Fuego, ¿no?!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:931
msgid ""
"That's what <i>they</i> did, not what <i>we</i> have to do. Now, please take "
"her and the other Aragwaithi away; King Varthan, I have no authority over "
"you, but you should go as well; your people need you."
msgstr ""
"Eso es lo que hicieron <i>ellos</i>, no lo que <i>nosotras</i> tenemos que "
"hacer. Ahora, por favor, llévatela a ella y a los demás aragwaithi; rey "
"Varthan, no tengo autoridad sobre ti, pero deberías irte también; tu pueblo "
"te necesita."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:935
msgid "You... I shall... do as you say, for I acknowledge my people need me."
msgstr "Tú… Haré… lo que dices, porque reconozco que mi pueblo me necesita."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:939
msgid ""
"Dvalin, you must help escorting the refugees to a safer place! Come with us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dvalin, debes ayudar a escoltar a los refugiados a un lugar más seguro! "
"¡Ven con nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:943
msgid "And flee from the battlefield? Never!"
msgstr "¿Y huir del campo de batalla? ¡Jamás!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:947
msgid ""
"You will not be fleeing, worthy Dvalin; you would be saving the defenceless "
"refugees. Other than Varthan, you will be the only leader left, so you will "
"be needed."
msgstr ""
"No estarás huyendo, digno Dvalin; estarás salvando a los refugiados "
"indefensos. Además de Varthan, serás el único líder que quede, así que te "
"necesitarán."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:951
msgid ""
"Well, thinking this way... Then we shall go east! Come with us, women and "
"children of dwarf-kind, elf-kind, humankind and troll-kind! We shall lead "
"you to safety!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, pensándolo así… ¡Entonces iremos al este! ¡Venid con nosotros, "
"mujeres y niños de la raza enana, élfica, humana y trol! ¡Os guiaremos a un "
"lugar seguro!"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:961
msgid ""
"Go with him, my sons. I shall stay and help Lady Maat. And no, don't try to "
"convince me otherwise; as Lord Abhai told me before leaving for Valon, the "
"old must make sure that there is a future for the young."
msgstr ""
"Id con él, hijos míos. Yo me quedaré y ayudaré a lady Maat. Y no, no "
"intentéis convencerme de lo contrario; como me dijo lord Abhai antes de "
"partir hacia Valon, los viejos debemos asegurar que haya futuro para los "
"jóvenes."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:965
msgid "Father..."
msgstr "Padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Aracyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:970
msgid ""
"And son... I know I may have been too strict, maybe even harsh, but... Know "
"that I am, and always have been, proud of the man you've become. Now go, and "
"lead the remaining Aragwaithi to safety! And you, my warriors, it was an "
"honour to fight alongside you! Let's bring some drake companions to follow "
"us to the world of the dead!"
msgstr ""
"Y hijo… Sé que quizá fui demasiado estricto, tal vez incluso duro, pero… Has "
"de saber que estoy, y siempre he estado, orgulloso del hombre en que te has "
"convertido. ¡Ahora ve y lleva a los aragwaithi restantes a un lugar seguro! "
"¡Y vosotros, guerreros míos, fue un honor luchar a vuestro lado! ¡Traigamos "
"algunos compañeros dracos que nos sigan al mundo de los muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:984
msgid ""
"The younger ones may follow Prince Varthan; as for the veterans, we shall "
"give these dragons hell before we go!"
msgstr ""
"Los más jóvenes pueden seguir al príncipe Varthan; en cuanto a los "
"veteranos, ¡daremos infierno a estos dragones antes de irnos!"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:993
msgid ""
"To the ruin and the end of the world and back to the earth whence we came - "
"together, my love!"
msgstr ""
"A la ruina y al fin del mundo y de vuelta a la tierra de donde vinimos —"
"¡juntos, amor mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelian
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:997
msgid "Death itself frightens me not with you by my side, Gil-Gawien..."
msgstr "La misma muerte no me asusta teniéndote a mi lado, Gil-Gawien…"

#. [message], speaker=GilGawien
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1005
msgid ""
"The younger ones may follow Prince Varthan; as for the veterans, we shall "
"send a few more drakes for Lord Thelian in the World of the Dead!"
msgstr ""
"Los más jóvenes pueden seguir al príncipe Varthan; en cuanto a los "
"veteranos, ¡enviaremos unos cuantos dracos más para lord Thelian en el Mundo "
"de los Muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Groth
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1016
msgid ""
"The women and the children must go and find a new home for our people; but I "
"shall stay and die a warrior's death!"
msgstr ""
"Las mujeres y los niños deben ir a buscar un nuevo hogar para nuestro "
"pueblo; ¡pero yo me quedaré y moriré como guerrero!"

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1026
msgid "And we shall be with you, Chief!"
msgstr "¡Y estaremos contigo, jefe!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1125
msgid ""
"Futile efforts; I shall obliterate you from existence and then chase them "
"down."
msgstr ""
"Esfuerzos inútiles; os borraré de la existencia y luego los perseguiré."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1129
msgid "I will not have that happen, Svarballi..."
msgstr "No permitiré que eso pase, Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1134
msgid "What... What are you doing...?"
msgstr "¿Qué… Qué estás haciendo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1138
msgid ""
"*Hathy, Deni, forgive me for what I'm about to do... But just like you, I "
"cannot stand to see someone I love risk her life - even if that means giving "
"my own...*"
msgstr ""
"*Hathy, Deni, perdonadme por lo que voy a hacer… Pero igual que vosotras, no "
"puedo soportar ver a alguien a quien amo arriesgar su vida —aunque eso "
"signifique dar la mía…*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1142
msgid ""
"Svarballi watched her in silence, as did the other dragons, drakes, humans, "
"elves, saurians and trolls; and soon an unbelievable silence befell the "
"bloody battlefield as everyone watched the High Ascendant."
msgstr ""
"Svarballi la observó en silencio, al igual que los demás dragones, dracos, "
"humanos, elfos, saurios y trolls; y pronto un silencio increíble cayó sobre "
"el sangriento campo de batalla mientras todos observaban a la Gran "
"Ascendente."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1149
msgid ""
"And then it happened: hundreds, thousands of greyish-blue streams of light "
"formed out of thin air all around Maat, wrapping her in a bright web of "
"light; then, for a split moment it was as if reality itself had been "
"shattered - for in that split moment everyone on that battlefield saw "
"glimpses of a million realms, each stranger than the other. As the light "
"receded and the visions were replaced by the landscape where they stood, "
"everyone could see Maat again, but she was not the same: her body emanated a "
"cold aura, her eyes shone like blue stars, and all contenders, even those "
"far from the Ascendant, could sense the power she exuded."
msgstr ""
"Y entonces ocurrió: cientos, miles de rayos de luz gris-azulada se formaron "
"de la nada alrededor de Maat, envolviéndola en una brillante red de luz; "
"luego, por un instante pareció como si la realidad misma se hubiera roto —"
"pues en ese instante todos en el campo de batalla vieron atisbos de un "
"millón de reinos, cada uno más extraño que el otro. Cuando la luz retrocedió "
"y las visiones fueron reemplazadas por el paisaje donde estaban, todos "
"pudieron ver a Maat de nuevo, pero ya no era la misma: su cuerpo emanaba un "
"aura fría, sus ojos brillaban como estrellas azules y todos los "
"contendientes, incluso los alejados de la Ascendente, podían sentir el poder "
"que exudaba."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1186
msgid ""
"So this is it: the fabled High Ascendant, who controls and harnesses the "
"power of the Worldsweave itself... It still will not help you, though, for "
"you are no goddess - and unlike Agniballi and Nitiballi, you're on your own!"
msgstr ""
"Así que esto es: la legendaria Gran Ascendente, que controla y aprovecha el "
"poder del Tejido de los Mundos mismo… Aun así no te servirá de nada, porque "
"no eres una diosa —¡y a diferencia de Agniballi y Nitiballi, estás sola!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1190
msgid ""
"I'm not on my own, Svarballi, not with the Raw by my side... I control the "
"Worldsweave that ties all dimensions - so step forward, Sky Dragon, and "
"measure your strength against that of existence itself!"
msgstr ""
"No estoy sola, Svarballi, no con el Raw a mi lado… ¡Controlo el Tejido de "
"los Mundos que une todas las dimensiones —así que da un paso al frente, "
"Dragón del Cielo, y mide tu fuerza contra la de la existencia misma!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1200
msgid "Maat must kill Svarballi"
msgstr "Maat debe matar a Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1230
msgid ""
"Pathetic creatures! How can you possibly believe that puny vermin like you "
"are capable of defeating me, the High Dragon of the Sky?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Criaturas patéticas! ¿Cómo podéis creer que alimañas insignificantes como "
"vosotros sois capaces de derrotarme a mí, ¡el Gran Dragón del Cielo?!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1237
msgid "Stand aside, warriors! Only I can defeat him!"
msgstr "¡Atrás, guerreros! ¡Solo yo puedo derrotarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1252
msgid "What is happening...?! How can a simple human wield such power...?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué está pasando…? ¡¿Cómo puede un simple humano manejar tanto poder…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Shakkha
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1256
msgid "Our king is in danger! Niddhon, Agadhor, we must go to his aid!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nuestro rey está en peligro! ¡Niddhon, Agadhor, debemos ir en su ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"It is futile to help him, lesser dragons, you will only suffer the same fate "
"as Svarballi!"
msgstr ""
"Es inútil ayudarlo, dragones menores, ¡solo sufriréis el mismo destino que "
"Svarballi!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1280
msgid "Stop your nonsense! I am immortal!"
msgstr "¡Deja de decir tonterías! ¡Soy inmortal!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1284
msgid "I never meant to kill you, Svarballi..."
msgstr "Nunca pretendí matarte, Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1299
msgid ""
"You... You are channelling too much power, you fool! At this rate you will "
"be obliterated!"
msgstr ""
"Tú… ¡Estás canalizando demasiado poder, necia! ¡A este ritmo serás "
"obliterada!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1303
msgid "I always knew that - but I <i>shall</i> see you beaten before I go!"
msgstr ""
"¡Siempre lo supe —pero <i>tú</i> serás derrotado antes de que yo me vaya!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1308
msgid "YOU... DARN... VERMIN!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡TÚ… MALDITA… PLAGA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/14_The_Sky_Dragon_Descends.cfg:1312
msgid "THIS IS YOUR END, SVARBALLI!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡ESTE ES TU FIN, SVARBALLI!!!"

#. [scenario], id=15_Farewell
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:4
msgid "Farewell"
msgstr "Despedida"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:21
msgid "Move Jevyan to the middle of the river to the east"
msgstr "Llevar a Jevyan al centro del río al este"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:45
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:39
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:46
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:823
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:41
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:46
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:679
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:748
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:47
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/20_Ring_Of_Fire.cfg:51
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/20_Ring_Of_Fire.cfg:563
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:47
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:794
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/23_Holy_Fire.cfg:45
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:44
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:720
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:845
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:48
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:410
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:41
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:428
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/32_Fading_Of_A_Flame.cfg:34
msgid "Death of Akashia"
msgstr "Muerte de Akashia"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Damn drake fire! We'll burn to ashes along with this forest! And to make "
"matters worse, I can barely see what is ahead of me with all this smoke!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito fuego de draco! ¡Vamos a quemarnos hasta las cenizas junto con este "
"bosque! ¡Y para colmo, apenas veo qué hay delante con tanto humo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:311
msgid ""
"The fire and the smoke are not our main problem. The drakes and the saurians "
"are fleeing the battlefield as well, but I'm certain they will try and kill "
"us if they have the chance."
msgstr ""
"El fuego y el humo no son nuestro principal problema. Los dracos y los "
"saurios también están huyendo del campo de batalla, pero estoy seguro de que "
"intentarán matarnos si tienen la oportunidad."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:315
msgid ""
"We have no choice but to fight our way through this mayhem! If only I could "
"harness the powers of the Rod... But that's unimportant now. Aragwaithi, "
"follow me! As for you Windsong, now that Lady Maat stayed behind and Myra is "
"unconscious, who is your representative?"
msgstr ""
"No tenemos más remedio que abrirnos paso a la fuerza en medio de este caos. "
"¡Si al menos pudiera aprovechar los poderes de la Vara…! Pero eso ahora no "
"importa. ¡Aragwaithi, seguidme! En cuanto a vosotras, Hijas del Viento, "
"ahora que lady Maat se quedó atrás y Myra está inconsciente, ¿quién es "
"vuestra representante?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:319
msgid "I am, King Varthan."
msgstr "Yo, rey Varthan."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:323
msgid "Could you protect us from the heat with some of your ciphers?"
msgstr "¿Podríais protegernos del calor con alguno de vuestros cifrados?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:327
msgid ""
"We could, but it would take us some time to cast them, and methinks we are "
"running short of it right now!"
msgstr ""
"Podríamos, pero nos llevaría un tiempo lanzarlos, ¡y creo que ahora mismo "
"nos falta precisamente eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:331
msgid "I thought the Windsong were more skilled..."
msgstr "Pensaba que las Hijas del Viento eran más hábiles…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:335
msgid "Well, apologies if we can't move heaven and earth at the snap of your-"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, disculpa si no podemos mover cielo y tierra con un chasquido de tus-"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:339
msgid ""
"No matter! We must hurry to a safer point; there is a river nearby, that is "
"where we shall regroup! Now, onwards!"
msgstr ""
"¡No importa! ¡Debemos llegar rápido a un punto más seguro; hay un río cerca, "
"allí nos reagruparemos! ¡Ahora, adelante!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Jevyan is carrying Myra's unconscious body; because of that, he won't be "
"able to attack anyone successfully!"
msgstr ""
"Jevyan está cargando el cuerpo inconsciente de Myra; por eso no podrá atacar "
"con éxito a nadie."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Look! The young man carries the unconscious Myra, the accursed daughter of "
"the Ascendant! This is our chance to avenge our fallen kin, warriors, we "
"must not let it escape!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad! ¡El joven lleva a la inconsciente Myra, la maldita hija de la "
"Ascendente! ¡Esta es nuestra oportunidad de vengar a nuestros caídos, "
"guerreros, no debemos dejarla escapar!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:362
msgid "As if we didn't have enough problems in our hands already..."
msgstr "Como si no tuviéramos ya bastantes problemas encima…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:366
msgid ""
"Jevyan, stay close to me and my sisters! We shall protect you no matter the "
"cost!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jevyan, quédate cerca de mí y de mis hermanas! ¡Te protegeremos cueste lo "
"que cueste!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:393
msgid "What was that just now?"
msgstr "¿Qué ha sido eso ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:397
msgid "This power... Lady Maat..."
msgstr "Este poder… Lady Maat…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:401
msgid "M-mother..."
msgstr "M-madre…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:405
msgid "I understand it; the world has just lost its brightest shine."
msgstr "Lo entiendo; el mundo acaba de perder su brillo más intenso."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:409
msgid ""
"But I don't feel the Sky Dragon's energy either... Our beloved lady made "
"sure she didn't go out alone..."
msgstr ""
"Pero tampoco siento la energía del Dragón del Cielo… Nuestra querida señora "
"se aseguró de no irse sola…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:413
msgid "There will be time to mourn later, now we must hurry!"
msgstr "Ya habrá tiempo de llorarla después, ¡ahora debemos darnos prisa!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:466
msgid ""
"We have made it to the river, but some of our own are still trying to find a "
"way out of the forest. Let's camp here for the time being, and clear the "
"path for the rest of our people."
msgstr ""
"Hemos llegado al río, pero algunos de los nuestros aún intentan salir del "
"bosque. Acampemos aquí por ahora y despejemos el camino para el resto de "
"nuestra gente."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:488
msgid "Ouch... Where... What is..."
msgstr "Ay… Dónde… Qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:492
msgid "Look, she's awakening!"
msgstr "¡Mirad, está despertando!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:496
msgid "Lady Myra, how do you feel?"
msgstr "Lady Myra, ¿cómo te sientes?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:500
msgid ""
"(looking around frantically) I must... I must get back to the city, I'm "
"supposed to fight alongside my mother..."
msgstr ""
"(mirando alrededor frenéticamente) Tengo que… Tengo que volver a la ciudad, "
"se supone que debo luchar junto a mi madre…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:504
msgid "Myra, your mother..."
msgstr "Myra, tu madre…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:508
msgid ""
"Don't you even dare to say she's dead! I can still sense her energy coming "
"from the battlefield!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ni se te ocurra decir que está muerta! ¡Todavía siento su energía viniendo "
"del campo de batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:512
msgid "She's got a point there, for I too can still sense Lady Maat's power."
msgstr "Tiene razón, porque yo también sigo sintiendo el poder de lady Maat."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:516
msgid ""
"Of course you do, such an immense outburst of energy would never vanish away "
"so quickly!"
msgstr ""
"¡Claro que sí, una explosión de energía tan inmensa nunca desaparece tan "
"rápido!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:520
msgid ""
"You... stay here if you wish, I am heading back to Garet-Desh, or what was "
"left of it..."
msgstr ""
"Vosotros… quedaos aquí si queréis, yo regreso a Garet-Desh, o a lo que quede "
"de ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Stubborn humans! At least let me follow you then; you're not in conditions "
"to go there alone."
msgstr ""
"¡Humanos cabezotas! Al menos déjame seguirte; no estás en condiciones de ir "
"sola."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:540
msgid "I'm going with you as well."
msgstr "Yo también voy contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:550
msgid "So am I."
msgstr "Yo también."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:587
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:277
msgid "I cannot fall now, Myra depends on me..."
msgstr "No puedo caer ahora, Myra depende de mí…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:615
msgid "I have fallen; who will lead the Aragwaithi now...?"
msgstr "He caído; ¿quién liderará ahora a los aragwaithi…?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:629
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:291
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:1018
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:573
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:964
msgid "How could I have fallen so easily...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo he podido caer tan fácilmente…?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell.cfg:654
msgid ""
"We are taking too much time in this burning forest! We'll get asphyxiated by "
"the smoke before we reach the river..."
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos tardando demasiado en este bosque en llamas! ¡Nos asfixiaremos con "
"el humo antes de llegar al río…!"

#. [scenario], id=15_Farewell_b
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:4
msgid "Farewell, Part 2"
msgstr "Despedida, 2ª Parte"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:23
msgid "Lead Myra to the ruins of the fallen palace of Garet-Desh"
msgstr "Llevar a Myra hasta las ruinas del palacio caído de Garet-Desh"

#. [side]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:65
msgid "Ghosts"
msgstr "Fantasmas"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:145
msgid ""
"Unbelievable... Such devastation wreaked by a single mage; the very air "
"crackles with Lady Maat's lingering energy!"
msgstr ""
"Increíble… Tanta devastación causada por una sola maga; ¡el mismo aire "
"crepita con la energía persistente de lady Maat!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Apparently, the explosion killed all the remaining contenders, but we must "
"proceed carefully; none can tell what we may find in this fog..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que la explosión mató a todos los contendientes restantes, pero "
"debemos avanzar con cuidado; nadie sabe qué podemos encontrar en esta niebla…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Weird... It seems like the energy unleashed in the explosion has impregnated "
"the flames, creating fire elementals..."
msgstr ""
"Qué raro… Parece que la energía liberada en la explosión ha impregnado las "
"llamas, creando elementales de fuego…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:167
msgid ""
"But not like normal elementals, for I cannot control them. Still, they don't "
"seem very hostile, so we may avoid fighting as long as we stay away from "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Pero no como los elementales normales, porque no puedo controlarlos. Aun "
"así, no parecen muy hostiles, así que podemos evitar luchar mientras nos "
"mantengamos alejados."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:180
msgid "Please... <i>Please</i>..."
msgstr "Por favor… <i>Por favor</i>…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:184
msgid ""
"As she rushed into the ruins of Abhai's castle, she felt Maat's presence "
"grow stronger. However, there was no one there; only the broken, ash-like "
"remains of countless drakes surrounding the crater where the High Ascendant "
"had made her last stand..."
msgstr ""
"Mientras corría hacia las ruinas del castillo de Abhai, sentía cada vez más "
"fuerte la presencia de Maat. Sin embargo, no había nadie; solo los restos "
"rotos, como ceniza, de cuatro inmensos dragones alrededor del cráter donde "
"la Gran Ascendente había hecho su última resistencia…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:188
msgid ""
"As the truth finally dawned upon her, crude and undeniable, Myra fell on her "
"knees, streams of tears sliding down her face, her body trembling almost "
"convulsively with her sobs; in those moments, it seemed to her that her life "
"was one of losses: her mother Ysara, her friends from Hashira's Valley, her "
"home of Hiera'Shirsha, her loyal friend Veela, and now her beloved foster-"
"mother, Maat, all had been taken from her, and she'd failed to do anything "
"to prevent that from happening... Myra remained there for a few minutes, "
"suddenly devoid of any strength and will, while her friends still roamed the "
"ruins, until a faint, flickering shine in the middle of the crater called "
"her attention."
msgstr ""
"Cuando por fin comprendió la cruda e innegable verdad, Myra cayó de "
"rodillas, con lágrimas resbalando por su su rostro, su cuerpo temblando casi "
"convulsivamente entre sollozos; en esos momentos le parecía que su vida era "
"una cadena de pérdidas: su madre Ysara, sus amigos del Valle de Hashira, su "
"hogar de Hiera’Shirsha, su leal amiga Veela, y ahora su querida madre "
"adoptiva, Maat, todos le habían sido arrebatados, y ella no había logrado "
"hacer nada para evitarlo… Myra se quedó allí unos minutos, de pronto sin "
"fuerzas ni voluntad, mientras sus amigos seguían recorriendo las ruinas, "
"hasta que un leve brillo parpadeante en el centro del cráter llamó su "
"atención."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:192
msgid "What is that...?"
msgstr "¿Qué es eso…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:199
msgid ""
"*A purple stone... Could mother have let it fall before? No, it would have "
"been destroyed in the explosion. But this is no ordinary gem: I feel a huge "
"power coming from it, and a terrible malice... This stone...*"
msgstr ""
"*Una piedra púrpura… ¿Podría haberla dejado caer madre antes? No, se habría "
"destruido en la explosión. Pero esta no es una gema cualquiera: siento un "
"poder inmenso emanando de ella, y una terrible malicia… Esta piedra…*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:206
msgid "<i>He cannot be completely destroyed...</i>"
msgstr "<i>No puede ser destruido por completo…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:210
msgid "*This stone is...!*"
msgstr "*¡Esta piedra es…!*"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:217
msgid ""
"*So this is why you wanted me to survive the battle, mother... Very well, I "
"shall guard his soul no matter what; but I must conceal its aura, so that no "
"one else shall sense it...*"
msgstr ""
"*Entonces por eso querías que sobreviviera a la batalla, madre… Muy bien, "
"guardaré su alma pase lo que pase; pero debo ocultar su aura para que nadie "
"más la sienta…*"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:227
msgid "Myra! Where have you been? I was starting to worry about you!"
msgstr "¡Myra! ¿Dónde estabas? ¡Empezaba a preocuparme por ti!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Let's return to our camp; there is nothing left in this place... not anymore."
msgstr "Volvamos a nuestro campamento; ya no queda nada en este lugar… ya no."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:249
msgid "Killed by elementals, o the irony..."
msgstr "Muerte por elementales, oh la ironía…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Why are we taking so long here? Let's get back to where the others are, I'm "
"starting to feel ill in this fog."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué nos estamos demorando tanto aquí? Volvamos donde están los demás, "
"esta niebla empieza a sentarme mal."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_b.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Let's go then... *I feel there was something extremely important for me to "
"find here, but I cannot force my friends to risk their health in this smoky "
"battlefield...*"
msgstr ""
"Vámonos entonces… *Siento que había algo extremadamente importante que "
"encontrar aquí, pero no puedo obligar a mis amigos a arriesgar su salud en "
"este campo de batalla lleno de humo…*"

#. [scenario], id=15_Farewell_c
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:4
msgid "Farewell, Part 3"
msgstr "Despedida, Parte 3"

#. [side], type=Troll Hero
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:33
msgid "Gark"
msgstr "Gark"

#. [side], type=Elvish Captain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:43
msgid "Ameldor"
msgstr "Ameldor"

#. [side], type=Elvish Captain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:47
msgid "Elves"
msgstr "Elfos"

#. [unit], id=Clavyan, type=Aragwaith Strongbow
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:98
msgid "Clavyan"
msgstr "Clavyan"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:127
msgid ""
"At last you're back, Myra! King Varthan is gathering with Dvalin and the "
"leaders of elves and trolls; they want to go north, to the Frozen Lands, but "
"I told him such path will pit us against the dragons once again! Please, "
"tell him we must go east, as far from the lizards as we can..."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin has vuelto, Myra! El rey Varthan está reunido con Dvalin y los "
"líderes de elfos y trolls; quieren ir al norte, a las Tierras Congeladas, "
"¡pero le dije que ese camino nos enfrentará otra vez a los dragones! ¡Por "
"favor, dile que debemos ir al este, lo más lejos posible de los lagartos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:131
msgid ""
"Be thou silent, nephew of Aracyn! Clearly you know not what lies to the "
"east, so I shall tell you: going there will take us to the lands of the "
"steppe people, the Hannuks! Maybe you also ignore the fact that they have "
"always been hostile towards us; something they make sure to remind us every "
"harvesting season with their relentless raids!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cállate, sobrino de Aracyn! ¡Claramente no sabes qué hay al este, así que "
"te lo diré: ir allí nos llevará a las tierras del pueblo de la estepa, ¡los "
"hannuk! ¡Tal vez también ignores que siempre han sido hostiles con nosotros; "
"algo que se encargan de recordarnos cada temporada de cosecha con sus "
"implacables incursiones!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:135
msgid ""
"But Ravyan is right when he says going north is dangerous. The dragons have "
"attacked from there as well, so it makes sense to presume they still have "
"bases there. Shek'har himself might be rallying new troops right now, for I "
"doubt Svarballi's defeat has made him give up on his campaign."
msgstr ""
"Pero Ravyan tiene razón cuando dice que ir al norte es peligroso. Los "
"dragones también han atacado desde allí, así que tiene sentido suponer que "
"aún tienen bases allí. El propio Shek’har podría estar reuniendo nuevas "
"tropas ahora mismo, porque dudo que la derrota de Svarballi le haya hecho "
"abandonar su campaña."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:139
msgid ""
"Besides, since the dragons are everyone's enemies, we might convince the "
"Hannuks to side with us against them."
msgstr ""
"Además, como los dragones son enemigos de todos, quizá podamos convencer a "
"los hannuk de ponerse de nuestro lado contra ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:143
msgid ""
"Good idea, but even if we convince them that they are Shek'har's next "
"target, will they really become our friends and allies? Forget not what Lord "
"Abhai said: we must find a new place to settle and rebuild your civilization "
"before fighting the dragons again. Will the Hannuks allow you to settle "
"anywhere near them?"
msgstr ""
"Buena idea, pero aunque los convenzamos de que ellos son el próximo objetivo "
"de Shek’har, ¿realmente se convertirán en nuestros amigos y aliados? No "
"olvides lo que dijo lord Abhai: debemos encontrar un nuevo lugar donde "
"asentarnos y reconstruir vuestra civilización antes de volver a luchar "
"contra los dragones. ¿Permitirán los hannuk que os asentéis cerca de ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:147
msgid ""
"I have read about the steppe people, and I know they have deep respect for "
"family ties. I believe that, if they see a half-Hannuk such as myself "
"amongst us, they may be friendlier..."
msgstr ""
"He leído sobre el pueblo de la estepa y sé que tienen un profundo respeto "
"por los lazos familiares. Creo que, si ven a una medio hannuk como yo entre "
"nosotros, podrían ser más amistosos…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:151
msgid ""
"If the call of your Hannuk blood is so strong, young Myra, I shall not stop "
"you from going east; but I shall lead the Aragwaithi to the Frozen Lands. "
"I'm certain that the dragons, with their vulnerability to cold, will have no "
"heart to search and fight us in that weather."
msgstr ""
"Si la llamada de tu sangre hannuk es tan fuerte, joven Myra, no te detendré "
"de ir al este; pero yo lideraré a los aragwaithi hacia las Tierras "
"Congeladas. Estoy seguro de que los dragones, con su vulnerabilidad al frío, "
"no tendrán corazón para buscarnos y luchar contra nosotros en ese clima."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:155
msgid ""
"This has nothing to do with blood! I'm just saying that the east is our best "
"option! But if you want to go north, then good luck; I am going east."
msgstr ""
"¡Esto no tiene nada que ver con la sangre! ¡Solo digo que el este es nuestra "
"mejor opción! Pero si quieres ir al norte, entonces buena suerte; yo voy al "
"este."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:159
msgid ""
"Correction: 'we are' going east. Because we're not going to abandon you "
"after all we've been through, right, Alenya, Dvalin?"
msgstr ""
"Corrección: «nosotros» vamos al este. Porque no vamos a abandonarte después "
"de todo lo que hemos pasado, ¿verdad, Alenya, Dvalin?"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Och, I hoped to be able to meet our kin in the far west, but all the "
"underground tunnels I know must be swarming with drakes and saurians by now, "
"and on the surface we dwarves will be an easy prey for the swifter lizards. "
"No, I will go east with you, my friends."
msgstr ""
"Och, esperaba poder reunirme con nuestros parientes en el lejano oeste, pero "
"todos los túneles subterráneos que conozco deben estar plagados de dracos y "
"saurios ahora, y en la superficie nosotros los enanos seríamos presa fácil "
"para los lagartos más rápidos. No, iré al este con vosotros, amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:167
msgid ""
"I make Dvalin's words mine. I too wanted to return to my home, but right now "
"all the paths are under dragon control. Moreover... I too don't want to "
"abandon you now, Myra."
msgstr ""
"Hago mías las palabras de Dvalin. Yo también quería volver a mi hogar, pero "
"ahora mismo todos los caminos están bajo control de los dragones. Además… Yo "
"tampoco quiero abandonarte ahora, Myra."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:171
msgid "If you're following them, cousin, then I shall come with you."
msgstr "Si vas con ellos, primo, entonces yo también iré contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Gark
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:175
msgid ""
"Steppes are vast and flat, a bad home for trolls. But the human king "
"promises the north holds vast mountain ranges, and so we follow him."
msgstr ""
"Las estepas son vastas y planas, un mal hogar para trolls. Pero el rey "
"humano promete que el norte tiene vastas cordilleras, y por eso lo seguimos."

#. [message], speaker=Ameldor
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:179
msgid ""
"I wish we could fight alongside our ancient friends in search of a new home; "
"alas, I must attend to my people's desires, and neither the frozen, "
"mountainous north, nor the vast eastern plains, make us feel safe. But we "
"know the southeast fringes of this continent are covered in deep forests; "
"hopefully we may settle there, until either the dragons are defeated in the "
"west or we are strong again."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá pudiéramos luchar junto a nuestros antiguos amigos en busca de un "
"nuevo hogar; ay, debo atender los deseos de mi pueblo, y ni el norte helado "
"y montañoso ni las vastas llanuras del este nos hacen sentir seguros. Pero "
"sabemos que los bordes sureste de este continente están cubiertos de "
"profundos bosques; con suerte podremos asentarnos allí, hasta que o bien los "
"dragones sean derrotados en el oeste o volvamos a ser fuertes."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:183
msgid ""
"And so the Winds' People are separated at last, scattered by the winds of "
"war and fate..."
msgstr ""
"Y así el Pueblo del Viento se separa por fin, dispersado por los vientos de "
"la guerra y el destino…"

#. [message], speaker=Clavyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:187
msgid "Erm, Lady Myra...?"
msgstr "Eh, lady Myra…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:191
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres?"

#. [message], speaker=Clavyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:195
msgid ""
"You may not recognize me, but I hail from the same village as you, our dear "
"Kiera..."
msgstr ""
"Puede que no me reconozcas, pero vengo del mismo pueblo que tú, nuestra "
"querida Kiera…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:199
msgid "<i>Your</i> dear Kiera, soldier."
msgstr "<i>Tu</i> querida Kiera, soldado."

#. [message], speaker=Clavyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Anyway, I have spoken with the remaining survivors of Kiera and of Doldesh, "
"our liege kingdom, and it is in their name that I offer you our services for "
"your journey eastwards."
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, he hablado con los supervivientes restantes de Kiera y de "
"Doldesh, nuestro reino señor, y en su nombre te ofrezco nuestros servicios "
"para tu viaje hacia el este."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Hold on! You desert me, your king, your people to follow a woman who hates "
"you?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Un momento! ¡¿Me abandonáis, a mí, vuestro rey, a vuestro pueblo, para "
"seguir a una mujer que os odia?!"

#. [message], speaker=Clavyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:211
msgid ""
"With all due respect, Lord Varthan, Kiera was sworn to Doldesh; we obeyed "
"King Vercyn, who died valiantly in his kingdom's defence, and afterwards we "
"willingly pledged our allegiance to Garet-Desh. But now, we are free to "
"follow whoever we want."
msgstr ""
"Con el debido respeto, señor Varthan, Kiera juró lealtad a Doldesh; "
"obedecimos al rey Vercyn, quien murió valientemente defendiendo su reino, y "
"después juramos lealtad voluntariamente a Garet-Desh. Pero ahora somos "
"libres de seguir a quien queramos."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:215
msgid ""
"(fuming) Well, if that is so, do as you wish. But know one thing: when you "
"see your comrades falling under volleys of Hannuk arrows, and finally "
"realise Myra's plan is foolish, you better go and find a new land in the "
"south, because the north will already be ours, and you shall not be welcome "
"there!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) Bueno, si es así, haced lo que queráis. ¡Pero sabed una cosa: "
"cuando veáis a vuestros camaradas caer bajo andanadas de flechas hannuk y "
"finalmente os deis cuenta de que el plan de Myra es una locura, mejor id a "
"buscar una nueva tierra en el sur, porque el norte ya será nuestro y no "
"seréis bienvenidos allí!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:219
msgid ""
"You know, <i>Majesty</i>, once I jested we might have been siblings... Now "
"I'm glad that never came to be. (turning to the Kieran soldier) Come with "
"me, survivors of Doldesh! I promise I shall forget our past divergences, and "
"lead you to a new and safe home!"
msgstr ""
"Sabes, <i>majestad</i>, una vez bromeé con que podríamos haber sido "
"hermanos… Ahora me alegro de que nunca fuera así. (volviéndose al soldado de "
"Kiera) ¡Venid conmigo, supervivientes de Doldesh! ¡Os prometo que olvidaré "
"nuestras diferencias pasadas y os llevaré a un nuevo y seguro hogar!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:223
msgid ""
"(whispering) Now our numbers have increased, and for that we must thank "
"Prince Varthan!"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Ahora hemos aumentado en número, ¡y por eso tenemos que "
"agradecer al príncipe Varthan!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#. [part]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:227
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:272
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:890
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/utils/intros.cfg:330
msgid "(chuckles)"
msgstr "(ríe)"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Er, Lady Myra, I am extremely sorry... no, I am ashamed to tell you that "
"some of our sisters have chosen to follow that <i>prince</i>..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, lady Myra, lo siento muchísimo… no, me avergüenza decirte que algunas de "
"nuestras hermanas han elegido seguir a ese <i>príncipe</i>…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:235
msgid ""
"If they believe they will be happier with the Aragwaithi, then I shall not "
"force them to do otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Si creen que serán más felices con los aragwaithi, entonces no las obligaré "
"a hacer otra cosa."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:239
msgid ""
"And so our paths diverge... (turning his back on Myra) To the north, my "
"people!"
msgstr ""
"Y así nuestros caminos se separan… (dándole la espalda a Myra) ¡Al norte, "
"pueblo mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/15_Farewell_c.cfg:243
msgid ""
"(to her followers) I know you're all exhausted, but we must hurry and leave "
"this place before Shek'har finds us again. Come, my people, we shall find a "
"new home for us; I promise you we shall..."
msgstr ""
"(a sus seguidores) Sé que estáis todos agotados, pero debemos apresurarnos y "
"abandonar este lugar antes de que Shek’har nos encuentre de nuevo. ¡Venid, "
"pueblo mío, encontraremos un nuevo hogar para nosotros; os lo prometo…!"

#. [scenario], id=16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:4
msgid "Blood of the Steppes"
msgstr "Sangre de las Estepas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:22
msgid "Explore the Hannuk Steppes"
msgstr "Explorar las Estepas Hannuk"

#. [objectives]
