#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:201
msgid ""
"There she goes, meditating in the open again... What does she muse so much "
"about?"
msgstr "Ahí va otra vez, meditando al aire libre… ¿En qué pensará tanto?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Maybe she's meditating on a way to summon new elementals again; I confess "
"even I have been thinking a lot about it lately. Besides, I'm certain our "
"friend hasn't overcome what happened at Garet-Desh yet, even though it's "
"been four months since that battle."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez esté meditando en cómo volver a invocar elementales; confieso que yo "
"también he pensado mucho en eso últimamente. Además, estoy segura de que "
"nuestra amiga aún no ha superado lo que pasó en Garet-Desh, aunque hayan "
"pasado ya cuatro meses desde esa batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:209
msgid ""
"I understand, but still, I think she should let us, her friends, help and "
"support her, instead of isolating herself as she has been doing!"
msgstr ""
"Lo entiendo, pero aun así creo que debería dejarnos, a sus amigos, ayudarla "
"y apoyarla, ¡en vez de aislarse como ha estado haciendo!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:213
msgid "I agree, and that is why I keep her company whenever I can-"
msgstr "Estoy de acuerdo, y por eso le hago compañía siempre que puedo…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:217
msgid ""
"But I'd like to help her as well! I too have followed and bled for her, it's "
"not fair you're the only one she lets stay close to her!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero yo también quiero ayudarla! ¡Yo también la he seguido y he sangrado "
"por ella, no es justo que solo tú puedas estar cerca!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:221
msgid ""
"Jevyan, can you be possibly jealous of Myra and I staying together so often?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Jevyan, ¿es posible que estés celoso de que Myra y yo pasemos "
"tanto tiempo juntas?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:225
msgid ""
"(blushing violently) Me, jealous...? Come on, don't be absurd, why would "
"I... Jealous, yeah, right..."
msgstr ""
"(se pone rojo como un tomate) ¿Yo, celoso…? Vamos, no seas ridícula, ¿por "
"qué iba a… Celoso, sí, claro…"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:229
msgid "Look, she's coming back!"
msgstr "¡Mirad, ya vuelve!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:236
msgid ""
"Well, comrades, I know it is still night, but we must not tarry here much "
"longer. The books salvaged from the Windsong libraries tell of how the "
"Hannuks never receive unexpected foreign guests after sunset; and, according "
"to our maps, we're now very close to their lands, so, if we make haste, "
"we'll reach them before the next twilight."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, camaradas, sé que aún es de noche, pero no podemos quedarnos aquí "
"mucho más. Los libros rescatados de las bibliotecas de las Hijas del Viento "
"cuentan que los hannuk nunca reciben huéspedes extranjeros inesperados "
"después del ocaso; y, según nuestros mapas, ahora estamos muy cerca de sus "
"tierras, así que, si nos damos prisa, llegaremos antes del próximo "
"crepúsculo."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:240
msgid ""
"Myra, I know you have explained your thoughts on the subject before, but the "
"men are still afraid the Hannuks will not receive us kindly..."
msgstr ""
"Myra, sé que ya explicaste tus ideas al respecto, pero los hombres siguen "
"temiendo que los hannuk no nos reciban amablemente…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:244
msgid ""
"You Aragwaithi are so insecure... Lady Myra has already warranted us they "
"will at the very least allow us to cross their lands towards the far-eastern "
"shores; and if they don't, we shall hack through their territory by force!"
msgstr ""
"Qué inseguros sois los aragwaithi… Lady Myra ya nos garantizó que al menos "
"nos dejarán cruzar sus tierras hacia las costas del lejano oriente; ¡y si "
"no, nos abriremos paso a la fuerza!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Their fears are legitimate, Akashia. It is true that they may forbid us from "
"crossing their land, perhaps even attack us, but going around their vast "
"land would cost us far too much time and even more resources. No, facing the "
"Hannuks is a risk we must take, but I assure you we'll not be vanquished; "
"this I swear."
msgstr ""
"Sus temores son legítimos, Akashia. Es cierto que podrían prohibirnos cruzar "
"su tierra, quizá incluso atacarnos, pero rodear su vasta extensión nos "
"costaría demasiado tiempo y aún más recursos. No, enfrentar a los hannuk es "
"un riesgo que debemos correr, pero os aseguro que no seremos vencidos; lo "
"juro."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:252
msgid "Gallant words, milady!"
msgstr "¡Palabras gallardas, milady!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:256
msgid ""
"(sighing tiredly) So let's dismantle our camp and keep going... And Dvalin, "
"you really should accept my horse for yourself; you will only slow us down "
"in the steppes."
msgstr ""
"(suspira cansada) Entonces desmontemos el campamento y sigamos… Y Dvalin, "
"realmente deberías aceptar mi caballo; solo nos retrasarás en las estepas."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:260
msgid ""
"(whispering) Och, elf, I told you already, don't speak to me like this in "
"front of my warriors!"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¡Och, elfa, ya te lo dije, no me hables así delante de mis "
"guerreros!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:264
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Fine, then. If you change your mind, tell me, that I will help "
"you climb on horseback."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Está bien. Si cambias de idea, dímelo, que te ayudo a subir al "
"caballo."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:268
msgid "Hrumph!"
msgstr "¡Hrumph!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:298
msgid ""
"So, Akashia. You've become Myra's second-in-command among the Windsong quite "
"fast."
msgstr ""
"Así que, Akashia. Te has convertido en la segunda al mando de Myra entre las "
"Hijas del Viento bastante rápido."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:302
msgid "Do you take issue with that?"
msgstr "¿Tienes algún problema con eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Oh, not at all! What I meant is that you seem to get along quite well with "
"her. That surprised me, as I was under the impression that Myra had few or "
"no friends."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, para nada! Lo que quise decir es que parece que os lleváis bastante "
"bien. Me sorprendió, porque tenía la impresión de que Myra tenía pocos o "
"ningún amigo."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:310
msgid "Hey!"
msgstr "¡Oye!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:314
msgid ""
"We hadn't seen each other in a while before it all began, since I was a "
"guardian in Hiera'Shirsha and she was studying under Lashimi in Hashira's "
"Valley. But we've always been rather close, actually. We were brought to "
"Hiera'Shirsha only two years apart, and we're also close in age. Besides, "
"our foster-mothers were very close friends so we were always around each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"No nos veíamos desde hacía un tiempo antes de que todo empezara, porque yo "
"era guardiana en Hiera’Shirsha y ella estudiaba con Lashimi en el Valle de "
"Hashira. Pero siempre hemos estado bastante unidas, en realidad. Nos "
"llevaron a Hiera’Shirsha con solo dos años de diferencia y también somos "
"cercanas en edad. Además, nuestras madres adoptivas eran muy buenas amigas, "
"así que siempre estábamos juntas."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:318
msgid "And your foster-mother was?"
msgstr "¿Y tu madre adoptiva era…?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Deianira, the Scarlet Lightning. She found me during an expedition to "
"Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"Deianira, el Rayo Escarlata. Me encontró durante una expedición a Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:326
msgid ""
"I've heard of the Scarlet Lightning! One of my mentors, Sunna of the "
"Solariel, used to tell me much about her."
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, he oído hablar de ella! Una de mis mentoras, Sunna de los Solariel, "
"me hablaba mucho de ella."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Sunna of the Solariel... Yes, I've heard of her too. My mother used to say "
"elves were 'stuck-up bitches', but she always had nice words for Sunna."
msgstr ""
"Sunna de los Solariel… Sí, también he oído de ella. Mi madre decía que los "
"elfos eran «engreídos de mierda», pero siempre tenía buenas palabras para "
"Sunna."

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:334
msgid "Um... that's good, I suppose...?"
msgstr "Eh… está bien, supongo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:349
msgid "*What a beautiful field of flowers; Veela would have loved it...*"
msgstr "*Qué hermoso campo de flores; a Veela le habría encantado…*"

#. [unit], id=Subutai, type=Hannuk Mangudai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:367
msgid "Subutai"
msgstr "Subutai"

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:388
msgid ""
"Look, another group of the cursed Aragwaithi comes to harass us! Just when "
"you thought they would leave us in peace for a while and focus on their own "
"problems... By the spirits of the air, what is wrong with these people?"
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad, otro grupo de malditos aragwaithi viene a molestarnos! ¡Justo cuando "
"pensabas que nos dejarían en paz un tiempo y se ocuparían de sus propios "
"problemas… Por los espíritus del aire, qué les pasa a esta gente!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:392
msgid "My, my, you Aragwaithi are truly unpopular in these realms, aren't you?"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya, los aragwaithi sois realmente impopulares por estos lares, ¿eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Calm down, Steppe Master, for we don't come as enemies. Rather, we're just "
"refugees of the war that destroyed our homes in the Meadows."
msgstr ""
"Tranquilo, Maestro de la Estepa, no venimos como enemigos. Más bien somos "
"refugiados de la guerra que destruyó nuestros hogares en los Prados."

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:400
msgid ""
"So you are just a ragtag bunch of losers with no home, no allies? By the "
"spirits of fire, I never thought I'd have the hated Aragwaithi at my mercy "
"like this... Warriors of the Steppes, suit yourselves! The glory of crushing "
"these rascals shall be ours!"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que solo sois un puñado de perdedores sin hogar ni aliados? ¡Por los "
"espíritus del fuego, nunca pensé que tendría a los odiados aragwaithi a mi "
"merced así…! ¡Guerreros de la Estepa, a vuestra voluntad! ¡La gloria de "
"aplastar a estos granujas será nuestra!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:404
msgid "Well, in the end they barely let us talk at all..."
msgstr "Bueno, al final apenas nos dejaron hablar…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:408
msgid ""
"(sighing) If we have no choice, then we must fight them. Maybe he'll be more "
"willing to listen to us at the point of a sword."
msgstr ""
"(suspirando) Si no tenemos opción, tendremos que luchar. Quizá así esté más "
"dispuesto a escucharnos, a punta de espada."

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:419
msgid ""
"Damn you people of the Meadows! You may have killed me, but you are no match "
"for the tribes you shall find as you go further into our steppes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea la gente de los Prados! Puede que me hayáis matado, ¡pero no "
"sois rival para las tribus que encontraréis más adentro en nuestras estepas!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Cease this hostile talk, Steppe Master. Really, I thought the Hannuks were "
"hospitable, but you have attacked me without even thinking twice, me, a "
"kinswoman of yours..."
msgstr ""
"Deja de hablar con hostilidad, Maestro de la Estepa. De verdad, pensaba que "
"los hannuk eran hospitalarios, ¡pero me has atacado sin pensarlo dos veces, "
"a mí, una pariente tuya…!"

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:427
msgid ""
"What kinswoman? I see only fair-haired Aragwaithi and mongrel witches "
"amongst you. And speaking of which, I now remember that you broom-riding "
"Windsong used to kidnap our young girls to fill up your darn ranks!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué pariente? Solo veo aragwaithi rubios y brujas mestizas entre vosotros. "
"Y hablando de eso, ahora recuerdo que vosotras, las Hijas del Viento que "
"vais en escoba, solíais raptar a nuestras niñas para engrosar vuestras "
"malditas filas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:431
msgid ""
"I won't deny our Order did bad things to other peoples in the past, but the "
"late High Ascendant Maat, my foster-mother, stopped that practice and "
"compensated the harassed peoples long ago. And I am your kinswoman, Steppe "
"Master, can't you see that in my features? My mother was Aragwaithi, but my "
"father was a Hannuk, though I have never met him myself..."
msgstr ""
"No negaré que nuestra Orden hizo cosas malas a otros pueblos en el pasado, "
"pero la difunta Gran Ascendente Maat, mi madre adoptiva, acabó con esa "
"práctica y compensó a los pueblos perjudicados hace mucho. Y soy tu "
"pariente, Maestro de la Estepa, ¿no lo ves en mis rasgos? Mi madre era "
"aragwaithi, pero mi padre era hannuk, aunque nunca lo he conocido…"

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:435
msgid ""
"Daughter of an Aragwaithi woman and a Hannuk...? Is it possible that you are "
"<i>his</i> daughter...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Hija de una mujer aragwaithi y un hannuk…? ¿Es posible que seas <i>su</i> "
"hija…?"

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:444
msgid "And what is your name, anyway?"
msgstr "¿Y cómo te llamas, por cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:448
msgid "I am Myra of Hiera'Shirsha."
msgstr "Soy Myra de Hiera’Shirsha."

#. [message], speaker=Subutai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:452
msgid ""
"Myra, if you really are like your foster-mother, then I think I can trust "
"you. You may cross my lands and into the steppes, but be aware that not all "
"other Hannuks may be as kind as me. Know also that this region of the "
"steppes is inhabited by rogue bands of hunters, ogres and wild animals. If "
"you manage to overcome these dangers and reach the Wolf Mountain, you may "
"find your father, the noble Tarkyn. Tell him of how Subutai of the Turtle "
"Clan was kind in letting you through his own lands."
msgstr ""
"Myra, si realmente eres como tu madre adoptiva, entonces creo que puedo "
"confiar en ti. Puedes cruzar mis tierras y adentrarte en las estepas, pero "
"ten en cuenta que no todos los demás hannuk serán tan amables como yo. "
"También debes saber que esta región de las estepas está habitada por bandas "
"de cazadores renegados, ogros y animales salvajes. Si logras superar estos "
"peligros y llegas a la Montaña del Lobo, tal vez encuentres a tu padre, el "
"noble Tarkyn. Dile que Subutai del Clan Tortuga fue amable al dejarlos pasar "
"por sus tierras."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:456
msgid "I will. Thank you, Steppe Master."
msgstr "Lo haré. Gracias, Maestro de la Estepa."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:473
msgid "So, my father's name's Tarkyn..."
msgstr "Así que mi padre se llama Tarkyn…"

#. [unit], id=Kublai, type=Hannuk Conqueror
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:491
msgid "Kublai"
msgstr "Kublai"

#. [message], speaker=Kublai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:507
msgid ""
"Halt! You have trespassed a land that belongs to me, outsiders, and so you "
"must compensate us in gold!"
msgstr ""
"¡Alto! ¡Habéis traspasado una tierra que me pertenece, forasteros, y por eso "
"debéis compensarnos con oro!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:511
msgid ""
"We have precious little gold even for ourselves, we can't afford spending it "
"anywhere else. And besides, if you don't want people to trespass your land, "
"then you should spread signs around it marking its frontiers, don't you "
"agree?"
msgstr ""
"Tenemos muy poco oro incluso para nosotros, no podemos permitirnos gastarlo "
"en cualquier sitio. Y además, si no quieres que la gente traspase tu tierra, "
"deberías poner señales alrededor marcando sus fronteras, ¿no crees?"

#. [message], speaker=Kublai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:515
msgid ""
"Impudent little girl, I will teach you a lesson! Nobody disrespects the "
"great Kublai, the Scourge of the Steppes, and lives to tell the tale!"
msgstr ""
"¡Niña insolente, te daré una lección! ¡Nadie falta al respeto al gran "
"Kublai, el Azote de las Estepas, y vive para contarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:519
msgid "Yeah, right..."
msgstr "Sí, claro…"

#. [message], speaker=Kublai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:530
msgid "How could I be defeated by a mere girl...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo he podido ser derrotado por una simple niña…?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:534
msgid ""
"Hey, look at all this gold... I bet he's one of the bandits Subutai warned "
"us about."
msgstr ""
"Eh, mirad todo este oro… Apuesto a que es uno de esos bandidos de los que "
"nos advirtió Subutai."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:539
msgid "You have found 250 pieces of gold!"
msgstr "¡Has encontrado 250 piezas de oro!"

#. [unit], id=Ogre_Chieftain, type=Great Ogre
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:561
msgid "Ogre Chieftain"
msgstr "Jefe Ogro"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:573
msgid "Whoa, watch out everyone, there is something in those ruins..."
msgstr "¡Cuidado todos, hay algo en esas ruinas…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ogre Chieftain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Tiny humans invade my land, me kill tiny humans, and then me children eat "
"tiny humans!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pequeños humanos invaden mi tierra, yo matar pequeños humanos, y luego mis "
"hijos comer pequeños humanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:581
msgid "Oh my, how lucky of us to have stumbled on a tribe of adult ogres..."
msgstr "Vaya, qué suerte la nuestra tropezar con una tribu de ogros adultos…"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Pah, ogres are nothing more than brainless savages, and their cleavers have "
"little effect on our armour! Stand aside, that we will stamp them out!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bah, los ogros no son más que salvajes sin cerebro y sus cuchillas tienen "
"poco efecto en nuestras armaduras! ¡Apartaos, que los exterminaremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:589
msgid ""
"Their ruins seem very old, but I think they'll make us a fine place to rest "
"for a while. I just wonder why everyone is so territorial in this vast "
"steppe..."
msgstr ""
"Sus ruinas parecen muy antiguas, pero creo que nos servirán como buen lugar "
"para descansar un rato. Solo me pregunto por qué todos son tan territoriales "
"en esta vasta estepa…"

#. [message], speaker=Ogre_Chieftain
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:600
msgid "Grurlg...!"
msgstr "¡Grurlg…!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:604
msgid ""
"The ogres were sitting on an actual trove... Wonder if they stole it from "
"Hannuks unlucky enough to step into their swamp?"
msgstr ""
"Los ogros estaban sentados sobre un verdadero tesoro… ¿Será que se lo "
"robaron a hannuk con tan mala suerte como para entrar en su pantano?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:609
msgid "You have found 300 pieces of gold!"
msgstr "¡Has encontrado 300 piezas de oro!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:627
msgid ""
"I think this is the mountain Subutai talked about; its pinnacle does "
"resemble a howling wolf."
msgstr ""
"Creo que esta es la montaña de la que habló Subutai; su cima sí parece un "
"lobo aullando."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:631
msgid ""
"So, Myra's father's clan must be close now. I just hope he receives us "
"friendly..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, el clan del padre de Myra debe estar cerca. Solo espero que nos "
"reciba amistosamente…"

#. [unit], id=Bleda, type=Hannuk Mangudai
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:666
msgid "Bleda"
msgstr "Bleda"

#. [unit], id=Denziq, type=Hannuk Conqueror
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:681
msgid "Denziq"
msgstr "Denziq"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:693
msgid "Uh-oh, I see trouble ahead..."
msgstr "Uy, veo problemas delante…"

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:697
msgid ""
"Listen to me, old Tarkyn: no longer will the Wolfpelt Clan accept being "
"ordered around by one such as you, who breaks the ancient traditions of the "
"Steppe Peoples by allowing women to wield the bow!"
msgstr ""
"Escúchame, viejo Tarkyn: ¡el Clan Piel de Lobo ya no acepta que le dé "
"órdenes alguien como tú, que rompe las antiguas tradiciones de los Pueblos "
"de la Estepa al permitir que las mujeres empuñen el arco!"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:701
msgid ""
"Oh, silence from you, unworthy scum! We all know you are merely coveting "
"Master Tarkyn's fertile lands! Master, you may count the aid of my clan."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, cállate, escoria indigna! Todos sabemos que solo codicias las fértiles "
"tierras del maestro Tarkyn. Maestro, puedes contar con la ayuda de mi clan."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:705
msgid ""
"I greatly appreciate your loyalty, worthy Bleda. Now, let's wave this puny "
"upstart aside and... But wait, who comes there in the Wolf Mountain?"
msgstr ""
"Agradezco mucho tu lealtad, digno Bleda. Ahora, apartemos a este advenedizo "
"insignificante y… Pero espera, ¿quién viene por la Montaña del Lobo?"

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:709
msgid "I recognize their green clothing and fair hair: they're Aragwaithi!"
msgstr "Reconozco su ropa verde y su pelo claro: ¡son aragwaithi!"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:713
msgid ""
"And they're followed by those witches and... who are those halflings...?"
msgstr "Y les siguen esas brujas y… ¿quiénes son esos medianos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:717
msgid ""
"They're cave-dwellers, and by the looks of it, they're all refugees. I think "
"the rumours were true then, the dragons have destroyed the Meadows..."
msgstr ""
"Son habitantes de cuevas y, por lo que parece, todos son refugiados. "
"Entonces las rumores eran ciertos, los dragones han destruido los Prados…"

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:721
msgid ""
"Ha! So these are the last of the cursed Aragwaithi, uh? Tarkyn, Bleda, I "
"suggest warming ourselves up on them before facing each other, what do you "
"say?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¿Así que estos son los últimos de los malditos aragwaithi, eh? Tarkyn, "
"Bleda, propongo que nos calentemos un poco con ellos antes de enfrentarnos "
"entre nosotros, ¿qué decís?"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:725
msgid "I admit the idea pleases me. What do you say, Master Tarkyn?"
msgstr "Admito que la idea me agrada. ¿Qué dices, maestro Tarkyn?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:729
msgid ""
"Let's at least give their leader the right to speak. (shouting) Refugees, "
"listen to me! I am Tarkyn of the Doe Clan, paramount in the western steppes! "
"Now answer me: who is your leader? Let him, or her, step up and say what "
"your business in our lands is."
msgstr ""
"Al menos demos a su líder el derecho a hablar. (gritando) ¡Refugiados, "
"escuchadme! ¡Soy Tarkyn del Clan Ciervo, soberano de las estepas "
"occidentales! Ahora respondedme: ¿quién es vuestro líder? Que él, o ella, dé "
"un paso al frente y diga qué os trae a nuestras tierras."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:733
msgid ""
"Greetings, Master Tarkyn... I am Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, daughter of Ysara of "
"Kiera..."
msgstr ""
"Saludos, maestro Tarkyn… Soy Myra de Hiera’Shirsha, hija de Ysara de Kiera…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:737
msgid "Daughter of Ysara...?!"
msgstr "¡¿Hija de Ysara…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:741
msgid ""
"As you said, we are just refugees, seeking a home for ourselves after the "
"dragons devastated the Meadows. We are travelling to the Far East, which we "
"know is uninhabited by human peoples..."
msgstr ""
"Como dijiste, solo somos refugiados buscando un hogar después de que los "
"dragones devastaran los Prados. Viajamos al Lejano Oriente, que sabemos que "
"está deshabitado por pueblos humanos…"

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:745
msgid ""
"Why aren't our arrows piercing their stinking bodies yet? Let's end this "
"useless talk and finish them!"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué nuestras flechas aún no están atravesando sus apestosos cuerpos? "
"¡Acabemos con esta charla inútil y acabémoslos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:749
msgid ""
"No! We can't kill them, their leader... This Myra, she's... she's my "
"daughter!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡No podemos matarlos, su líder… Esta Myra, es… es mi hija!"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:753
msgid "Your daughter?! But... how can this be?"
msgstr "¡¿Tu hija?! Pero… ¿cómo puede ser?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:757
msgid ""
"She's the daughter I had with an Aragwaithi woman called Ysara, whom I "
"captured when fighting an Aragwaithi raid. You are too young to know her "
"story, but your elders certainly remember her, Bleda."
msgstr ""
"Es la hija que tuve con una mujer aragwaithi llamada Ysara, a quien capturé "
"luchando contra una incursión aragwaithi. Eres demasiado joven para conocer "
"su historia, pero tus mayores seguro la recuerdan, Bleda."

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:761
msgid ""
"So you don't just spit on our traditions, but you mingle with our hated "
"enemies as well! Do you see how unworthy your dear 'Master' is, Bleda?"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que no solo escupes sobre nuestras tradiciones, sino que te mezclas con "
"nuestros odiados enemigos también! ¿Ves lo indigno que es tu querido "
"«maestro», Bleda?"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:765
msgid ""
"Master Tarkyn, you know I deeply respect you; but, though your daughter is "
"welcome in our lands, we must not allow these Aragwaithi to cross the "
"steppes unscathed."
msgstr ""
"Maestro Tarkyn, sabes que te respeto profundamente; pero, aunque tu hija sea "
"bienvenida en nuestras tierras, no debemos permitir que estos aragwaithi "
"crucen las estepas ilesos."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:769
msgid ""
"By the spirits of air, don't you think enough blood has been spilled in this "
"senseless war with the Aragwaithi? And besides, they're being followed by "
"dwarves and Windsong, two peoples with whom we have no quarrel; I say let "
"them cross our land into the Far East, and forge an alliance with them, so "
"that their heirs and ours may be friends."
msgstr ""
"¡Por los espíritus del aire, no creéis que ya se ha derramado suficiente "
"sangre en esta guerra sin sentido con los aragwaithi?! Y además, les siguen "
"enanos y Hijas del Viento, dos pueblos con los que no tenemos disputa; digo "
"que dejemos que crucen nuestras tierras hacia el Lejano Oriente y forjemos "
"una alianza con ellos, para que sus herederos y los nuestros puedan ser "
"amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Denziq
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:773
msgid ""
"Over my dead body! I will not allow any more filth to be laid on the honour "
"of the Hannuks! And you, Bleda: will you do as Tarkyn, or will you uphold "
"the honour of our people and stamp out these invaders?"
msgstr ""
"¡Sobre mi cadáver! ¡No permitiré que se manche más el honor de los hannuk! Y "
"tú, Bleda: ¿harás lo que dice Tarkyn o defenderás el honor de nuestro pueblo "
"y exterminarás a estos invasores?"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:777
msgid ""
"I... I am truly sorry, Master Tarkyn, but in this I shall ride with Denziq. "
"I will not kill other Hannuks in defence of any Aragwaithi."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Lo siento mucho, maestro Tarkyn, pero en esto cabalgaré con Denziq. No "
"mataré a otros hannuk para defender a ningún aragwaithi."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:781
msgid ""
"So our alliance is broken, for I will not allow any harm to afflict my "
"daughter."
msgstr ""
"Entonces nuestra alianza se rompe, porque no permitiré que se haga daño a mi "
"hija."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:785
msgid "Father, don't...!"
msgstr "¡Padre, no…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:789
msgid ""
"And you, girl! Show me you have my blood in your veins and lead your people "
"to victory!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y tú, muchacha: ¡Muéstrame que tienes mi sangre en las venas y lleva a tu "
"pueblo a la victoria!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:793
msgid ""
"How dare he order me around...? Onwards, my friends! We must not allow "
"<i>Master</i> Tarkyn to be killed here!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo se atreve a darme órdenes…? ¡Adelante, amigos! ¡No podemos permitir "
"que maten al <i>maestro</i> Tarkyn aquí!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:799
msgid "Defeat both Bleda and Denziq"
msgstr "Derrotar a Bleda y Denziq"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:827
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:45
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:50
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:683
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:752
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:51
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:51
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:798
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/23_Holy_Fire.cfg:49
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:45
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:432
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:37
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:333
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:464
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:584
msgid "Death of Tarkyn"
msgstr "Muerte de Tarkyn"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:846
msgid "No! Spare his life, for he does not deserve to die."
msgstr "¡No! ¡Perdonadle la vida, no merece morir!"

#. [message], speaker=Bleda
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:850
msgid ""
"I will not suffer the shame of being spared by filthy Aragwaithi and "
"unworthy traitors of his own race! (stabs himself)"
msgstr ""
"¡No sufriré la vergüenza de ser perdonado por sucios aragwaithi y traidores "
"indignos de su propia raza! (se apuñala)"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:854
msgid "(sighing) So much hatred, for what?"
msgstr "(suspirando) Tanto odio… ¿para qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:862
msgid ""
"Denziq and his clan were a bunch of unworthy idiots, but I truly regret "
"having to kill Bleda. Let his clansmen flee; they will find somewhere else "
"to live."
msgstr ""
"Denziq y su clan eran un hatajo de idiotas indignos, pero realmente lamento "
"haber tenido que matar a Bleda. Dejad que sus clanes huyan; encontrarán otro "
"lugar donde vivir."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:866
msgid ""
"But they will certainly tell to other Hannuks what happened here; won't you "
"be attacked again then?"
msgstr ""
"Pero seguro que contarán a otros hannuk lo que pasó aquí; ¿no te atacarán de "
"nuevo entonces?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:870
msgid ""
"No. We Hannuks do not take anyone's grudge as our own, unless it is a threat "
"to all of us. And you are nothing more than a ragtag band of losers of a "
"distant war."
msgstr ""
"No. Los hannuk no tomamos la venganza de nadie como propia, a menos que sea "
"una amenaza para todos nosotros. Y vosotros no sois más que un puñado de "
"perdedores de una guerra lejana."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:874
msgid ""
"(sulks) You sure talk a lot for someone who has just had your arse saved by "
"this ragtag bunch of losers, <i>dad</i>."
msgstr ""
"(refunfuña) Hablas mucho para alguien a quien acaba de salvarle el culo este "
"puñado de perdedores, <i>papá</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:878
msgid ""
"To begin with, I wouldn't have even needed your help hadn't you showed up, "
"<i>sweetheart</i>. And you better watch out the language you use with me, "
"understand?"
msgstr ""
"Para empezar, no habría necesitado vuestra ayuda si no hubierais aparecido, "
"<i>cariño</i>. Y mejor cuida el lenguaje que usas conmigo, ¿entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:882
msgid ""
"(mumbling) He has just met me and is already lecturing me, how dare...?!"
msgstr ""
"(murmurando) Acaba de conocerme y ya me está dando lecciones, ¿cómo se "
"atreve…?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:886
msgid ""
"(whispering) It may be only me, but I think these two will get along quite "
"well..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Puede que solo sea yo, pero creo que estos dos se van a llevar "
"bastante bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:894
msgid ""
"But come into my village; after travelling for such a long time, you must be "
"tired. And you, Myra, after you tend to your wounded, come to my hut; I'd "
"like to talk with you."
msgstr ""
"Pero entrad en mi aldea; después de viajar tanto tiempo, debéis estar "
"cansados. Y tú, Myra, cuando atiendas a tus heridos, ven a mi cabaña; me "
"gustaría hablar contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:948
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:503
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:790
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:788
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/20_Ring_Of_Fire.cfg:693
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/21_The_Will_Of_The_Naiad.cfg:447
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:874
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/23_Holy_Fire.cfg:420
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:908
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:873
msgid "I can't fall, I must find a new home for everyone..."
msgstr "No puedo caer, tengo que encontrar un nuevo hogar para todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:976
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:531
