#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:990
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:545
