#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:615
msgid "I have failed in protecting my people..."
msgstr "He fallado en proteger a mi pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:1004
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:559
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:846
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/19_Fires_Of_Hope.cfg:844
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/20_Ring_Of_Fire.cfg:735
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/22_Where_The_Sun_Is_Born.cfg:930
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/23_Holy_Fire.cfg:476
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/24_The_Sun_Path.cfg:950
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/25_Wings_Of_Rebellion.cfg:929
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/26_The_Conquest_Of_The_Promised_Land.cfg:629
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/31_Night_Fire.cfg:438
msgid "Argh! How can I die now, Alenya needs me...!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Cómo puedo morir ahora, Alenya me necesita…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:1032
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:587
msgid ""
"I searched my daughter for so long, how can I die after just meeting her?..."
msgstr ""
"Busqué a mi hija durante tanto tiempo, ¿cómo puedo morir después de haberla "
"encontrado…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/16_Blood_Of_The_Steppes.cfg:1044
msgid ""
"We have been crossing these steppes for far too long; if we keep like this, "
"we will die of exhaustion!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos estado cruzando estas estepas durante demasiado tiempo; ¡si seguimos "
"así, moriremos de agotamiento!"

#. [scenario], id=17_Ashes_Of_The_War
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:4
msgid "Ashes of the War"
msgstr "Cenizas de la Guerra"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:17
msgid "Destroy Assix with Myra"
msgstr "Destruir a Assix con Myra"

#. [objectives]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:55
msgid ""
"Hint: Tarkyn's units that remained alive to the end of the previous scenario "
"are now under Myra's command. Additionally, she may now recruit Hannuks."
msgstr ""
"PISTA: Las unidades de Tarkyn que sobrevivieron hasta el final del escenario "
"anterior están ahora bajo el mando de Myra. Además, ahora puede reclutar "
"hannuk."

#. [side], type=Saurian Lich
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:84
msgid "Assix"
msgstr "Assix"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:151
msgid ""
"So, Ravyan, I see those children have finally let you go... Did you manage "
"to convince them your hair is not made of gold?"
msgstr ""
"Así que, Ravyan, veo que esos niños por fin te han dejado ir… ¿Lograste "
"convencerlos de que tu pelo no está hecho de oro?"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:155
msgid "(chuckling) No, I just gave up and yielded some of it..."
msgstr "(riendo) No, simplemente me rendí y les di un poco…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:159
msgid ""
"We have to admit, my friend, the education we used to receive at home was "
"extremely biased. These Hannuks are nothing like the ruthless barbarians we "
"were told they were."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que admitir, amigo, que la educación que recibíamos en casa era muy "
"sesgada. Estos hannuk no tienen nada que ver con los bárbaros despiadados "
"que nos decían que eran."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Och, I understand ye. It was the same with us dwarves about the trolls, "
"until I met that brave Groth. Do you think the remains of his people have "
"managed to find a new home?"
msgstr ""
"Och, te entiendo. Con nosotros los enanos era lo mismo con los trolls, hasta "
"que conocí al valiente Groth. ¿Crees que los restos de su pueblo han logrado "
"encontrar un nuevo hogar?"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:167
msgid ""
"I hope they have, as I hope the elvish survivors have managed to find a new "
"and safe forest for themselves..."
msgstr ""
"Espero que sí, como espero que los supervivientes élficos hayan logrado "
"encontrar un bosque nuevo y seguro para ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:171
msgid ""
"Sorry for spoiling the adorable moment, but we must discuss what we have "
"ahead of us. Master Tarkyn has welcomed us in his land, but we can't stay "
"here forever, and we still have a lot of Hannuk tribes on our way until we "
"reach the Far East."
msgstr ""
"Perdonad por romper el momento adorable, pero tenemos que hablar de lo que "
"nos espera. El maestro Tarkyn nos ha recibido en su tierra, pero no podemos "
"quedarnos aquí para siempre, y aún tenemos muchas tribus hannuk en el camino "
"hasta llegar al Lejano Oriente."

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:175
msgid ""
"Look! A rider comes from our western neighbours... And he brings the bloody "
"banner!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad! ¡Un jinete viene de nuestros vecinos del oeste… Y trae el estandarte "
"ensangrentado!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:179
msgid "What does this 'bloody banner' mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué significa ese «estandarte ensangrentado»?"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:183
msgid "That an ally has just been destroyed by an invading force..."
msgstr "Que un aliado acaba de ser destruido por una fuerza invasora…"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Does that mean the dragons have followed us into the steppes? But we haven't "
"seen any of them during our entire journey out of the Meadows!"
msgstr ""
"¿Eso significa que los dragones nos han seguido hasta las estepas? ¡Pero no "
"hemos visto ninguno durante todo nuestro viaje desde los Prados!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:191
msgid ""
"Maybe they were just reorganizing after the defeat of their leader. Don't "
"forget that Shek'har and his sons still live."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez solo se estaban reorganizando tras la derrota de su líder. No "
"olvides que Shek’har y sus hijos aún viven."

#. [unit], id=Messenger, type=Hannuk Mangudai
#. [unit_type], id=Messenger, race=celestial
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:206
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/celestials/d1_Messenger.cfg:5
msgid "Messenger"
msgstr "Mensajero"

#. [message], speaker=Messenger
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:216
msgid "(panting) Master Tarkyn... Lizards... Walking dead... Coming..."
msgstr "(jadeando) Maestro Tarkyn… Lagartos… Muertos andantes… Vienen…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:220
msgid "Get a hold of yourself, man! Take a breath and tell us what exactly..."
msgstr "¡Contrólate, hombre! Respira hondo y dinos exactamente qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:230
msgid "Darn it, he was badly wounded already..."
msgstr "Maldición, ya estaba gravemente herido…"

#. [message], speaker=Sentinel
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Look! I can see the lizards the messenger was talking about; I have seen "
"those monsters before, they're saurians; but there are other... things with "
"them..."
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad! Puedo ver los lagartos de los que hablaba el mensajero; he visto "
"esos monstruos antes, son saurios; pero hay otras… cosas con ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:238
msgid "They must be undead..."
msgstr "Deben ser no-muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:242
msgid ""
"(Sibilant voice in the distance): Myra of Hiera'Shirsha! I have long craved "
"the moment I'd have the pleasure of destroying you and your cursed "
"companions! You made me suffer beyond comprehension, and made me turn into a "
"monster; but I am now more powerful than ever before, and now I shall have "
"my revenge!"
msgstr ""
"(voz sibilante a lo lejos): ¡Myra de Hiera’Shirsha! ¡Cuánto he ansiado el "
"momento en que tendría el placer de destruiros a ti y a tus malditos "
"compañeros! Me hicisteis sufrir más allá de lo comprensible y me "
"convertisteis en un monstruo; ¡pero ahora soy más poderoso que nunca y "
"tendré mi venganza!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:246
msgid ""
"This voice... No, it can't be Assix... Veela crushed him in those caves..."
msgstr "Esta voz… No, no puede ser Assix… Veela lo aplastó en aquellas cuevas…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:250
msgid ""
"So he is that lizard who stole the Book of the Dead from Hiera'Shirsha; he "
"evidently learned the infamous transformation into an immortal sorcerer: a "
"lich."
msgstr ""
"Así que es ese lagarto que robó el Libro de los Muertos de Hiera’Shirsha; "
"evidentemente aprendió la infame transformación en hechicero inmortal: un "
"liche."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:254
msgid "Immortal you say?!"
msgstr "¡¿Inmortal dices?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Immortal, yes, but not invincible; he is highly resistant against physical "
"damage, but the arcane arts of Alenya and Lady Myra can easily destroy the "
"magic that binds his soul to his body and turn his skeleton into ashes."
msgstr ""
"Inmortal, sí, pero no invencible; es muy resistente al daño físico, pero las "
"artes arcanas de Alenya y lady Myra pueden destruir fácilmente la magia que "
"ata su alma a su cuerpo y convertir su esqueleto en cenizas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:262
msgid ""
"(in rage) Aragwaithi, Windsong, prepare for battle! And you, Alenya, don't "
"you even dare laying a finger on that cursed lizard, he's mine!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) ¡Aragwaithi, Hijas del Viento, preparaos para la batalla! ¡Y tú, "
"Alenya, ni se te ocurra tocar a ese lagarto maldito, es mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:266
msgid "(raises eyebrows) As you wish, <i>milady</i>..."
msgstr "(alza las cejas) Como desees, <i>milady</i>…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:270
msgid ""
"Hannuks, prepare yourselves as well! Our arrows and blades may have little "
"effect on fleshless skeletons, but we can still trample them under the "
"weight of our war chariots!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hannuk, preparaos también! Nuestras flechas y espadas pueden tener poco "
"efecto en esqueletos sin carne, ¡pero aún podemos aplastarlos bajo el peso "
"de nuestros carros de guerra!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:285
msgid ""
"You damned little witch, you have no idea of the pain I suffered when I "
"drank from the Fountain of Life... But I shall presently give you a small "
"taste of that pain!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita brujita, no tienes idea del dolor que sufrí cuando bebí de la "
"Fuente de la Vida…! ¡Pero ahora mismo os daré un pequeño sabor de ese dolor!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:302
msgid "Foolish apes! Death no longer affects me!"
msgstr "¡Monos estúpidos! ¡La muerte ya no me afecta!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:309
msgid "BY THE NINE HELLS, I TOLD YOU HE'S MINE!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡POR LOS NUEVE INFIERNOS, OS DIJE QUE ES MÍO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:339
msgid "When will you understand it? You cannot defeat me!"
msgstr "¿Cuándo lo entenderéis? ¡No podéis derrotarme!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:346
msgid ""
"As I thought, ciphers and physical attacks have no effect on him... I must "
"use arcane spells."
msgstr ""
"Tal como pensaba, los cifrados y los ataques físicos no le hacen efecto… "
"Tengo que usar hechizos arcanos."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:370
msgid "No, I can't die again!"
msgstr "¡No, no puedo morir otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:374
msgid "VANISH INTO OBLIVION, YOU DISGUSTING LIZARD!"
msgstr "¡¡¡DESAPARECE EN EL OLVIDO, LAGARTO ASQUEROSO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:378
msgid ""
"Humans, dwarves and saurians alike stood in awe as a massive outburst of "
"arcane energy wrapped the saurian lich, reducing him to ashes and destroying "
"what was left of his soul. With his destruction, the undead readily fell, "
"and the surviving saurians, suddenly overwhelmed, ran for their lives."
msgstr ""
"Humanos, enanos y saurios por igual se quedaron atónitos mientras una enorme "
"explosión de energía arcana envolvía al liche saurio, reduciéndolo a cenizas "
"y destruyendo lo que quedaba de su alma. Con su destrucción, los no-muertos "
"cayeron de inmediato, y los saurios supervivientes, repentinamente "
"superados, huyeron por sus vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:391
msgid ""
"We have destroyed Assix and his lackeys, but I'm certain his troop was but a "
"vanguard. Akashia, select the swiftest Sky Runners and tell them to fly to "
"the west and see the size of the enemy's real army."
msgstr ""
"Hemos destruido a Assix y sus lacayos, pero estoy segura de que su tropa era "
"solo una vanguardia. Akashia, selecciona a los Corredores del Cielo más "
"rápidos y diles que vuelen hacia el oeste para ver el tamaño del verdadero "
"ejército enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:395
msgid "As you command, milady."
msgstr "Como ordenes, milady."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:454
msgid "Some time later..."
msgstr "Algún tiempo después…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:458
msgid "So, have they returned?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿han vuelto?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:462
msgid ""
"They have, milady... According to them, the enemy army is immense, as if the "
"drakes hadn't had those massive losses in the Meadows. And, to make matters "
"worse, this new army is commanded by Shek'har himself."
msgstr ""
"Sí, milady… Según ellos, el ejército enemigo es inmenso, como si los dracos "
"no hubieran sufrido esas enormes pérdidas en los Prados. Y, para empeorar "
"las cosas, este nuevo ejército está comandado por el propio Shek’har."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:466
msgid ""
"(screaming in rage) Blast it! Haven't they destroyed our homes already?! "
"What else do they want from us?!"
msgstr ""
"(gritando de rabia) ¡Maldición! ¿¡Es que no han destruido ya nuestros "
"hogares!? ¡¿Qué más quieren de nosotros?!"

#. [message], speaker=Alenya
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:470
msgid ""
"Revenge, most likely. Revenge for the humiliation suffered at Garet-Desh."
msgstr ""
"Estoy bastante segura de que Shek’har quiere venganza por la humillación "
"sufrida en Garet-Desh."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:474
msgid ""
"This is a serious matter indeed. We must hurry to the city of Ughure, where "
"the Great Shamans live, and tell them what is happening. Only they have the "
"power to summon the Golden Horde of the Hannuks, with which we may defeat "
"these lizards."
msgstr ""
"Es un asunto grave de verdad. Debemos apresurarnos hacia la ciudad de "
"Ughure, donde viven los Grandes Chamanes, y contarles lo que está pasando. "
"Solo ellos tienen el poder de convocar a la Horda Dorada de los hannuk, con "
"la que quizá podamos derrotar a estos lagartos."

#. [message], speaker=Dvalin
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:478
msgid ""
"And this time, we are not just fleeing without giving them the payback; they "
"have lost many fire dragons, drakes and saurians already, not counting that "
"the Sky Dragon is no more."
msgstr ""
"Y esta vez no solo estamos huyendo sin darles su merecido; ya han perdido "
"muchos dragones de fuego, dracos y saurios, sin contar que el Dragón del "
"Cielo ya no está."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:482
msgid ""
"You're right, Dvalin: this time, we will settle this matter once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, Dvalin: esta vez arreglaremos este asunto de una vez por todas."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:486
msgid ""
"It is decided then; now, we must prepare to evacuate this land. And hurry "
"up, for we have no second to waste!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces está decidido; ahora debemos prepararnos para evacuar esta tierra. "
"¡Y daos prisa, no tenemos ni un segundo que perder!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/17_Ashes_Of_The_War.cfg:599
msgid "Oh no, dragon armies loom in the horizon! We're doomed..."
msgstr ""
"¡Oh no, ejércitos de dragones se perfilan en el horizonte! ¡Estamos "
"perdidos…!"

#. [scenario], id=18_Besieged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:4
msgid "Besieged"
msgstr "Sitiados"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:22
msgid "Defeat Rugar and Atyllan"
msgstr "Derrotar a Rugar y Atyllan"

#. [objectives]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:60
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:693
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:762
msgid ""
"Hint: Focus on defeating both Atyllan and Rugar, don't waste time trying to "
"kill the other leaders"
msgstr ""
"PISTA: Centraos en derrotar a ambos Atyllan y Rugar, no perdáis tiempo "
"intentando matar a los demás líderes"

#. [side], type=Hannuk Great Shaman
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/18_Besieged.cfg:88
