#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:59
msgid "Maat'Kare"
msgstr "Maat'Kare"

#. [unit], id=Aldrik, type=Child
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:79
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/34_Last_Revelations.cfg:42
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/36_A_New_Legend_Rises.cfg:78
msgid "Aldrik"
msgstr "Aldrik"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Executioner
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:87
msgid "Karon"
msgstr "Karon"

#. [side], type=Twilight Walker
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:106
msgid "Damalis"
msgstr "Damalis"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:197
msgid ""
"Aldrik, come see uncle Ravyan, he has ended a city gathering just to see you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aldrik, ven a ver al tío Ravyan, terminó una reunión de la ciudad solo para "
"verte!"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:201
msgid "It's alright, let the boy play with his friends..."
msgstr "Está bien, deja que el niño juegue con sus amigos..."

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Darn it, I'm getting old for all these bureaucratic affairs... Sitting for "
"hours in a row is more tiring than it may seem."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, me estoy haciendo viejo para tantos asuntos burocráticos... Estar "
"sentado horas seguidas es más cansado de lo que parece."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:209
msgid "Has any of you heard news from Akashia and Dvalin recently?"
msgstr "¿Alguno de ustedes ha tenido noticias recientes de Akashia y Dvalin?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:213
msgid ""
"Akashia is still cloistered in Hiera'Laksha; I told her to take some time "
"off work, but she's so absorbed with training those new girls... Dvalin is "
"still busy digging the mountains after the tunnels that lead to the Great "
"Continent. As far as I know, they were closed during an earthquake many "
"years ago, but Dvalin says he will not rest before finding a way for Alenya "
"to see her home again. However, last time I saw her she really did not seem "
"to be that eager for that."
msgstr ""
"Akashia sigue recluida en Hiera’Laksha; le dije que se tomara un tiempo "
"libre del trabajo, pero está tan absorta entrenando a las chicas nuevas… "
"Dvalin sigue ocupado cavando las montañas en busca de los túneles que llevan "
"al Gran Continente. Que yo sepa, se cerraron durante un terremoto hace "
"muchos años, pero Dvalin dice que no descansará hasta encontrar un camino "
"para que Alenya pueda volver a casa. Sin embargo, la última vez que la vi "
"realmente no parecía tener prisa por irse de este lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:217
msgid ""
"Dwarves and elves are so complicated... Why don't they marry once and for "
"all, have children and be happy?"
msgstr ""
"Los enanos y los elfos son tan complicados... ¿Por qué no se casan de una "
"vez, tienen hijos y son felices?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:221
msgid ""
"I guess it is harder for them to overcome the differences between their "
"peoples... However, when we visited Alenya just a few days ago, I thought "
"her belly was a bit larger than it usually is, didn't you think so too?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que les cuesta más superar las diferencias entre sus pueblos... Sin "
"embargo, cuando visitamos a Alenya hace unos días, me pareció que su barriga "
"estaba un poco más grande de lo normal, ¿tú también lo pensaste?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Nah, I think she's just getting fat; no wonder why, she keeps eating and "
"drinking dwarf food..."
msgstr ""
"Nah, creo que solo está engordando; no me extraña, no para de comer y beber "
"comida enana..."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:237
msgid "What is it now?"
msgstr "¿Y ahora qué?"

#. [message]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:241
msgid ""
"There are two forces coming to our city, sir: minotaurs from the southwest "
"and vampires from the northwest. Should I send the rallying call to our "
"soldiers?"
msgstr ""
"Hay dos fuerzas viniendo a nuestra ciudad, señor: minotauros del suroeste y "
"vampiros del noroeste. ¿Debo dar la orden de reunir a nuestros soldados?"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:245
msgid ""
"Yes. This minotaur attack is only natural, they're constantly harassing us; "
"but the vampires seem to have forgotten that attacking us is foolish, and so "
"we must remind them of that. Myra, would you like to lead us to victory once "
"more, for old times' sake?"
msgstr ""
"Sí. Este ataque de minotauros es lo normal, no paran de hostigarnos; pero "
"los vampiros parece que olvidaron que atacarnos es una tontería, y tenemos "
"que recordárselo. Myra, ¿te gustaría liderarnos a la victoria una vez más, "
"por los viejos tiempos?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:249
msgid ""
"(smiling) Well, if you so insist... Aldrik, you stay in the academy until "
"mommy and daddy are done with those meanies, and don't try and convince me "
"to let you fight, understand?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Bueno, si tanto insistes... Aldrik, tú quédate en la academia "
"hasta que mamá y papá terminen con esos malos, ¡y no intentes convencerme de "
"que te deje pelear, entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Aldrik
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:253
msgid "(Sulks)"
msgstr "(hace pucheros)"

#. [message], speaker=Damalis
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Look at them... They think they can come and take our lands as they wish, "
"but they're terribly wrong! Let's avenge our fallen kinsmen, my warriors!"
msgstr ""
"Mírenlos... Creen que pueden venir y tomar nuestras tierras como les dé la "
"gana, ¡pero están terriblemente equivocados! ¡Venguemos a nuestros hermanos "
"caídos, guerreros!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:276
msgid "Ah, now I see your new units, Ravyan."
msgstr "Ah, ahora veo tus nuevas unidades, Ravyan."

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:280
msgid ""
"We have commissioned the dwarves to forge these armours for us. I have "
"noticed in many occasions that the Aragwaithi soldiers, though swift, were "
"too vulnerable to enemy attacks. By wearing armour, they will last more in "
"battle, though on the downside all those metallic parts will encumber them "
"considerably."
msgstr ""
"Encargamos a los enanos que forjaran estas armaduras para nosotros. He "
"notado en muchas ocasiones que los soldados aragwaithi, aunque rápidos, eran "
"demasiado vulnerables a los ataques enemigos. Con armadura durarán más en "
"batalla, aunque el inconveniente es que todas esas partes metálicas los "
"entorpecerán bastante."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Well, they were not very strong, after all. However, this vampire attack "
"happening all of a sudden is bothering me; their last attack on Maat'kare "
"was over two years ago, right?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, al fin y al cabo no eran muy fuertes. Sin embargo, este ataque "
"vampírico repentino me preocupa; su último ataque a Maat'Kare fue hace más "
"de dos años, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Exactly; it coincided with the founding of Hiera'Laksha, actually. That "
"vampire commander must have been an unusually good tactician, if he managed "
"to avoid the Windsong; by sea they couldn't have come, for vampires don't "
"sail."
msgstr ""
"Exacto; coincidió con la fundación de Hiera'Laksha, de hecho. Ese comandante "
"vampiro debió ser un táctico excepcionalmente bueno si logró evitar a las "
"Hijas del Viento; por mar no pudieron haber venido, porque los vampiros no "
"navegan."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:297
msgid ""
"That's weird; Vrykos is very careful with his best strategists, why would he "
"let one go on a suicidal attack...? Well, maybe this Damalis managed to "
"avoid his lord's vigilance as well, or maybe he was just lucky after all. I "
"must be getting paranoid..."
msgstr ""
"Eso es raro; Vrykos es muy cuidadoso con sus mejores estrategas, ¿por qué "
"dejaría que uno se fuera en un ataque suicida...? Bueno, tal vez este "
"Damalis logró evitar la vigilancia de su señor, o simplemente tuvo suerte. "
"Debo estar volviéndome paranoica..."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:361
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:415
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:416
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/31_Night_Fire.cfg:406
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/32_Fading_Of_A_Flame.cfg:533
msgid "How could I have fallen, so many people depend on me...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo he podido caer, tanta gente depende de mí…?"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:379
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:433
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:434
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/31_Night_Fire.cfg:424
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/32_Fading_Of_A_Flame.cfg:551
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/33_The_Valley_Of_Silence.cfg:448
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:1316
msgid "Jevyan! No, you can't die now... NO!"
msgstr "¡Jevyan! ¡No, no puedes morir ahora… NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Ravyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:393
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:1368
msgid "I have failed in protecting Maat'Kare..."
msgstr "He fallado en proteger Maat’Kare…"

#. [message], speaker=Tarkyn
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:407
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/35_Wrath_Of_The_Heavens.cfg:1382
msgid "Argh! My days are ended; farewell, friends..."
msgstr "¡Argh! Mis días han terminado; adiós, amigos…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:411
msgid "Father, no! Please, don't die, I need you...!"
msgstr "¡Padre, no! ¡Por favor, no mueras, te necesito...!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/27_The_Rise_Of_MaatKare.cfg:423
msgid ""
"By the Gods of Light, we have fought endless hordes of dragons and so many "
"other enemies, and we can't defeat even these small troops?"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, hemos luchado contra hordas interminables de "
"dragones y tantos otros enemigos, y no podemos derrotar ni siquiera a estas "
"pequeñas tropas?!"

#. [scenario], id=28_Embers_Of_War
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:4
msgid "Embers of War"
msgstr "Ascuas de Guerra"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:33
msgid "Death of Eranak"
msgstr "Muerte de Eranak"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:67
msgid "Eranak"
msgstr "Eranak"

#. [side], type=Mistress
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:86
msgid "Duchess Lara"
msgstr "Duquesa Lara"

#. [side], type=Mistress
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:91
msgid "Northern Vampires"
msgstr "Vampiros del Norte"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:106
msgid "Chief Hagash"
msgstr "Jefe Hagash"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:111
msgid "Kamdrol"
msgstr "Kamdrol"

#. [unit], id=Kunlun, type=Hannuk Sharpshooter
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:140
msgid "Kun'lun"
msgstr "Kun’lun"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Weird... We have entered Ogesh's lands quite a while ago, but we haven't "
"seen any orc. Last time we came by this path, we were greeted quite "
"boisterously, but now..."
msgstr ""
"Qué raro… Hace rato que entramos en las tierras de Ogesh, pero no hemos "
"visto ni un solo orco. La última vez que pasamos por aquí nos recibieron con "
"bastante alboroto, pero ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:186
msgid ""
"I don't like this quietness either; it's as if every orc in the surroundings "
"have gathered at a single place..."
msgstr ""
"Tampoco me gusta esta calma; es como si todos los orcos de los alrededores "
"se hubieran reunido en un solo lugar…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:190
msgid "...a place that needs every friendly arm to defend it..."
msgstr "…un lugar que necesita todos los brazos amigos para defenderlo…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Exactly. Besides, now that we're closer to Uldrol, I can sense something "
"abnormal amidst this fog: I sense despair, anger, anxiety, lives being "
"ended... There is a battle raging on nearby, no doubt about it."
msgstr ""
"Exacto. Además, ahora que estamos más cerca de Uldrol, puedo sentir algo "
"anormal entre esta niebla: siento desesperación, rabia, ansiedad, vidas que "
"se acaban… Hay una batalla furiosa muy cerca, sin duda."

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:198
msgid ""
"*sniff* Smoke... The fog disguised its appearance well, but not its smell. "
"By the Gods of Light, I hoped I'd never again inhale this horrible smell; "
"it's almost as if we were back to the Meadows, with the dragons raining fire "
"everywhere..."
msgstr ""
"*olfatea* Humo… La niebla disimulaba bien su aspecto, pero no su olor. Por "
"los Dioses de la Luz, esperaba no volver a oler este olor horrible; es casi "
"como si estuviéramos de vuelta en los Prados, con los dragones lloviendo "
"fuego por todas partes…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:202
msgid ""
"I fed the same hopes, Jevy, but the shadow of war is unfortunately far-"
"reaching; at least this time we won't be facing dragons... What?"
msgstr ""
"Yo albergaba las mismas esperanzas, Jevy, pero la sombra de la guerra por "
"desgracia llega muy lejos; al menos esta vez no nos enfrentaremos a "
"dragones… ¿Qué pasa?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:206
msgid ""
"If you don't mind, I'd really prefer that you didn't call me like that in "
"front of everyone."
msgstr "Si no te importa, preferiría que no me llamaras así delante de todos."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:210
msgid ""
"'Everyone'? But we're alone with the elementals- ah, I see... Sorry, I'm so "
"used to travelling alone with you, I forgot we have company this time..."
msgstr ""
"¿«Todos»? Pero si estamos solos con los elementales… ah, ya veo… Perdona, "
"estoy tan acostumbrada a viajar solo contigo que olvidé que esta vez tenemos "
"compañía…"

#. [message], speaker=Kunlun
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:214
msgid "Oh, please don't mind me, I'm just an aide, remember? (giggles)"
msgstr ""
"Oh, por favor no me presten atención, solo soy una ayudante, ¿recuerdan? "
"(risita)"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:218
msgid ""
"(blushes) I still don't understand why Tarkyn insisted so much on sending an "
"aide along... No offence to you, Kun'lun."
msgstr ""
"(se sonroja) Todavía no entiendo por qué Tarkyn insistió tanto en enviar una "
"ayudante... Sin ofender, Kunlun."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:222
msgid ""
"You'd expect that, after all these years, he'd have grown past picking on "
"you... But we can only benefit from such a promising fighter by our side. "
"Now, over with the talking; I know it's still early, but we have a friend in "
"need, and so we must hurry."
msgstr ""
"Uno esperaría que, después de tantos años, ya hubiera superado lo de "
"molestarte... Pero solo podemos beneficiarnos de tener a una luchadora tan "
"prometedora a nuestro lado. Ahora, basta de charlas; sé que es temprano, "
"pero tenemos un amigo que nos necesita y debemos apurarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:236
msgid ""
"Grunts, look! Myra of Hiera'Shirsha has arrived, just as chief Ogesh has "
"told us! Now we're saved!"
msgstr ""
"¡Grunts, mirad! ¡Ha llegado Myra de Hiera’Shirsha, tal como nos dijo el jefe "
"Ogesh! ¡Ahora estamos salvados!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:240
msgid "Warrior, where is Lord Ogesh? Has he been wounded?"
msgstr "Guerrero, ¿dónde está lord Ogesh? ¿Está herido?"

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:244
msgid "(Looks distressed)"
msgstr "(mira angustiado)"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:248
msgid "No! Don't tell me he's..."
msgstr "¡No! No me digas que está…"

#. [message], speaker=Hagash
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Yes, witch, that fool of my brother is dead; I would show you his stinking "
"corpse, but my wolves were quite hungry, you see, and left nothing of him. A "
"pity, really, I wanted to use his skull to adorn my throne..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, bruja, ese estúpido de mi hermano está muerto; te mostraría su apestoso "
"cadáver, pero mis lobos tenían bastante hambre, ya ves, y no dejaron nada de "
"él. Una lástima, quería usar su cráneo para adornar mi trono…"

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:256
msgid ""
"YOU DAMN TURD-LICKING BASTARD, WE WILL AVENGE OUR CHIEF A HUNDRED-FOLD, JUST "
"YOU WAIT AND SEE!"
msgstr ""
"¡MALDITO LAMEMIERDA HIJO DE PUTA, VENGAMOS A NUESTRO JEFE CIEN VECES, YA "
"VERÁS!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Eranak, do not let the enemy unbalance you, and tell your grunts not to lose "
"their damn heads either! I will bring that stinking weakling still breathing "
"for you as a prisoner, this I promise you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eranak, no dejes que el enemigo te desequilibre, y dile a tus grunts que "
"tampoco pierdan la maldita cabeza! ¡Te traeré a ese debilucho apestoso "
"todavía respirando como prisionero, te lo prometo!"

#. [message], speaker=Kunlun
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:264
msgid "(whispers) Why is she talking like this?"
msgstr "(susurra) ¿Por qué habla así?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:268
msgid ""
"(whispers and snickers) She's just speaking a language orcs understand, see? "
"This, amongst other things, was how she managed to earn their respect."
msgstr ""
"(susurra y ríe) Solo está hablando en un idioma que los orcos entienden, "
"¿ves? Así, entre otras cosas, es como se ganó su respeto."

#. [message], speaker=Lara
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:272
msgid ""
"The arrogance of this outsider wench is dismaying! She thinks we're worms "
"beneath her feet, but today we'll show her just how wrong she is! Advance, "
"Children of the Night, this is our chance to avenge all of our brothers that "
"fell by the treacherous hands of Myra of Hiera'Shirsha!"
msgstr ""
"¡La arrogancia de esta forastera es descorazonadora! ¡Cree que somos gusanos "
"bajo sus pies, pero hoy le mostraremos lo equivocada que está! ¡Adelante, "
"Hijos de la Noche, esta es nuestra oportunidad de vengar a todos nuestros "
"hermanos caídos por las traidoras manos de Myra de Hiera’Shirsha!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:276
msgid ""
"And you'll end up as another name in the list of vampires to be avenged "
"unless you leave this place immediately."
msgstr ""
"Y acabarás como otro nombre más en la lista de vampiros por vengar a menos "
"que abandones este lugar ahora mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Lara
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:288
msgid ""
"A thousand curses upon you, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha! You may think this was "
"just another slaughter of vampires that will go unpunished, but the night "
"will soon engulf this continent, and its children will..."
msgstr ""
"¡Mil maldiciones sobre ti, Myra de Hiera’Shirsha! Puedes pensar que esto fue "
"solo otra matanza de vampiros que quedará impune, pero la noche pronto "
"envolverá este continente, y sus hijos…"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:292
msgid "Just shut your mouth at once!"
msgstr "¡Cierra la boca de una vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Lara
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:296
msgid "Ughh!!!"
msgstr "¡¡Ughh!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Hagash
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Damn you and your tricks, Windsong! I will retreat now, but I promise you "
"this is not the last time we'll meet!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita seas tú y tus trucos, Hija del Viento! ¡Me retiro ahora, pero te "
"prometo que no será la última vez que nos veamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:315
msgid "Actually, it <i>is</i>."
msgstr "En realidad, <i>sí</i> lo es."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:319
msgid ""
"As Hagash ran from the battlefield, Myra raised the Trident of the Seas, and "
"her eyes started shining intensely. Then, everyone stood still as the skies "
"were suddenly covered in dark storm clouds, and the wind increased its "
"violence."
msgstr ""
"Mientras Hagash huía del campo de batalla, Myra alzó el Tridente de los "
"Mares y sus ojos comenzaron a brillar intensamente. Entonces, todos se "
"quedaron inmóviles cuando el cielo se cubrió de repente de nubes negras de "
"tormenta y el viento aumentó su violencia."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:336
msgid ""
"And then, when it seemed like Hagash would actually manage to escape, a "
"blinding lightning shone from the clouds, the skies bellowed and a lightning "
"fell from above on the orcish chieftain, reducing him to ashes."
msgstr ""
"Y entonces, cuando parecía que Hagash realmente lograría escapar, un "
"relámpago cegador brilló desde las nubes, los cielos rugieron y un rayo cayó "
"desde lo alto sobre el jefe orco, reduciéndolo a cenizas."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:363
msgid ""
"Erm, sorry, Eranak, I think I've overdone it... I know you wanted to punish "
"him personally."
msgstr ""
"Ejem, perdona, Eranak, creo que me he pasado… Sé que querías castigarlo tú "
"personalmente."

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Ha! You struck the vermin down as he fled like a chicken, and before the "
"very eyes of his soldiers, I myself couldn't have humiliated him better! Now "
"let those weaklings cry back to their capital, they have a good story to "
"tell that stupid Hagor!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Lo fulminaste mientras huía como una gallina, y delante de los ojos de "
"sus soldados! ¡Yo mismo no lo habría humillado mejor! ¡Que esos debiluchos "
"vuelvan llorando a su capital, tienen una buena historia que contarle a ese "
"estúpido de Hagor!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:371
msgid "Hagor? You mean the son of Hagash?"
msgstr "¿Hagor? ¿Te refieres al hijo de Hagash?"

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:375
msgid ""
"The same. Unfortunately, he has recently proved his mettle and earned the "
"loyalty of his father's lackeys, so, even though we've killed Hagash, we're "
"still at war."
msgstr ""
"El mismo. Por desgracia, hace poco ha demostrado su valía y se ha ganado la "
"lealtad de los lacayos de su padre, así que, aunque hayamos matado a Hagash, "
"seguimos en guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:390
msgid "Eranak, tell me more about this new orcish-vampire alliance."
msgstr "Eranak, cuéntame más sobre esta nueva alianza entre orcos y vampiros."

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:394
msgid ""
"All I know is that we received a message just yesterday from that despicable "
"Hagash, bragging that our city was screwed because he had Vrykos of the "
"vampires with him, but I'm sure they've united because they both wanted "
"chief Ogesh's lands..."
msgstr ""
"Todo lo que sé es que ayer mismo recibimos un mensaje de ese despreciable "
"Hagash, presumiendo de que nuestra ciudad estaba perdida porque tenía a "
"Vrykos de los vampiros con él, pero estoy seguro de que se han unido porque "
"ambos querían las tierras del jefe Ogesh…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:398
msgid ""
"Vrykos may have coveted his lands, but I don't think he'd have either the "
"willingness or the necessity to ally with Hagash only for that. After all, "
"thus he'd have to share the conquered lands with the orc, and besides, "
"Vrykos is way too proud to ask for anyone's aid, especially a non-vampire... "
"No, there is some hidden reason behind this sudden alliance, and I will find "
"it out."
msgstr ""
"Vrykos puede que codiciara sus tierras, pero no creo que tuviera ni la "
"voluntad ni la necesidad de aliarse con Hagash solo por eso. Al fin y al "
"cabo, tendría que compartir las tierras conquistadas con el orco y, además, "
"Vrykos es demasiado orgulloso para pedir ayuda a nadie, especialmente a un "
"no-vampiro… No, hay alguna razón oculta detrás de esta repentina alianza, y "
"la voy a descubrir."

#. [message], speaker=Kunlun
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:447
msgid "I should've been more careful..."
msgstr "Debería haber sido más cuidadosa…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:451
msgid "Brave Kun'lun, we failed you...!"
msgstr "¡Valiente Kun’lun, te hemos fallado…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kunlun
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:455
msgid ""
"You never failed me, or any of us, Lady Myra... Just, please, send my mortal "
"shell back home, so my family may observe the rites..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca me habéis fallado, ni a mí ni a ninguno de nosotros, lady Myra… Solo, "
"por favor, enviad mi cuerpo mortal a casa para que mi familia pueda realizar "
"los ritos…"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:459
msgid "I will, my friend; I promise I will..."
msgstr "Lo haré, amiga mía; te lo prometo…"

#. [message], speaker=Eranak
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:470
msgid "Bloody curses, I have fallen without avenging chief Ogesh!"
msgstr "¡Malditas sean las sangres, he caído sin vengar al jefe Ogesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Damn it, how could we have let him die? Without him, nothing will stop "
"Hagash from uniting all of orc-kind against us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, cómo hemos podido dejar que muriera! ¡Sin él, nada impedirá que "
"Hagash una a todos los orcos contra nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Myra
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/28_Embers_Of_War.cfg:486
msgid ""
"We have taken too much time to break this siege! More vampires and orcs are "
"coming, Uldrol is condemned to fall!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hemos tardado demasiado en romper este asedio! ¡Vienen más vampiros y "
"orcos, Uldrol está condenada a caer!"

#. [scenario], id=29_Forging_Alliances
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:4
msgid "Forging Alliances"
msgstr "Forjando Alianzas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:21
msgid "Defeat Ronak with Myra"
msgstr "Derrotar a Ronak con Myra"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:33
msgid "Death of Ronak at the hands of anyone else than Myra"
msgstr "Muerte de Ronak a manos de alguien que no sea Myra"

#. [objectives]
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/scenarios/29_Forging_Allies.cfg:44
msgid ""
"NOTE: You may recruit orcs in this scenario only; orcish units will not be "
