#. [unit_type], id=Mermaid Naiad, race=merman, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Mermaid_Naiad.cfg:18
msgid ""
"There are legends, told by the most seasoned sailors, about a mermaid of "
"unparalleled beauty, whose mere voice could sway entire fleets from their "
"goal and lead them astray; and to whom the very sea seemed to obey like a "
"tame beast. Such stories are often dismissed as pure fantasy, but those who "
"claim to have seen that mythical mermaid are capable of waging their ships "
"that they have seen the fabled Naiad with their own eyes."
msgstr ""
"Existen leyendas, contadas por los marineros más curtidos, sobre una sirena "
"de belleza sin igual, cuya sola voz podía desviar flotas enteras de su rumbo "
"y llevarlas a la perdición; y a la que el mismísimo mar parecía obedecer "
"como a una bestia domesticada. Tales historias suelen considerarse pura "
"fantasía, pero quienes afirman haber visto a esa sirena mítica son capaces "
"de apostar sus barcos a que vieron a la legendaria náyade con sus propios "
"ojos."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
