msgstr "Guerrero del trueno sirenido"

#. [unit_type], id=Merman Thunder Warrior, race=merman
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Merman_Thunder_Warrior.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The Mermen Warriors form the core of the mermen armies. Wielding powerful "
"tridents, they are a bane to any who dare enter their waters.\n"
"\n"
"        Having mastered the use of the storm trident, these warriors are one "
"of the main reasons of the merfolk dominance of the seas."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros sirénidos forman el núcleo de los ejércitos sirénidos. "
"Blandiendo poderosos tridentes, son una pesadilla para cualquiera que se "
"atreva a entrar en sus aguas.\n"
"\n"
"Habiendo dominado el uso del tridente de tormenta, estos guerreros son una "
"de las principales razones del dominio sirénido sobre los mares."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lich, race=undead
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Saurian_Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Lich"
msgstr "Liche saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lich, race=undead
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Saurian_Lich.cfg:21
msgid ""
"A lich is the physical embodiment of black magic's first goal: the quest to "
"achieve immortality. Though a great deal is sacrificed in the rebirth, in "
"becoming a lich one cheats death of that which truly gives it terror. For it "
"is the mind that is retained, and the spirit which follows, though the body "
"may wither away.\n"
"\n"
"It is not known, save perhaps by the inner circles of necromancy, whether "
"life is prolonged indefinitely or simply extended. But the fact that this "
"question can be raised at all, testifies to the magnitude of what their "
"order has achieved."
msgstr ""
"Un liche es la encarnación física del primer objetivo de la magia negra: la "
"búsqueda de la inmortalidad. Aunque se sacrifica mucho en el renacimiento, "
"al convertirse en liche se engaña a la muerte de aquello que realmente le da "
"terror. Porque es la mente la que se conserva, y el espíritu el que sigue, "
"aunque el cuerpo pueda marchitarse.\n"
"\n"
"No se sabe, salvo quizá por los círculos internos de la necromancia, si la "
"vida se prolonga indefinidamente o simplemente se extiende. Pero el hecho de "
"que esta pregunta pueda plantearse ya da fe de la magnitud de lo que su "
"orden ha logrado."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=melee
