#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Simian.cfg:18
msgid ""
"These large beings live in tropical forests all over the world. Albeit "
"peaceful in normal times, they will fight fiercely to defend their territory."
msgstr ""
"Estos grandes seres viven en los bosques tropicales de todo el mundo. Aunque "
"son pacíficos en tiempos normales, lucharán con ferocidad para defender su "
"territorio."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/Simian.cfg:36
