#. [unit_type], id=Dragon Sorceress, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Dragon_Sorceress.cfg:5
msgid "female^Dragon Sorceress"
msgstr "Hechicera Dragón"

#. [unit_type], id=Dragon Sorceress, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Dragon_Sorceress.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The Dragon Sorceress is a woman who has bound with the soul of a High "
"Dragon. Wielding the mighty Trident of the Seas, with which she effectively "
"commands the sea and the storms, she still has much to develop, but her "
"powers are already nearly peerless amongst humans and even elves."
msgstr ""
"La Hechicera Dragón es una mujer que ha ligado su alma a la de un Gran "
"Dragón. Empuñando el poderoso Tridente de los Mares, con el que comanda "
"eficazmente el mar y las tormentas, aún tiene mucho que desarrollar, pero "
"sus poderes ya son casi inigualables entre humanos e incluso elfos."

#. [unit_type], id=High Ascendant, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/High_Ascendant.cfg:5
msgid "female^High Ascendant"
msgstr "Ascendiente Suprema"

#. [unit_type], id=High Ascendant, race=windsong, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=High Ascendant Irdya Avatar, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/High_Ascendant.cfg:27
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/High_Ascendant_Irdya.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Windsong legends tell of weavers who are bound not to a single spirit, but "
"to The Raw itself. As they grew up, quickly rising through the ranks of the "
"Windsong, they reached pinnacles of power that other mortals could only "
"dream of, becoming like goddesses amongst humans. They were given the title "
"of 'High Ascendant', and their deeds and wisdom became the stuff of many a "
"legend of the Windsong and even other people.\n"
"\n"
"Albeit peaceful in normal times, a High Ascendant who decides to unleash her "
"full power is a terrifying sight, even for the mightiest beings."
msgstr ""
"Las leyendas de las Hijas del Viento hablan de tejedoras que no están "
"ligadas a un solo espíritu, sino al Tejido mismo. A medida que crecían, "
"ascendiendo rápidamente en las filas de las Hijas del Viento, alcanzaron "
"cimas de poder con las que otros mortales solo podían soñar, convirtiéndose "
"en diosas entre los humanos. Recibieron el título de «Ascendiente Suprema», "
"y sus hazañas y sabiduría se convirtieron en material de numerosas leyendas "
"entre las Hijas del Viento e incluso otros pueblos.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque pacíficas en tiempos normales, una Ascendiente Suprema que decide "
"liberar todo su poder es un espectáculo aterrador, incluso para los seres "
"más poderosos."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/High_Ascendant.cfg:56
