msgstr "Tormenta Infinita"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Ascendant, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Ascendant.cfg:5
msgid "female^Nature Ascendant"
msgstr "Ascendiente de la Naturaleza"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Ascendant, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Ascendant.cfg:36
msgid ""
"Few Weavers and Prophets reach the rank of Ascendant. Not just because of "
"the difficult in reaching this goal, but also because of the danger and "
"sacrifice necessary. The path to becoming a Nature Ascendant, by its turn, "
"is similar to that of becoming a normal Ascendant, especially in its "
"difficulty. As the woman binds herself to the spirit of Nature, the bound "
"between them is augmented; consequently, not only her power over other "
"natural spirits increases, but she also develops an affinity with non-"
"sentient beings, making them do her bidding; and (perhaps most importantly) "
"her life force becomes much stronger, thus making her body immune to "
"diseases, poison and most physical damage.\n"
"\n"
"Because she's the first of her kind, the Nature Ascendant doesn't fully "
"understand her own powers yet; but one thing is certain: the strength of "
"Nature's Spirit that flows through her is not something to be taken lightly."
msgstr ""
"Pocas tejedoras y profetisas alcanzan el rango de Ascendiente. No solo por "
"la dificultad de lograrlo, sino también por el peligro y el sacrificio "
"necesarios. El camino para convertirse en Ascendiente de la Naturaleza es "
"similar al de convertirse en una Ascendiente normal, especialmente en su "
"dificultad. A medida que la mujer se une al espíritu de la Naturaleza, el "
"vínculo entre ellas se fortalece; en consecuencia, no solo aumenta su poder "
"sobre otros espíritus naturales, sino que también desarrolla afinidad con "
"seres no sensibles, haciéndolos obedecer sus órdenes; y (quizá lo más "
"importante) su fuerza vital se vuelve mucho más fuerte, haciendo su cuerpo "
"inmune a enfermedades, venenos y la mayoría de los daños físicos.\n"
"\n"
"Al ser la primera de su clase, la Ascendiente de la Naturaleza aún no "
"comprende completamente sus propios poderes; pero una cosa es segura: la "
"fuerza del Espíritu de la Naturaleza que fluye a través de ella no es algo "
"que deba tomarse a la ligera."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Ascendant.cfg:82
msgid "arrow-thorns"
msgstr "flechas-espinas"

#. [unit_type], id=Avatar of Nature, race=windsong, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Avatar of Nature Extreme, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar.cfg:5
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar_Extreme.cfg:5
msgid "female^Avatar of Nature"
msgstr "Avatar de la Naturaleza"

#. [unit_type], id=Avatar of Nature, race=windsong, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Avatar of Nature Extreme, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar.cfg:27
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar_Extreme.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The Avatar of Nature is the vessel chosen by the spirits of nature to "
"channel their full power in defence of their beloved world. Being almost "
"like an embodiment of the planet itself, her power is far superior to that "
"of most beings, and is on par with the High Dragons themselves."
msgstr ""
"El Avatar de la Naturaleza es el recipiente elegido por los espíritus de la "
"naturaleza para canalizar todo su poder en defensa de su amado mundo. Siendo "
"casi una encarnación del planeta mismo, su poder es muy superior al de la "
"mayoría de los seres y está a la altura de los propios Grandes Dragones."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar.cfg:77
msgid "Soul Outburst"
msgstr "Erupción de Alma"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Avatar_Extreme.cfg:65
msgid "Soul Barrage"
msgstr "Bombardeo de Almas"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Prophetess, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Prophet.cfg:5
msgid "female^Nature Prophetess"
msgstr "Profetisa de la Naturaleza"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Prophetess, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Prophet.cfg:22
msgid ""
"There are many among the Windsong who could successfully lead an army, or "
"plan a battle, as the council has all children trained to the best of their "
"ability. So, for the Windsong, knowing when to act is more important. The "
"Raw is affected by all events, both past and future, and is fluidic as these "
"possibilities change. Through her accompanying spirit, some Weavers learn to "
"interpret flows in The Raw as predictions for future events. With time and "
"experience, her predictions become more accurate and dependable. Eventually, "
"if she is of quality, she will be invited to join the ranks of the Prophets. "
"Unlike the farseers of other peoples, the Windsong Prophets do not 'witness' "
"events so much as apply an expanded form of cause and effect. Knowing all "
"flows are open to interpretation, Prophets are discouraged from making "
"predictions without the council of her peers.\n"
"\n"
"Unlike Envoys, Prophets have much time to study the arts of leadership and "
"healing, and she has now learned to cure poison. Moreover, her increasing "
"connection with nature has given her new powers not only over the spirits, "
"but also over the plants."
msgstr ""
"Hay muchas entre las Hijas del Viento que podrían liderar con éxito un "
"ejército o planear una batalla, pues el consejo entrena a todas las niñas lo "
"mejor que puede. Por eso, para las Hijas del Viento, saber cuándo actuar es "
"más importante. El Tejido se ve afectado por todos los eventos, pasados y "
"futuros, y es fluido a medida que cambian estas posibilidades. A través de "
"su espíritu acompañante, algunas tejedoras aprenden a interpretar los flujos "
"del Tejido como predicciones de eventos futuros. Con el tiempo y la "
"experiencia, sus predicciones se vuelven más precisas y fiables. "
"Eventualmente, si es de calidad, será invitada a unirse a las filas de las "
"Profetisas. A diferencia de los videntes de otros pueblos, las Profetisas de "
"las Hijas del Viento no «ven» los eventos tanto como aplican una forma "
"ampliada de causa y efecto. Sabiendo que todos los flujos están abiertos a "
"interpretación, se desaconseja a las profetisas hacer predicciones sin el "
"consejo de sus pares.\n"
"\n"
"A diferencia de las enviadas, las profetisas tienen mucho tiempo para "
"estudiar las artes del liderazgo y la sanación, y ahora ha aprendido a curar "
"venenos. Además, su creciente conexión con la naturaleza le ha dado nuevos "
"poderes no solo sobre los espíritus, sino también sobre las plantas."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Prophet.cfg:67
msgid "Thorns"
msgstr "Espinas"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Prophet.cfg:79
msgid "Soul Blast"
msgstr "Explosión de Alma"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Weaver, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Weaver.cfg:5
msgid "female^Nature Weaver"
msgstr "Tejedora de la Naturaleza"

#. [unit_type], id=Nature Weaver, race=windsong, gender=female
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Weaver.cfg:24
msgid ""
"While most Windsong are able to devote themselves to only one or two aspects "
"of the cipher, there are those who are able to access many. When such a "
"child is born, a spirit from The Raw appears and binds to them. However, "
"this particular child has bound with a spirit of Nature; the full "
"consequences of such unusual union are still unknown, but it is clear that "
"her potential is great."
msgstr ""
"Mientras que la mayoría de las Hijas del Viento solo pueden dedicarse a uno "
"o dos aspectos del cifrado, hay quienes pueden acceder a muchos. Cuando nace "
"una niña así, un espíritu del Tejido aparece y se une a ella. Sin embargo, "
"esta niña en particular se ha unido a un espíritu de la Naturaleza; las "
"consecuencias completas de esta unión tan inusual aún se desconocen, pero "
"está claro que su potencial es enorme."

#. [attack], type=cold, range=melee
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Weaver.cfg:54
msgid "purge"
msgstr "purga"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: wesnoth-A_Song_of_Fire/units/heroes-windsong/Nature_Weaver.cfg:72
msgid "Soul Bullet"
msgstr "Proyectil de Alma"

